INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('821', '1', '2017-09-18 09:19:01', '2017-09-18 09:19:01', '<div readability=\"55\"><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/sach_trang_2017_3.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td readability=\"4\">\n<p>B trng B TT&amp;TT Trng Minh Tun cng  ngh V CNTT tip tc phi hp vi cc c quan, n v thuc B  i mi hnh thc cng b Sch Trng a dng hn, thun tin trong vic tra cu, s dng.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Chiu ngy 19/9, ti H Ni, B TT&amp;TT va t chc l cng b pht hnh Sch Trng CNTT-TT Vit Nam 2017. y l n phm cung cp thng tin, s liu thng k chnh thc v mt s lnh vc do B TT&amp;TT qun l, c th gm: ng dng CNTT, Cng nghip CNTT, An ton thng tin, Vin thng, Internet, Pht thanh, truyn hnh v thng tin in t, Bu chinh, Nghin cu v o to v CNTT-TT cng cc lnh vc khc c lin quan.</p>\n<p>Pht biu ti l cng b pht hnh Sch Trng 2017, y vin Trung ng ng, B trng B TT&amp;TT Trng Minh Tun cho bit, trong thi gian qua, ng v Chnh ph  rt quan tm n s pht trin ca ngnh CNTT c bit l trong bi cnh trn th gii xut hin nhiu xu hng cng ngh tin tin vi CNTT l nn tng cho s i mi v sng to.</p>\n<p>CNTT  nc ta c coi l h tng ca h tng kinh t - x hi, l ng lc  pht trin t nc, nng cao nng lc cnh tranh quc gia, gp phn y mnh s nghip cng nghip ha, hin i ha. CNTT cng l lnh vc qun l nh nc c B TT&amp;TT rt ch trng trong giai on hin nay.</p>\n<p> p ng nhu cu thng tin phc v cho cng tc qun l nh nc, pht trin th trng, thu ht u t, hi nhp kinh t th gii trong lnh vc CNTT-TT t nm 2009, B TT&amp;TT  t chc xy dng Sch Trng CNTT-TT Vit Nam. y l mt n phm c uy tn, cung cp s liu thng k chnh thc v lnh vc do B TT&amp;TT qun l, phn nh hin trng pht trin CNTT-TT ca t nc, c nhiu c quan, t chc trong nc v quc t s dng.</p>\n<p>Sau hai nm 2015 - 2016 tp trung r sot cc ch s v ngnh CNTT-TT, nm nay, B TT&amp;TT  phi hp vi cc B, ngnh, a phng v cc t chc lin quan tip tc thu thp, x l, phn tch s liu  hon thnh xy dng Sch Trng CNTT-TT.</p>\n<p>Theo i din V CNTT - B TT&amp;TT, c khi ng trin khai t khong thng 3/2017, n nay phin bn ting Vit ca Sch Trng CNTT-TT 2017  c in v pht hnh, phin bn ting Anh ca n phm ny s c hon thin, in n v d kin pht hnh trong thng 10 nm nay. ng thi, B TT&amp;TT cng s cng b ti liu Sch Trng CNTT-TT Vit Nam 2017 di dng in t trn Cng thng tin ca B  c gi c th tham kho rng ri.</p><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/sach_trang_2017_4.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td readability=\"1\">\n<p>Nm 2017 l ln u tin n phm Sch Trng CNTT-TT c xy dng v pht hnh vi 2 n phm ting Vit v ting Anh ring bit.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Cng trong pht biu ti bui l, B trng Trng Minh Tun cho bit, trong nm 2016, ngnh TT&amp;TT tip tc khng nh vai tr, v tr ca mnh trong s pht trin kinh t x hi ca t nc. Tng doanh thu pht sinh ton ngnh c t 1,64 triu t ng (tng ng 72,7 t USD), tc  tng trng t 9,1% so vi nm 2015, cao hn 3% so vi tng trng GDP trung bnh c nc.</p></div>', 'Tip tc i mi phng php thng k, nng cao gi tr thng tin trong Sch Trng CNTT-TT', '<div><img src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/sach_trang_2017_3.jpg\" width=\"130\" height=\"100\"> ICTnews - B&#7897; tr&#432;&#7903;ng B&#7897; TT&amp;TT Tr&#432;&#417;ng Minh Tu&#7845;n &#273;&#7873; ngh&#7883; V&#7909; CNTT th&#7901;i gian t&#7899;i ti&#7871;p t&#7909;c ph&#7889;i h&#7907;p ch&#7863;t ch&#7869; v&#7899;i c&aacute;c B&#7897;, ng&agrave;nh, &#273;&#7883;a ph&#432;&#417;ng, c&aacute;c t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, doanh nghi&#7879;p &#273;&#7875; ho&agrave;n thi&#7879;n, &#273;&#7893;i m&#7899;i ph&#432;&#417;ng ph&aacute;p ph&acirc;n t&iacute;ch, th&#7889;ng k&ecirc;, n&acirc;ng cao gi&aacute; tr&#7883; th&ocirc;ng tin trong S&aacute;ch Tr&#7855;ng. ]]&gt;</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tiep-tuc-doi-moi-phuong-phap-thong-ke-nang-cao-gia-tri-thong-tin-trong-sach-trang-cntt-tt', '', '', '2017-09-18 09:19:01', '2017-09-18 09:19:01', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/18/tiep-tuc-doi-moi-phuong-phap-thong-ke-nang-cao-gia-tri-thong-tin-trong-sach-trang-cntt-tt/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
