INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('823', '1', '2017-09-18 08:22:01', '2017-09-18 08:22:01', '<div readability=\"19\">\n<p>M c thu thp mt s lng ln d liu ngi dng, bao gm: Tn my tnh, danh sch nhng phn mm  ci t, bao gm nhng bn cp nht ca Windows, danh sch tt c nhng tin trnh ang chy, a ch IP v a ch MAC, thng tin b sung.</p>\n<p><em>VD: Liu tin trnh c ang chy vi quyn qun tr hay khng.</em></p>\n<h2><strong>Tc ng tim n</strong></h2><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"CClearner &#x111;ang &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c s&#x1EED; d&#x1EE5;ng v&#xF4; c&#xF9;ng r&#x1ED9;ng r&#xE3;i n&#xEA;n kh&#x1EA3; n&#x103;ng s&#x1ED1; m&#xE1;y b&#x1ECB; l&#xE2;y nhi&#x1EC5;m c&#x169;ng r&#x1EA5;t l&#x1EDB;n.\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/xyz1.png\" /></td></tr><tr><td readability=\"1\">\n<p>CClearner ang c s dng v cng rng ri nn kh nng s my b ly nhim cng rt ln.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Tc ng ca cuc tn cng ny c th rt nghim trng. CCleaner tuyn b  c hn 2 t lt ti xung trn ton th gii tnh n thng 11 nm 2016 v tng thm 5 triu mi tun.</p>\n<p>Nhng h thng b nh hng cn c khi phc li trng thi trc ngy 15/8/2017, cp nht ln phin bn mi nht ca CCleaner hoc ci mi  trnh ly nhim.</p>\n<p>Phin bn hin ti ca CCleaner l v5.34.Nhng, phin bn min ph ca CCleaner khng cung cp cp nht t ng, v vy ngi dng cn phi thc hin cp nht mt cch th cng.</p>\n<p>Vo thi im ny, nhng chng trnh pht hin virus i vi nguy c ny vn cn rt thp, ch vo mc khong 1/64 (trong 64 antivirus th ch c 1 antivirus pht hin ra). V vy, <strong>khuyn co ngi dng cn kim tra li, cp nht phin bn 5.34 hoc mi hn ca CCleaner; hoc g b ng dng.</strong>\n<br /></p></div>', 'Cnh bo m c trong chng trnh dn rc my tnh CClearner', '<div><img src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/xyz12.png\" width=\"130\" height=\"100\"> ICTnews - M&atilde; &#273;&#7897;c n&agrave;y c&oacute; trong phi&ecirc;n b&#7843;n ch&iacute;nh th&#7913;c c&#7911;a ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m v&agrave; th&#7921;c hi&#7879;n &#273;&aacute;nh c&#7855;p th&ocirc;ng tin v&#7873; t&ecirc;n m&aacute;y t&iacute;nh, danh s&aacute;ch nh&#7919;ng ph&#7847;n m&#7873;m &#273;&atilde; c&agrave;i &#273;&#7863;t, danh s&aacute;ch t&#7845;t c&#7843; nh&#7919;ng ti&#7871;n tr&igrave;nh &#273;ang ch&#7841;y&hellip; ]]&gt;</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'canh-bao-ma-doc-trong-chuong-trinh-don-rac-may-tinh-cclearner', '', '', '2017-09-18 08:22:01', '2017-09-18 08:22:01', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/18/canh-bao-ma-doc-trong-chuong-trinh-don-rac-may-tinh-cclearner/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
