INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('825', '1', '2017-09-18 04:00:01', '2017-09-18 04:00:01', '<div readability=\"36\">\n<p>Thng tin nu trn c S TT&amp;TT H Ni cho bit trong bo co tnh hnh thc hin k hoch ng dng CNTT trong hot ng ca c quan nh TP.H Ni 9 thng v nhim v trng tm 3 thng cui nm.</p><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/ho_so_y_te.gif\" /></td></tr><tr><td readability=\"2\">\n<p>Phng Phc ng thuc qun Long Bin l mt trong 20 phng, x ca H Ni th im trin khai ng dng qun l h s sc khe in t cho ngi dn (Ngun nh: news.zing.vn)</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Trong k hoch ng dng CNTT trong hot ng ca c quan nh nc TP.H Ni nm 2017, cng vi vic xc nh y l nm t ph cn bn v CNTT, lnh o UBND Thnh ph cng t mc tiu y mnh trin khai v khai thc c hiu qu cc ng dng CNTT  xy dng chnh quyn in t, nng cao cht lng, hiu qu hot ng ca cc s, ban, ngnh, qun/huyn/th x, x/phng/th trn  phc v tt hn ngi dn v doanh nghip.</p>\n<p>Cng ti k hoch ny, mt trong nhng nhim v trng tm ca cng tc ng dng CNTT trong hot ng ca c quan nh nc TP.H Ni trong nm nay l ng dng CNTT, xy dng h thng thng tin trong cc lnh vc gio dc; t ai;  th; giao thng; vn ha th thao; du lch; qun l u t, ti chnh; qun l n th, khiu ni t co ton Thnh ph; v y t.</p>\n<p>nh gi v kt qu thc hin nhim v trng tm k trn trong cc thng u nm nay, i din S TT&amp;TT H Ni - c quan thng trc Ban ch o ng dng CNTT TP.H Ni cho bit, mt s h thng thng tin  c xy dng t quy m ln v c hiu qu vi s ngi tham gia h thng nhiu, s lng ngi truy cp ng v s lng h s c x l ln; cc phn mm, h thng thng tin khc ang c cc n v tip tc khai thc, s dng hiu qu  m bo khng lm gin on hot ng iu hnh, phc v cng dn, doanh nghip.</p>\n<p>C th, vi lnh vc gio dc, trn c s kt qu trin khai thnh cng h thng tuyn sinh u cp trc tuyn ca nm ngoi, trong nm nay, S GD&amp;T H Ni  trin khai ng dng ti 2.620 n v trng hc. n nay,  c hn 250.000 gia nh tham gia vi trn 6,2 triu lt truy cp vo Cng tuyn sinh u cp trc tuyn. T l h s ng k trc tuyn nm 2017 ca c 3 cp t 70,68% (khi mm non t 74,21%, khi lp 1 t 72,32% v khi lp 6 t 68,07%), tng gn 15% so vi nm ngoi.</p></div>', 'H Ni  thit lp gn 860.000 h s sc khe in t cho ngi dn', '<div><img src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/ho_so_y_te.gif\" width=\"130\" height=\"100\"> ICTnews - Vi&#7879;c tri&#7875;n khai &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng qu&#7843;n l&yacute; h&#7891; s&#417; s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917; cho ng&#432;&#7901;i d&acirc;n H&agrave; N&#7897;i &#273;&atilde; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c H&agrave; N&#7897;i th&iacute; &#273;i&#7875;m t&#7841;i 20 ph&#432;&#7901;ng/x&atilde; c&#7911;a c&aacute;c qu&#7853;n huy&#7879;n Long Bi&ecirc;n, Ba &#272;&igrave;nh, Nam T&#7915; Li&ecirc;m, Gia L&acirc;m, S&oacute;c S&#417;n; &#273;&atilde; kh&#7903;i t&#7841;o 1.436 t&agrave;i kho&#7843;n v&agrave; thi&#7871;t l&#7853;p 859.062 h&#7891; s&#417; &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917;. ]]&gt;</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ha-noi-da-thiet-lap-gan-860-000-ho-so-suc-khoe-dien-tu-cho-nguoi-dan', '', '', '2017-09-18 04:00:01', '2017-09-18 04:00:01', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/18/ha-noi-da-thiet-lap-gan-860-000-ho-so-suc-khoe-dien-tu-cho-nguoi-dan/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('826', '1', '2017-09-18 02:43:01', '2017-09-18 02:43:01', '<div readability=\"36\">\n<p>Hin nay, c nhiu n v cung cp dch v hp trc tuyn nhng gi c, chi ph cn cao v cha thc s ph hp vi nhm doanh nghip va v nh vn chim n 97% tng s doanh nghip ti Vit Nam. Trong khi , nhng dch v t cc n v nc ngoi i hi chi ph vn hnh ln. C th ni, cn kht v gii php hp trc tuyn ang l vn  chung ca nhm doanh nghip ny.</p><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/bai-2-ict-news-1-anh-mobifone.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p><strong>Th trng gii php hp trc tuyn  k tha ngi thiu</strong></p>\n<p>So vi nhng hi ngh trc tip, hp trc tuyn s gip cc doanh nghip gim thiu chi ph, thi gian, n gin ho cc quy trnh, th tc, nng cao hiu qu cuc hp. T , cc sn phm hi ngh truyn hnh cng ra i  p ng nhu cu hp trc tuyn ca cc doanh nghip. Tuy nhin, a phn cc sn phm ny u l sn phm chuyn dng t nc ngoi v mun s dng nhng sn phm ny th doanh nghip phi c cc thit b t tin i km, cng nh cn n i ng chuyn gia vn hnh. V d, vi mt chng trnh truyn hnh trc tip t 2 im cu, mi im cu cn s dng b thit b hi ngh truyn hnh c tr gi t 150 - 300 triu. Nh vy vi 2 im cu, chi ph cho ton b thit b ri vo khong 300 - 600 triu. Mt khc, yu cu v ng truyn, bng thng cng ko theo chi ph pht sinh hng thng khng nh. C th, mun s dng cc sn phm ny, cng ty phi trang b mt ng truyn Internet  mnh nh Leasedline, ISDN, E1 v chi ph  duy tr ng truyn ny ri vo khong t 10  14 triu ng/thng.</p>\n<p>Nh vy, c th thy, cc gii php hi ngh truyn hnh trn th trng Vit Nam vn cha linh hot v gi cn cao so vi nhu cu ca s ng. Cc gii php ny a phn hng n cc doanh nghip ln, doanh nghip c vn u t nc ngoi, thng xuyn phi t chc nhng cuc hp trc tuyn ln, quy m xuyn quc gia. Ngc li, vi nhm doanh nghip va v nh, tim lc ti chnh hn ch v cn gp nhiu kh khn trong vic ng dng cng ngh thng tin th s dng nhng sn phm hi ngh truyn hnh t  v cn s vn hnh phc tp ca i ng k thut l qu sc vi h.</p>\n<p>Do , cc doanh nghip va v nh ang rt cn mt gii php hp trc tuyn vi gi thnh hp l, ph hp vi nhu cu.</p>\n<p><strong>MegaMeeting  s la chn thng minh cho doanh nghip va v nh</strong></p><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/bai-2-ict-news-anh-2-mobifone.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div>', 'MegaMeeting: Gii php hp trc tuyn dnh cho doanh nghip va v nh', '<div><img src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/bai-2-ict-news-1-anh-mobifone.jpg\" width=\"130\" height=\"100\"> ICTnews - C&oacute; nhi&#7873;u &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; cung c&#7845;p d&#7883;ch v&#7909; h&#7885;p tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n nh&#432;ng gi&aacute; c&#7843;, chi ph&iacute; c&ograve;n cao v&agrave; ch&#432;a th&#7921;c s&#7921; ph&ugrave; h&#7907;p v&#7899;i nh&oacute;m doanh nghi&#7879;p v&#7915;a v&agrave; nh&#7887; v&#7889;n chi&#7871;m &#273;&#7871;n 97% t&#7893;ng s&#7889; doanh nghi&#7879;p t&#7841;i Vi&#7879;t Nam. ]]&gt;</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'megameeting-giai-phap-hop-truc-tuyen-danh-cho-doanh-nghiep-vua-va-nho', '', '', '2017-09-18 02:43:01', '2017-09-18 02:43:01', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/18/megameeting-giai-phap-hop-truc-tuyen-danh-cho-doanh-nghiep-vua-va-nho/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('827', '1', '2017-09-18 02:19:01', '2017-09-18 02:19:01', '<div readability=\"10\"><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/1.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td readability=\"1\">\n<p>Khi ASEAN cn y mnh hn na vic i ph vi nhng thch thc v an ninh mng.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Theo thng tin t Cng thng tin in t B Cng an, pht biu khai mc ti Hi ngh B trng cc nc ASEAN v an ninh mng din ra ngy 18/9/2017 ti Singapore, B trng B Truyn thng v Thng tin, B trng ph trch An ninh mng Singapore Yaacob Ibrahim nhn mnh, nm 2017 l thi im k nim 50 nm ASEAN hp tc v pht trin. ASEAN l t chc quc t  gp phn quan trng duy tr cho s an ninh, n nh trong khu vc.</p>\n<p>Cng ng ASEAN ang a ra mt hng i r rng, vi s hp tc ngy cng cht ch hn trong cng ng kinh t ASEAN v trong nhiu lnh vc khc.</p>\n<p>B trng Yaacob Ibrahim cho rng, trong qu kh ASEAN tng i ph vi nhng mi e da v hin nay ASEAN phi y mnh hn na vic i ph vi nhng thch thc v an ninh mng nhm thu c nhng li ch ti a t nn kinh t s trong tng lai.</p></div>', 'ASEAN sit cht an ninh mng bo v nn kinh t s', '<div><img src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/1.jpg\" width=\"130\" height=\"100\"> ICTnews - Theo B&#7897; tr&#432;&#7903;ng ph&#7909; tr&aacute;ch An ninh m&#7841;ng Singapore Yaacob Ibrahim, kh&#7889;i ASEAN c&#7847;n t&#259;ng c&#432;&#7901;ng &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o an ninh tr&ecirc;n kh&ocirc;ng gian m&#7841;ng, coi &#273;&acirc;y l&agrave; n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng cho s&#7921; ph&aacute;t tri&#7875;n c&#7911;a n&#7873;n kinh t&#7871; s&#7889;. ]]&gt;</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'asean-siet-chat-an-ninh-mang-bao-ve-nen-kinh-te-so', '', '', '2017-09-18 02:19:01', '2017-09-18 02:19:01', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/18/asean-siet-chat-an-ninh-mang-bao-ve-nen-kinh-te-so/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('828', '1', '2017-09-18 02:13:01', '2017-09-18 02:13:01', '<div readability=\"9\"><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/ccleaner-796x434.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td readability=\"0\">\n<p></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Cc nh nghin cu bo mt ca Cisco Talos pht hin my ch ti v c s dng bi Avast (cng ty s hu CCleaner)  b xm phm nhm pht tn m c bn trong CCleaner. Nhm cho bit trong mt khong thi gian nht nh, phin bn CCleaner 5.33 ca Avast cha loi m c a tng.</p>\n<p>Theo Avast, CCleaner c ti hn 2 t ln, khin n tr thnh mc tiu bo b ca hacker. C tc dng dn rc, chng trnh c thit k  xa b cc tp tin d tha, khng mong mun (crapware) trn my tnh v cung cp mt vi bin php bo v quyn ring t trn web. 2,27 triu ngi dng b nh hng t cuc tn cng v Avast tin rng  hnh ng kp thi, ngn chn s c gy hi cho ngi dng.</p></div>', 'Phn mm dn rc my tnh CCleaner b ci m c', '<div><img src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/ccleaner-796x434.jpg\" width=\"130\" height=\"100\"> ICTnews - Hacker &#273;&atilde; ph&aacute; v&#7905; b&#7843;o m&#7853;t c&#7911;a CCleaner &#273;&#7875; c&#7845;y m&atilde; &#273;&#7897;c v&agrave;o &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng v&agrave; ph&aacute;t t&aacute;n &#273;&#7871;n h&agrave;ng tri&#7879;u ng&#432;&#7901;i d&ugrave;ng. ]]&gt;</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'phan-mem-don-rac-may-tinh-ccleaner-bi-cai-ma-doc', '', '', '2017-09-18 02:13:01', '2017-09-18 02:13:01', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/18/phan-mem-don-rac-may-tinh-ccleaner-bi-cai-ma-doc/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('829', '1', '2017-09-18 01:03:01', '2017-09-18 01:03:01', '<div readability=\"21\">\n<p>Mi y khi trao i v v tn cng thay i giao din ng lot nhiu trang thng tin in t ca cc c quan, n v tnh B Ra - Vng Tu hi thng 2 nm nay, i din S Thng tin v Truyn thng (S TT&amp;TT) ca tnh tha nhn trng hp tn cng ny l do m ngun li thi ca cc n v ch qun trang thng tin in t m tiu biu l S Khoa hc v Cng ngh (S KH&amp;CN).</p>\n<p>T v tn cng  th S TT&amp;TT tnh B Ra - Vng Tu y mnh ch trng giao cng vic xy dng trang thng tin in t ca cc n v trn a bn cho Trung tm CNTT&amp;TT trc thuc S. Trung tm CNTT&amp;TT s c nhim v trin khai cc trang thng tin in t mi, ng thi r sot nhng trang no hin nay khng t yu cu th thay th.</p><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"z1-trung-tam-cntt-tt-ba-ria-vung-tau-mot-moi-xay-dung-trang-thong-tin-dien-tu-an-toan-thong-tin-mang.jpg\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/18/z1-trung-tam-cntt-tt-ba-ria-vung-tau-mot-moi-xay-dung-trang-thong-tin-dien-tu-an-toan-thong-tin-mang.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td readability=\"2\">\n<p>S TT&amp;TT tnh B Ra - Vng Tu ch trng giao cng vic xy dng trang thng tin in t ca cc n v trn a bn cho Trung tm CNTT&amp;TT  m bo an ton mng, nhng trang no hin nay khng t yu cu th c th thay th (nh minh ho: Internet).</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>V tn cng kh nghim trng nu trn din ra sng ngy 5/2/2017, khi 10 trang thng tin in t ca mt s c quan Nh nc tnh B Ra - Vng Tu b thay i giao din, bao gm: bantuyengiao.bari-vungtau.gov.vn, sokhcn.baria-vungtau.gov.vn, dost.baria-vungtau.gov.vn, dkqm.sotttt.baria-vungtau.gov.vn, daotaonghe.soldtbxh.baria-vungtau.gov.vn, egate.sotttt.baria-vungtau.gov.vn, doanhnghiep.baria-vungtau.gov.vn, tuoitre.baria-vungtau.gov.vn, kythuattdc.baria-vungtau.gov.vn v motcuacapxa.baria-vungtau.gov.vn. 10 trang web ny u c t hosting (lu tr) trn cng mt server (my ch).</p>\n<p>Trao i vi ICTnews, S TT&amp;TT tnh B Ra - Vng Tu cho bit Trung tm CNTT&amp;TT  cng cc i tc h tr v an ninh mng  khc phc, x l s c. L hng bo mt trn trang web S KH&amp;CN tnh B Ra - Vng Tu  c v ngay.</p>\n<p>Trung tm CNTT&amp;TT  tin hnh loi b cc tp tin m hacker a vo th mc cha m ngun cc website trn; ng thi phi hp cng c quan ch qun cc website v chuyn gia ca cc cng ty an ninh mng r sot m ngun, khc phc trit  cc l hng v tin hnh cp nht cc bn v li.</p></div>', 'BR-VT: Tp trung mt mi xy dng cc trang thng tin in t  m bo an ton mng', '<div><img src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/18/z1-trung-tam-cntt-tt-ba-ria-vung-tau-mot-moi-xay-dung-trang-thong-tin-dien-tu-an-toan-thong-tin-mang.jpg\" width=\"130\" height=\"100\"> ICTnews - S&#7903; TT&amp;TT t&#7881;nh B&agrave; R&#7883;a - V&#361;ng T&agrave;u ch&#7911; tr&#432;&#417;ng giao c&ocirc;ng vi&#7879;c x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng trang th&ocirc;ng tin &#273;i&#7879;n t&#7917; c&#7911;a c&aacute;c &#273;&#417;n v&#7883; tr&ecirc;n &#273;&#7883;a b&agrave;n cho Trung t&acirc;m CNTT&amp;TT &#273;&#7875; &#273;&#7843;m b&#7843;o an to&agrave;n m&#7841;ng, nh&#7919;ng trang n&agrave;o hi&#7879;n nay kh&ocirc;ng &#273;&#7841;t y&ecirc;u c&#7847;u th&igrave; c&oacute; th&#7875; thay th&#7871;. ]]&gt;</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'br-vt-tap-trung-mot-moi-xay-dung-cac-trang-thong-tin-dien-tu-de-dam-bao-an-toan-mang', '', '', '2017-09-18 01:03:01', '2017-09-18 01:03:01', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/18/br-vt-tap-trung-mot-moi-xay-dung-cac-trang-thong-tin-dien-tu-de-dam-bao-an-toan-mang/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('830', '1', '2017-09-18 00:54:01', '2017-09-18 00:54:01', '<div readability=\"29\">\n<p>D kin nm 2020,  n s hot ng cng thi im vi tuyn metro s 1 i vo hot ng.</p>\n<p>Hin n v u t tip tc lng nghe  kin ca cc s, ban, ngnh v chuyn gia, lm r nhng vn  cha c thng nht v gi Mt trn T quc thnh ph xem xt, t  mi lp d n kh thi.</p>\n<p>Trc , t nm 2010 UBND TP.HCM  chp thun  xut ca Cng ty C phn Cng ngh Tin Phong v d n t chc thu ph  t vo khu trung tm. Nm 2012,  n c trnh UBND TP.HCM.</p>\n<p>n cui nm 2016, UBND thnh ph yu cu S GTVT phi hp vi n v  xut chnh sa, hon thin  n.</p>\n<p>Tip n, u nm 2017, UBND thnh ph ng  ch trng cho php cng ty Tin Phong t cn i kinh ph  tip tc nghin cu, lp  xut d n Thu ph s dng ng b xe  t lu thng vo trung tm thnh ph gp phn gim n tc giao thng theo cc quy nh hin hnh v u t theo hnh thc i tc cng t.</p>\n<p>Vic  xut loi hp ng d n phi ph hp v gim ti a s tham gia t ngn sch thnh ph.</p>\n<p>Theo UBND TP.HCM, vic giao nghin cu lp  xut d n khng rng buc ch nh Cng ty C phn Cng ngh Tin Phong lm nh u t thc hin d n. Cc nh u t khc vn c quyn tham gia nghin cu lp  xut d n theo quy nh. Thnh ph s t chc la chn nh u t thc hin d n theo ng quy nh hin hnh.</p>\n<p>S Giao thng Vn ti c giao ch tr, phi hp vi cc S, ngnh c lin quan h tr, hng dn cng ty Tin Phong thc hin cc th tc theo quy nh trong qu trnh nghin cu lp  xut d n.</p>\n<p>Sau khi  xut d n c nghin cu hon thnh v giao np, UBND thnh ph  ngh y ban Mt trn T quc Vit Nam thnh ph mi cc nh khoa hc chuyn ngnh, cc chuyn gia tham gia gp , phn bin ni dung  xut d n  hon thin trc khi thm nh, ph duyt.</p></div>', 'TP.HCM cn nhc lp 36 trm khng dng thu ph  t vo ni   chng n tc', '<div><img src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/19/un-tac.jpg\" width=\"130\" height=\"100\"> ICTnews - TP.HCM &#273;ang xem x&eacute;t t&#7915; n&#259;m 2019 s&#7869; b&#7855;t &#273;&#7847;u x&acirc;y d&#7921;ng 36 tr&#7841;m thu ph&iacute; kh&ocirc;ng d&#7915;ng t&#7841;i khu v&#7921;c trung t&acirc;m TP.HCM, m&#7913;c thu t&#7915; 30.000 &ndash; 50.000 &#273;&#7891;ng t&ugrave;y lo&#7841;i xe &#273;&#7875; ch&#7889;ng &ugrave;n t&#7855;c gi&#7901; cao &#273;i&#7875;m. ]]&gt;</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tp-hcm-can-nhac-lap-36-tram-khong-dung-thu-phi-o-to-vao-noi-do-de-chong-un-tac', '', '', '2017-09-18 00:54:01', '2017-09-18 00:54:01', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/18/tp-hcm-can-nhac-lap-36-tram-khong-dung-thu-phi-o-to-vao-noi-do-de-chong-un-tac/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('831', '1', '2017-09-18 00:00:01', '2017-09-18 00:00:01', '<div readability=\"14\"><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/18/quangcanh.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td readability=\"1\">\n<p>Bui tp hun thu ht hn 300 i biu. nh: Tng cc Hi quan</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Thng tin trn Cng thng tin Tng cc Hi quan cho thy, trong nm va qua, lc lng CNTT ngnh Hi quan trong nm qua  n lc trin khai thnh cng mc tiu ca nm u tin trong k hoch ci cch, hin i ha giai on 2016-2020. Tuy nhin, nm nay nhim v t ra cng kh khn hn trong bi cnh hng ha XNK tng trng tr li i km vi nguy c gian ln, bun lu xuyn bin gii.</p>\n<p>Bn cnh , th gii ang bc vo cuc cch mng cng nghip ln th t v Chnh ph Vit Nam cng th hin cam kt mnh m v ci cch, to nn tng php l. C quan hi quan cng ang n lc ci cch, to thun li cho thng mi ng thi m bo an ninh, an ton.</p>\n<p>Hi ngh tp hun din ra trong 2 ngy 18 - 19/9 s i su vo nhng ni dung st vi cc k hoch,  n trng im ca ngnh Hi quan trong thi gian ti nh: Gim st hng ha ti cng bin, cng hng khng; trin khai C ch mt ca ng khng; tng cng dch v cng trc tuyn; kt ni C ch mt ca ASEAN khi tt c cc nc thnh vin  ph duyt Ngh nh th.</p></div>', 'CNTT hi quan tp trung vo gim st hng ha v c ch mt ca', '<div><img src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/18/quangcanh.jpg\" width=\"130\" height=\"100\"> ICTnews - T&#7841;i h&#7897;i ngh&#7883; t&#7853;p hu&#7845;n CNTT v&agrave; th&#7889;ng k&ecirc; ng&agrave;nh H&#7843;i quan v&#7915;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7893; ch&#7913;c, c&aacute;c c&aacute;n b&#7897; h&#7843;i quan &#273;&#432;&#7907;c t&#7853;p trung v&agrave;o c&aacute;c n&#7897;i dung nh&#432; gi&aacute;m s&aacute;t h&agrave;ng h&oacute;a; C&#417; ch&#7871; m&#7897;t c&#7917;a &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng kh&ocirc;ng; d&#7883;ch v&#7909; c&ocirc;ng tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n hay k&#7871;t n&#7889;i c&#417; ch&#7871; m&#7897;t c&#7917;a ASEAN. ]]&gt;</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cntt-hai-quan-tap-trung-vao-giam-sat-hang-hoa-va-co-che-mot-cua', '', '', '2017-09-18 00:00:01', '2017-09-18 00:00:01', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/18/cntt-hai-quan-tap-trung-vao-giam-sat-hang-hoa-va-co-che-mot-cua/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
