INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('880', '1', '2017-09-05 08:51:00', '2017-09-05 08:51:00', '<div><h2><span>Dn tr</span> To ra nhiu c hi, nhng Messi ri Icardi qu v duyn khin Argentina ti Venezuela cm ha 1-1 trn sn El Monumental (Buenos Aires)  lt trn th 16 vng loi World Cup 2018 khu vc Nam M.\n<br />\n<br /></h2><div>\n<p></p>\n<div data-back=\"E6E6FA\" data-border=\"999\" dir=\"center\" type=\"content\" w=\"90%\">\n<p><i><strong>Lt trn th 16 vng loi World Cup 2016 khu vc Nam M, ngy 6/9</strong></i></p>\n<p>3h00: Bolivia <strong>1-0</strong> Chile</p>\n<p>3h30: Colombia <strong>1-1</strong> Brazil</p>\n<p>4h00: Ecuador <strong>1-2</strong> Peru</p>\n<p>6h30: Argentina <strong>1-1</strong> Venezuela</p>\n<p>7h00: Paraguay <strong>1-2</strong> Uruguay</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Sau khi ha Uruguay 0-0  lt u trc, Argentina cn 3 im  gia nhp nhm 4 i dn u Nam M ti vng loi. Vic Colombia b cm ha, Chile tht bi l c hi khng th tt hn  Argentina bt ph.</p>\n<p>Tuy nhin, hng cng Argentina li chi v duyn  trn u ny khi lin tc b l c hi, nht l Icardi cn Messi chi qu m nht. Venezuela chi tnh to hn v c c bn thng dn trc nh cng Murrilo.</p>\n<p></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"Messi v ng i  c mt trn u kh v duyn\" photoid=\"64099c20-92a5-11e7-b146-8f070d792a38\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/argentina3-1504662459927.jpg\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/argentina3-1504662459927.jpg\" type=\"photo\" h=\"379\" w=\"634\" data-original=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/argentina3-1504662459927.jpg\"></div>\n<div>\n<p>Messi v ng i  c mt trn u kh v duyn</p></div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Icardi nhanh chng g ha 1-1 sau pha dt im p ngi Feltscher, nhng Argentina khng th ghi thm bn thng  hip 2. Vic Di Maria ri sn t qu sm l nguyn nhn khin Argentina chi thiu ng nt v b tc trc Venezuela.</p>\n<p>Sau 16 lt trn vng loi World Cup khu vc Nam M, Brazil ang dn u vi 37 im, tip theo l Uruguay (27 im), Comlombia (26 im) v Peru (24 im). Argentina (24 im) vn km Peru v hiu s v h s phi rt n lc rt nhiu  hai vng u cui cng, trong khi Chile (23 im) cng ang nui hy vng.</p>\n<p>Argentina tung ra sn i hnh thin v tn cng 3-4-3 vi Acosta, Banega, Pizarro, Di Maria  gia sn, Icardi  tin o cng Messi, Dybala trn hng cng. Ngay sau ting ci khai cuc, Argentina  y cao i hnh ln tn cng nhm tm kim bn thng.</p>\n<p>Ngay pht th 4, Mascherano thc hin pha chc khe chnh xc  Icardi thot xung, nhng tin o ny khng th nh bi th thnh Farinez trong tnh hung i mt y ng tic.</p>\n<p>5 pht sau, Di Maria i bng k thut bn cnh tri vt qua 2 cu th i phng ri cng ngang vo vng cm, nhng Icardi  khng th chm chn vo bng. Argentina ang p sn, cn Venezuela phng ng ton din.</p>\n<p></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"Venezuela m t s trc nh cng Murrillo\" photoid=\"634c3f90-92a5-11e7-9162-0b8089a3a3e1\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/argentina1-1504662459909.jpg\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/argentina1-1504662459909.jpg\" type=\"photo\" h=\"393\" w=\"634\" data-original=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/argentina1-1504662459909.jpg\"></div>\n<div>\n<p>Venezuela m t s trc nh cng Murrillo</p></div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Pht 12, Messi pht ng tn cng cho Di Maria cng ngang vo trong, mt ln na Icardi li dt im hng. 4 pht sau Banega quyt nh dt im tm xa, nhng bng chm ngi hu v Venezuela i ht ng bin ngang.</p>\n<p>Pht 22, t qu tt tm thp bn cnh tri ca Di Maria, Icardi lao vo  ni rt nhanh nhng th thnh Farinez  c mt phn x cu thua tuyt vi cho Venezuela. Chn thng khng mong mun khin Di Maria ri sn ngay pht 25.</p>\n<p>Nhng pht tip theo chng kin s b tc ca Argentina trc li  phng ng tiu cc ca Venezuela. C hi ng ch  cn li ca i ch nh l c st cng ca Messi b Farinez bay ngi cn ph  cui hip 1.</p>\n<p>Hip 2 mi bt u c 3 pht, bt ng  xy ra. Venezuela t chc pha phn cng nhanh v mt trung l, Murillo bng ln dt im tinh t h Romero trong tnh hung i mt, m t s trn u cho Venezuela.</p>\n<p>Tuy nhin n pht 55, Acuna n lc i bng ri cng ngang  Icardi dt im cn thnh, p chn Feltscher g ha 1-1 cho Argentina. Tin o ny  thnh cng, sau khi b l qu nhiu c hi  trn u ny.</p>\n<p></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"Icardi g ha 1-1 cho Argentina  hip 2\" photoid=\"63b20640-92a5-11e7-b146-8f070d792a38\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/argentina2-1504662459919.jpg\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/argentina2-1504662459919.jpg\" type=\"photo\" h=\"430\" w=\"634\" data-original=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/argentina2-1504662459919.jpg\"></div>\n<div>\n<p>Icardi g ha 1-1 cho Argentina  hip 2</p></div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Pht 60 Icardi  ng trong vng cm, nhng trng ti khng cho Argentina c hng qu pht n. Hng th Argentina c phen tht tim khi Rondon  pht nguy him khin th thnh Romero phi vt v bt bng.</p>\n<p>Pht 74, Acosta i bng to bo nhng c dt im ca anh li a bng i vt x ngang. Cc cu th Venezuela x l kh nhiu tiu xo trong thi u, khin Argentina gp nhiu b tc  trn u ny.</p>\n<p>n pht b gi cui cng, Messi n lc t ph ri chc khe  Pastore dt im nhanh, nhng Farinez  cu thua cho Venezuela. Argentina b cm ha 1-1 trn sn nh trc i th  b loi Venezuela.</p>\n<p><strong><i>i hnh thi u</i></strong></p>\n<p><strong>Argentina</strong>: Romero, Mascherano, Fazio, Otamendi, Dybala (Bendetto 62), Pizarro, Banega, Messi, Acosta, Icardi (Pastore 75), Di Maria (Acuna 25)</p>\n<p>Bn thng: Feltscher og 54</p>\n<p>Th vng: Banega, Acosta</p>\n<p><strong>Venezuela</strong>: Farinez, Garcia, Chancellor, Villanueva, Feltscher, Figuera, Moreno, Murillo, Herrera (Santos 77), Cordova, Rondon (Martinez 82)</p>\n<p>Bn thng: Murillo 51</p>\n<p>Th vng: Villanueva, Figuera, Chancellor, Herrera, Feltscher</p>\n<p>Trng ti: Roberto Tobar</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"\" photoid=\"72834a10-92a7-11e7-ad98-95c40de4dd6c\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/thumb_w/640/2017/screen-shot-2017-09-06-at-8-58-08-am-1504663349327.png\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/screen-shot-2017-09-06-at-8-58-08-am-1504663349327.png\" type=\"photo\" h=\"1002\" w=\"1064\" data-original=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/screen-shot-2017-09-06-at-8-58-08-am-1504663349327.png\"></div>\n<div></div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong>Thy Linh</strong></p>\n\n<div></div></div></div>', 'Messi v duyn, Argentina ha tht vng Venezuela', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'messi-vo-duyen-argentina-hoa-that-vong-venezuela', '', '', '2017-09-05 08:51:00', '2017-09-05 08:51:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/05/messi-vo-duyen-argentina-hoa-that-vong-venezuela/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
