n</p>\n<p><strong>Pht 21: </strong>Pedro thot xung b li hu v Arsenal  pha sau, tuy nhin c dt im ca tin o ngi Ty Ban Nha qu hin v khng th thng c Cech.</p>\n<p><strong>Pht 20:</strong> Kolasinac tung ra c st chn tri t u khu vc tri vng cm a, bng p t kh kh chu song Courtois vn  ngi chnh xc.</p>\n<p></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"Pha khng chin gia Azpilicueta (tri) v Welbeck (phi)\" photoid=\"8a699b30-9ba7-11e7-81b4-cf79a2d9c36d\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/thumb_w/640/2017/welbeck-1505652983534.jpg\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/welbeck-1505652983534.jpg\" type=\"photo\" h=\"800\" w=\"1199\" data-original=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/welbeck-1505652983534.jpg\"></div>\n<div>\n<p>Pha khng chin gia Azpilicueta (tri) v Welbeck (phi)</p></div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong>Pht 17:</strong> Bellerin cng bng t st bin ngang bn phi vo cho Lacazette p vo dt im. Mt c st chm cho rt nhanh ca tin o ngi Php, Courtois vn phn x tt</p>\n<p><strong>Pht 16: </strong>Arsenal ln bng tn cng rt nhuyn, Bellerin tt bng t bn phi vo cho Welbeck nh u  cch khung thnh ch chng 6m. ng tic, tin o ngi Anh li a bng i chch ct</p>\n<p><strong>Pht 14:</strong> Fabregas b phm li  bn phi ngang u vng cm a, trng ti cho Chelsea hng php li th, tuy nhin cc cu th i ch nh khng th gy nguy him cho Cech</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"Monreal (phi) c gng ngn cn Willian (tri) i bng\" photoid=\"c0e37ce0-9ba6-11e7-87c1-c5d43a753c95\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/thumb_w/640/2017/chelsea-1-1505652645808.jpg\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/chelsea-1-1505652645808.jpg\" type=\"photo\" h=\"800\" w=\"1200\" data-original=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/chelsea-1-1505652645808.jpg\"></div>\n<div>\n<p>Monreal (phi) c gng ngn cn Willian (tri) i bng</p></div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong>Pht 7</strong>: Moses t ra rt au n khi cu th ngi Nigeria c gng ngn cn Lacazette i bng. Moses  phi nh ti cc nhn vin y t chm sc, tuy nhin anh vn c th tip tc thi u.</p>\n<p><strong>Pht 5:</strong> Fabregas nhn bng kh trng tri  