INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('911', '1', '2017-09-16 20:09:00', '2017-09-16 20:09:00', '<div><h2><span>Dn tr</span> Ln u tin k t khi nm i Long An, HLV Nguyn Minh Phng gip i ny c chin thng, nh vt qua HA Gia Lai 2-1 ngay trn sn i phng. Nh thng l, cu th ni ting nht Vit Nam Nguyn Cng Phng li gy tht vng. </h2><div>\n<p></p>\n<div data-back=\"E6E6FA\" data-border=\"999\" dir=\"center\" type=\"content\" w=\"90%\">\n<p><strong>Lch thi u vng 18</strong></p>\n<p>Ngy 16/9</p>\n<p>17h, sn Bnh Dng: B.Bnh Dng <strong>31</strong> CLB H Ni</p>\n<p>17h, sn Cn Th: Cn Th <strong>21</strong> CLB TPHCM</p>\n<p>17h, sn Lch Tray: Hi Phng <strong>20</strong> Khnh Ho</p>\n<p>Ngy 17/9</p>\n<p>17h, sn Pleiku: HA Gia Lai <strong>12</strong> Long An</p>\n<p>17h, sn Thanh Ho: Thanh Ho <strong>23</strong> Qung Nam</p>\n<p>17h, sn Chi Lng: SHB  Nng <strong>01</strong> SL Ngh An</p>\n<p>18h, sn Thng Nht: Si Gn FC <strong>00</strong> Than Qung Ninh</p></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>D HA Gia Lai khng phi l i mnh, nhng h vn c nh gi cao hn Long An trong trn u ny, bi i bng min Ty Nam b ang trong cn khng hong, c bit l v mt tinh thn.</p>\n<p>Tuy nhin, khi u khng tt ca chnh HA Gia Lai trong nhng pht u trn, t mt tnh hung  lt li kh v duyn  tc ng rt ln n tinh thn ca i bn.</p>\n<p>Pht 10, pha treo bng khng c g l nguy him ca Thnh Trung bn pha Long An t pha cnh phi, li khin trung v Henrique Motta lng tng dng i a bng v li nh, biu khng cho Long An bn m t s 1-0.</p>\n<p></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"HA Gia Lai bt ng tht th trc Long An (nh: Nguyn nh)\" photoid=\"166108\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/thumb_w/640/2017/hagl-longan2-17-9-17-1505653369096.jpg\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/hagl-longan2-17-9-17-1505653369096.jpg\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/hagl-longan2-17-9-17-1505653369096.jpg\" w=\"2875\" h=\"2157\"></div>\n<div>HA Gia Lai bt ng tht th trc Long An (nh: Nguyn nh)</div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Sau bn thua, HA Gia Lai gia tng sc p, nhng cc t phi hp lt nht ca h trc khu vc cm a ca i khch khng   h khoang thng hng phng ng ca i bng trong tay HLV Nguyn Minh Phng.</p>\n<p>Tnh hung ng ch  nht m HA Gia Lai to ra trong hip 1 l pha st xa ca Cng Phng, nhng bng li i chch x ngang.</p>\n<p>Ngc li, Long An d khng gi nhiu bng, nhng h vn thi u kh t tin, nh c bn thng dn trc.</p>\n<p>Sang hip 2, Long An tip tc c bn thng khng lu sau khi hip u th nh bt u, cng t mt tnh hung ng nh khng c g l nguy him.</p>\n<p>Pht 52, ngoi binh Wander Luiz bn pha i bng min Ty Nam b dng sc mnh cn lt gia vng vy 3  4 hu v HA Gia Lai, trc khi tung c st xa him hc t khong cch 25m, lm b tay th mn T Vnh Li ca i bng ph ni, nng t s ln 2-0 cho Long An.</p>\n<p> u sn bn kia, mi cho n pht 59, nhng n lc tn cng ca HA Gia Lai mi c n p. Cu th vo sn t bng gh d b Vn Ton i bng n lc, chuyn cho Cng Phng, trc khi Cng Phng nh bng cho Minh Vng,  Minh Vng m bng h th thnh Tin Anh trong pha i mt, thu ngn cch bit xung cn 1-2 cho HA Gia Lai.</p>\n<p>Tuy nhin, chng  l cha   i bng ca bu c trnh c tht bi ngay trn sn nh.</p>\n<p>Ngc li, chin thng va nu gip Long An bng dy hy vng tr hng, cho d hy vng ny vn cn rt mong manh, do h vn b i th gn nht l Cn Th b xa n 9 im (Long An hin mi c 8 im, Cn Th c 17 im). y cng l chin thng u tin ca HLV Nguyn Minh Phng, k t ngy ng dn dt i bng min Ty Nam b. </p>\n<p></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"\" photoid=\"fa7cb510-9ba7-11e7-b64e-5167602a163f\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/thumb_w/640/2017/screen-shot-2017-09-17-at-7-58-36-pm-1505653140963.png\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/screen-shot-2017-09-17-at-7-58-36-pm-1505653140963.png\" type=\"photo\" h=\"742\" w=\"1340\" data-original=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/screen-shot-2017-09-17-at-7-58-36-pm-1505653140963.png\"></div>\n<div></div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p><strong>Kim in</strong></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"\" photoid=\"157946\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/logobanthethao-1504269342438.gif\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/logobanthethao-1504269342438.gif\" type=\"photo\" data-or