INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('920', '1', '2017-09-08 09:43:00', '2017-09-08 09:43:00', '<div><h2><span>Dn tr</span> Sau 2 gi 34 pht, ht ging s 1 Rafael Nadal  ginh chin thng 3-1 (4-6, 6-0, 6-3, 6-2) trc Martin Del Potro ti trn bn kt 2 M m rng 2017. Nh vy, Nadal v Kevin Anderson s l cp n nam tranh ti  trn chung kt nm nay. </h2><div>\n<p>Nadal tng tht bi trc Del Potro ti bn kt M m rng nm 2009, tay vt ngi Argentina sau  tin thng ti ngi v ch.  cng l chc v ch Grand Slam duy nht ca Del Potro. Trong khi  k t tht bi y, Nadal tri qua 14 chin thng lin tip  cc trn bn kt Grand Slam.</p>\n<p>Del Potro c nh gi l i th kh lng vi Nadal  trn bn kt hai M m rng 2017, bi trn con ng vo bn kt tay vt ngi Argentina  loi nhng tay vt ang c phong  tt nh Dominic Thiem hay Roger Federer.</p>\n<p></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"Nim vui chin thng ca Nadal\" photoid=\"59ef9540-9508-11e7-ac8f-119591f8c7fb\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/ap17252089220549-1504924899457.jpg\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/ap17252089220549-1504924899457.jpg\" type=\"photo\" h=\"396\" w=\"512\" data-original=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/ap17252089220549-1504924899457.jpg\"></div>\n<div>\n<p>Nim vui chin thng ca Nadal</p></div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>C hai tay vt u bt nhp vi trn bn kt vi phong  tt. Nadal c phn thm d i th khi thc hin chin thut bng bn v lin tc p tri i th, tuy nhin Del Potro khng gp nhiu kh khn.</p>\n<p>Nadal khng duy tr c s n nh, anh  i th b game 5 vt ln dn trc 3-2. Tay vt ht ging s 1 ngay lp tc thay i chin thut khi ch ng tn cng, nhng ch l  nhng game anh cm giao bng. Del Potro cm giao bng qu tt, Nadal khng c c hi phn cng v d bm ui rt n lc song vn  i th thng 6-4.</p>\n<p>S mnh m tip tc c Nadal duy tr khi bc vo set hai khi c quyn giao bng trc, Del Potro  mc sai lm  game hai khi  i th c break-point v ri b game thnh cng. S thng hoa ca Nadal c th hin r rt cng khin Del Potro lm vo tnh cnh kh khn. Sau khi mt break  game 4, tay vt ngi Argentina sm chp nhn bung set hai,  i th thng nhanh 6-0.</p>\n<p>p lc v tm l khin Del Potro cha th ct c chui game t hai. Tay vt ngi Argentina tip tc mt break  game u cm giao bng ca set ba. Nadal ko di chui game thng lin tip ln con s 9  dn trc 3-0  set ba. Game 4, nhng tng Del Potro vn thua khi m  i th dn trc ti 40-15, nhng anh  cu hai break-point thnh cng  chn bc tin ca Nadal.</p>\n<p></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"Del Potro ui dn trong cuc i u vi Nadal\" photoid=\"5f305710-9508-11e7-b38e-5912e5874422\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/ap17252064339819-1504924908106.jpg\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/ap17252064339819-1504924908106.jpg\" type=\"photo\" h=\"370\" w=\"512\" data-original=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/ap17252064339819-1504924908106.jpg\"></div>\n<div>\n<p>Del Potro ui dn trong cuc i u vi Nadal</p></div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Tuy nhin, cng ch cn mt break, Nadal cng  to nn bc ngot trn u bi tay vt ngi Ty Ban Nha thi u qu hiu qu. K t khi thay i chin thut, chi tn cng nhiu hn, s winner ca Nadal tng vt, trong khi s li t nh hng rt t khi xut hin.</p>\n<p>Thng set ba vi t s 6-3, Nadal ung dung bc vo set bn. Del Potro sa st v tinh thn nn khng cn thi u mnh m, chnh xc c nh trong giai on u. Set bn, ht ging s 24 c quyn giao bng trc nhng anh ch lm tt nhim v  game u, Del Potro mt game ba v nm, qua   Nadal vt ln dn trc ti 5-1. Nadal thng d dng 6-2  set ny, qua  ginh quyn vo chung kt gp Kevin Anderson. Tay vt ngi Nam Phi thng Carreno-Busta 3-1  trn bn kt u tin (4-6, 7-5, 6-3, 6-4).</p>\n<p>Thng k sau trn cho thy, Nadal c 5 ace v hai li kp, anh c ti 45 winner v 20 li t nh hng. Trong set u, Nadal ch c 9 winner v 10 li t nh hng, so snh gia nhng ch s ny mi thy c s thay i qu mnh m ca Nadal. Trong khi Nadal i ln th Del Potro i xung,  set u tay vt ngi Argentina c 14 winner, nh hng 14 li, nhng c trn anh ch c 22 winner v 40 li t nh hng.</p>\n<p><strong>P.S</strong></p>\n\n<div></div></div></div>', '\"Ra hn\" trc Del Potro, Nadal ginh v vo chung kt', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'rua-han-truoc-del-potro-nadal-gianh-ve-vao-chun