INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('928', '1', '2017-09-06 11:18:00', '2017-09-06 11:18:00', '<div><h2><span>Dn tr</span> Vi chin thng 3-1 trc Federer (7-5, 3-6, 7-6, 6-4), Del Potro  ginh quyn vo bn kt M m rng 2017. Anh s i u vi ht ging s 1 Rafael Nadal  ginh tm v vo chung kt.\n<br /></h2><div>\n<p>Mt trn bn kt gia hai tay vt xut sc hng u th gii hin nay, Federer v Nadal  khng th din ra  M m rng 2017. Trong khi tay vt s 1 th gii Rafael Nadal d dng ginh chin thng trc Andrey Rublev  ginh v vo bn kt th Roger Federer  khng th vt qua Del Potro.</p>\n<p>Sau 2 gi 54 pht tranh ti, Del Potro ginh chin thng 3-1 (7-5, 3-6, 7-6, 6-4). Mt cuc chin kh quyt lit khi c hai u thi u vi phong  tt, Del Potro vt qua c nhng thi khc quyt nh v ginh tm v i tip.</p>\n<p></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"Del Potro ang tr li vi nhng trn cu nh cao\" photoid=\"194fd2b0-9383-11e7-bf49-518afd19be20\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/ap17250150496473-1504757715263.jpg\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/ap17250150496473-1504757715263.jpg\" type=\"photo\" h=\"315\" w=\"512\" data-original=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/ap17250150496473-1504757715263.jpg\"></div>\n<div>\n<p>Del Potro ang tr li vi nhng trn cu nh cao</p></div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Chin thng ca tay vt ca Del Potro c cht ngc nhin, nhng khng phi sc. Tay vt ngi Argentina tng tim cn tp 4 th gii, anh cng tng v ch US Open. Tuy nhin do chn thng di hn, nn sau khi tr li thi u, Del Potro vn cha th tm c phong  nh cao trong gn hai nm qua.</p>\n<p>Trc M m rng 2017, Federer v Del Potro tng gp nhau mt ln trong nm nay. Ti Miami Open thng ba va qua, Federer trn ng tin ti ngi v ch  h gc i th ngi Argentina vi t s 2-0.</p>\n<p>Federer chi khng ti  trn u ny, anh c 17 ace, mc ba li kp. T l ginh im trung bnh khi c quyn giao bng ca FedEx t 66% (91/137), ngoi ra anh c 60 winner, 41 li t nh hng. Trong khi , Del Potro c 12 ace, hai li kp. Tay vt ngi Argentina c t l ginh im khi c quyn giao bng t 71%, 48 winner v 32 li t nh hng.</p>\n<p>Trc khi tin ti gp Federer, Del Potro h gc Bautista-Agut  vng bn v c nh gi s l thch thc ln i vi FedEx. Set u tin, Federer cm giao bng trc, hai tay vt to nn mt cuc bm ui quyt lit khi u qun l rt tt cc game cm giao bng. Bc ngot din ra  game 11 khi Del Potro b game ri tin ti chin thng 7-5.</p>\n<p></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img alt=\"Federer  khng th vo bn kt gii Grand Slam th ba trong nm sau khi v ch Australian Open v Wimbledon (khng tham d Roland Garros)\" photoid=\"2266a2c0-9383-11e7-bf49-518afd19be20\" src=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/ap17250095809030-1504757730647.jpg\" rel=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/ap17250095809030-1504757730647.jpg\" type=\"photo\" h=\"326\" w=\"512\" data-original=\"https://dantricdn.com/2017/ap17250095809030-1504757730647.jpg\"></div>\n<div>\n<p>Federer  khng th vo bn kt gii Grand Slam th ba trong nm sau khi v ch Australian Open v Wimbledon (khng tham d Roland Garros)</p></div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p>Set hai, sau khi Federer b game bn  vt ln dn trc 3-1, tay vt ngi Thy S  khng cho i th c hi i game. Federer thng 6-3  set hai v qun bnh t s 1-1.</p>\n<p>Del Potro khi u tt  set ba khi b game thnh cng game hai. Tuy nhin, tay vt ngi Argentina khng th bo ton cc game cm giao bng trc s tn cng mnh m ca i th. Federer i li break  game by  xa c hi thng nhanh ca i phng. Hai tay vt  chi rt tt trong cc game cm giao bng sau , y set u vo vn quyt thng.</p>\n<p>Kh nng bo v im ca Federer v Del Potro  lot tie-break u ti. Tay vt ngi Thy S lin tc mt 1 im  nhng lot 2 pha giao bng, Del Potro cng vy. Tuy nhin  giai on cui, Del Potro  chi tt hn  c chin thng 10-8.</p>\n<p>Federer cm giao bng trc  set bn, Del Potro bm ui rt tt. Tay vt ngi Thy S chi khng tt  game 5 v b b game. Del Potro bin break ny tr thnh bc ngot ca game u, cm giao bng tt thm ba game, tay vt ngi Argentina thng 6-4 v kt thc trn u.</p>\n<p><strong>P.S</strong></p>\n\n<div></div></div></div>', 'nh bi Federer, Del Potro vo bn kt gp Nadal', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'danh-bai-federer-del-potro-vao-ban-ket-gap-nadal', '', '', '2017-09-06 11:18:00', '2017-09-06 11:18:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/06/danh-bai-federer-del-potro-vao-ban-ket-gap-nadal/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
