INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1391', '1', '2017-09-20 00:48:18', '2017-09-20 00:48:18', '<div><h2>Tng thng M ku gi loi b nhng mi e do n ch quyn  Bin ng, trong bi pht biu u tin ti i Hi ng Lin Hp Quc. </h2><article><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"Tng thng M Donald Trump hm 19/9 pht biu ti i Hi ng Lin Hp Quc  New York. nh: Reuters.\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/20/trump-un-2343-1505868455.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Tng thng M Donald Trump hm 19/9 pht biu ti i Hi ng Lin Hp Quc  New York. nh: <em>Reuters</em>.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><span>Tng thng Donald Trump c bnh lun r rng nhm vo Nga v Trung Quc, khi cho rng</span><span> phi \"loi b nhng mi e da n ch quyn\", t Ukraine ti Bin ng, theo <em>AFP</em>. </span></p>\n<p>\"Chng ta phi duy tr ng h lut php, tn trng cc bin gii v tn trng vn ho, v s can d ho bnh m nhng iu ny cho php\", ng ni trc i Hi ng gm 193 thnh vin. <span>\"V nh mong mun ca nhng ngi sng lp c quan ny, chng ta phi lm vic cng nhau, cng nhau i u vi nhng k e do chng ta bng s hn lon, ln xn v ni khip s\".</span></p>\n<p>Trung Quc n phng i ch quyn vi hu ht din tch Bin ng, ni c lng hng ha tr gi 5 nghn t USD lu thng mi nm, chng ln ln tuyn b ch quyn ca cc nc ng Nam , trong  c Vit Nam. Nc ny cn ngang nhin xy dng phi php 7 o nhn to ti cc  thuc qun o Trng Sa ca Vit Nam. </p>\n<p>M tuyn b khng ng v bn no trong tranh chp Bin ng nhng nhn mnh quyn thc hin cc chin dch t do hng hi. Chnh quyn Tng thng Trump  thc hin ba chin dch p st o nhn to Trung Quc xy tri php  Trng Sa k t thng 5. </p>\n<p><em>Wall Street Journal</em> u thng ny a tin B Ch huy Thi Bnh Dng ca M c k hoch thc hin cc cuc tun tra t do hng hi ti Bin ng hai n ba ln trong vi thng ti. <span>K hoch tun tra mi c cho l nhm th hin thi  nht qun hn trc vic Trung Quc tuyn b ch quyn phi php  Bin ng. Mt s cuc tun tra s khng ch s dng tu chin t hi qun M m cn c th iu ng c my bay qun s.</span></p>\n<p><strong>Trng Gip</strong></p></article></div>', 'Trump ln n nhng mi e da ch quyn  Bin ng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'trump-len-an-nhung-moi-de-doa-chu-quyen-o-bien-dong', '', '', '2017-09-20 00:48:18', '2017-09-20 00:48:18', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/trump-len-an-nhung-moi-de-doa-chu-quyen-o-bien-dong/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1392', '1', '2017-09-19 23:24:57', '2017-09-19 23:24:57', '<div><h2>Trn ng t mnh 7,1  rung chuyn Mexico, lm nhiu nh sp, t nht 248 ngi thit mng.</h2><article>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div data-component=\"true\" data-component-type=\"video\" data-component-value=\"167381\" data-component-typevideo=\"2\"></div></div></div>\n<p>Hng nghn ngi chy ra ng trong hong lon v hng triu ngi mt in khi trn ng t xy ra vo khong tra 19/9, theo <em>Reuters</em>. <span>ng t xy ra vo khong 13h, cch th  Mexico khong 160 km. N c xc nh mnh 7,1 , gy rung lc mnh, ko di  th , theo </span><em>New York Times. </em></p>\n<p>t nht 248 ngi cht trn khp Mexico, theo <em>Guardian</em>. <span>Hn 40 to nh v cc cng trnh khc b sp  th  Mexico, trong  c t nht hai trng hc. </span></p>\n<p><span>Talia Hernandez, 28 tui, cho bit khi ng t xy ra, c ang  tng hai mt to nh. C to nh rung chuyn. C chy vi xung cu thang khi n va  sp xung. C may mn thot cht v ch b thng  chn. \"Khng th tin c l ti cn sng\", Hernandez ni trong hong ht, nc mt gin gia, trong khi cc nhn vin y t gip ly cc mnh knh v ra khi chn c.</span></p>\n<p><span>ng Jorge Ortiz Diaz, 66 tui, mt ngi tham gia cu h, cho bit trn ng t xy ra \"nh th Cha ni gin vi chng ti\".</span></p>\n<p>y l trn ng t lm nhiu ngi cht nht  Mexico t nm 1985. Thm ho xy ra cng vo ngy 19/9, lm hng nghn ngi thit mng. Trn ng t mi nht xy ra cha y hai tun sau trn mnh 8,1   pha nam nc ny khin 90 ngi cht. </p><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"V tr tm chn hai trn ng t\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/20/earthquake-4672-1505865113.png\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>V tr tm chn hai trn ng t hm 7 v 19/9.  ho: <em>NewYorkTimes</em>. </p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><span>ng Paul Earle, nh a cht hc ca Cc Kho st a cht M, cho rng cn qu sm  ni liu c bt c mi lin h no gia hai trn ng t hay khng. D trn u tin mnh hn nhiu, trn hm 19/9  gn th  Mexico hn, gy thit hi ln hn. </span></p>\n<p><span>Tng thng Mexico Enrique Pena Nieto ng thng ip trn Twitter, cho bit ng  tr li th . Trc , ng ang trn ng n Oaxaca vo thi im xy ra ng t. U ban cu tr khn cp quc gia s hp khi Tng thng c mt  nh gi tnh hnh v phi hp cc n lc cu h. </span></p>\n<p>\n<div data-component=\"true\" data-component-type=\"video\" data-component-value=\"167383\" data-component-typevideo=\"2\"></div></p>\n<p>Nh trc tng mng trong ng t. Video: <em>Twitter</em>.</p>\n<p><strong>Khnh Lynh</strong></p></article></div>', 'ng t mnh rung chuyn Mexico, hn 240 ngi cht', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dong-dat-manh-rung-chuyen-mexico-hon-240-nguoi-chet', '', '', '2017-09-19 23:24:57', '2017-09-19 23:24:57', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/dong-dat-manh-rung-chuyen-mexico-hon-240-nguoi-chet/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
