INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1396', '1', '2017-09-19 15:00:00', '2017-09-19 15:00:00', '<div><h2>Mt trc thng tn cng Ka-52 ca khng qun Nga gp li k thut, t phng rocket vo ngi theo di cuc tp trn Zapad 2017.</h2><article>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div data-component=\"true\" data-component-type=\"video\" data-component-value=\"167345\" data-component-typevideo=\"2\"></div></div>\n<p> Khonh khc chic Ka-52 b \"cp c\"</p></div>\n<p>Hai ngi nhp vin trong tnh trng nguy kch sau khi trng rocket t mt trc thng tn cng Ka-52 trong cuc tp trn Zapad 2017. V vic xy ra hm 18/9  trng bn Luzhsky gn thnh ph Saint Petersburg, Nga, <em>Moscow Times</em> a tin.</p>\n<p>Ngun tin giu tn ca trang tin <em>66.ru </em>cho bit chic Ka-52  gp s c \"cp c\" khi bay   cao thp, khin cc qu rocket t khai ha. \"t nht hai t b chy, hai ngi b thng nng phi nhp vin, nhiu kh nng h u l nh bo\", ngun tin ny tit l. B Quc phng Nga cha a ra bnh lun v v vic, chi cho bit c hai trc thng tn cng tham gia ni dung trinh st v ym tr mt t trong tp trn Zapad 2017.</p>\n<p>Cuc tp trn chung Zapad-2017 gia Nga v Belarus din ra t ngy 14 n 20/9, c cho l c hi  Nga th nghim nhiu khi nim chin thut mi, trong  c nhng chin thut c rt ra t kinh nghim  Syria. B Quc phng Belarus cho bit lc lng tham gia tp trn gm 138 xe tng, 231 xe thit gip, 241 h thng pho v tn la n o chin thut, cng 40 my bay chin u lm nhim v tun tra cnh gii trn khng.</p>\n<p><strong>T Qunh</strong></p></article></div>', 'Trc thng Nga trc trc, bn rocket trng ngi xem tp trn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'truc-thang-nga-truc-trac-ban-rocket-trung-nguoi-xem-tap-tran', '', '', '2017-09-19 15:00:00', '2017-09-19 15:00:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/truc-thang-nga-truc-trac-ban-rocket-trung-nguoi-xem-tap-tran/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1397', '1', '2017-09-19 14:23:00', '2017-09-19 14:23:00', '<div><h2>Mt hm i tu chin Australia ang di chuyn v pha Bin ng trong mt ng thi nhm ph trng sc mnh ti khu vc.</h2><article><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"australia-dieu-6-tau-chien-toi-bien-dong-tap-tran\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/19/8332014e04ac7e3c251678370d03ec-4890-8613-1505813096.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Nhm tu tc chin ca Australia ang di chuyn ti Bin ng. nh: <em>Daily Telegraph.</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Chnh ph Australia  iu hm i gm 6 tu chin tham gia gia cc cuc tp trn ti Bin ng, nhng vn cha a ra quyt nh cui cng v vic c trin khai nhm tu i vo cc khu vc tranh chp  vng bin ny hay khng, <em>Daily Telegraph</em> hm nay a tin.</p>\n<p>y l mt phn trong k hoch tp trn ko di hai thng ca Canberra ti khu vc n  Dng - Thi Bnh Dng, k hoch trin khai nhm tu chin thc hin nhim v ln nht ca nc ny trong 30 nm qua.</p>\n<p><span>Theo Daily Telegraph, cc quan chc cp cao Australia gn y thng xuyn hp bn v la chn chin lc  khu vc ty Thi Bnh Dng cng nh quan im ca nc ny v tranh chp lnh th ti Bin ng. </span><span>Cc cuc hp tuy cha lm r nhng hot ng trin khai hi qun c th, gm chin dch ln ny, nhng  xc nh chin lc ca Canberra trong khu vc.</span></p>\n<p>ng thi ca hi qun Australia din ra trong bi cnh Th tng Malcolm Turnbull ang ku gi Trung Quc tng cng sc sp  ngn chn chng trnh tn la n o ca Triu Tin v ngay lp tc vp phi s ch trch kch lit ca truyn thng Bc Kinh.</p>\n<p>T People\'s Daily cho rng cho rng Australia ang tm cch \"bao vy\" Trung Quc thng qua cc cuc tp trn ti khu vc. Tuy nhin, mt ngun tin cp cao t Canberra cho bit cuc tp trn  c ln k hoch t 12 thng trc, b Bc Kinh nhn nhn nh mt cch gy p lc vi Trung Quc trong bi cnh cng thng Triu Tin.</p>\n<p><span>Chuyn gia Peter Jennings, gim c iu hnh ca vin Chnh sch Chin lc Australia nhn nh p lc ca ng Turnbull i vi Trung Quc l qu r rng, v tht \"nc ci\" khi cho rng Canberra ang bao vy Bc Kinh.</span></p>\n<p><span>Ngy 18/9, B trng Quc phng Australia Marise Payne nhn mnh nhm 6 tu chin ny </span><span>s chng minh kh nng tc chin ca hi qun nc ny trong cc lnh vc nh </span><span>chng tu ngm cho n h tr nhn o v cu tr thin tai.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span>Nguyn Hong</span></strong></p></article></div>', 'Australia iu 6 tu chin ti Bin ng tp trn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'australia-dieu-6-tau-chien-toi-bien-dong-tap-tran', '', '', '2017-09-19 14:23:00', '2017-09-19 14:23:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/australia-dieu-6-tau-chien-toi-bien-dong-tap-tran/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
