INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1399', '1', '2017-09-19 14:12:18', '2017-09-19 14:12:18', '<div><h2>T Lin Hp Quc, Tng thng M cnh bo s buc phi hy dit Triu Tin hon ton nu nc ny khng li bc trc thch thc ht nhn. </h2><article>\n<div>\n<div data-component=\"true\" data-component-type=\"video\" data-component-value=\"167418\" data-component-typevideo=\"2\"></div></div>\n<p>\"M c sc mnh v s kin nhn ln lao, nhng nu b buc phi bo v bn thn hoc cc ng minh, chng ti s khng c la chn no ngoi tr hu dit hon ton Triu Tin\", <em>AFP</em> dn li Tng thng Trump hm nay ni trong bi pht biu u tin ca ng ti i Hi ng Lin Hp Quc. </p>\n<p>\"Ngi Tn la ang trong mt nhim v t st vi ng v ch  ca ng\", ng Trump ni,  cp n bit danh mi ng dnh cho lnh o Kim Jong-un. \"M  chun b sn sng v c th, nhng hy vng iu ny s khng cn thit\". </p>\n<p>Nhng ting x xo r ln khp khn phng i Hi ng khi ng Trump pht li cnh bo cng rn nht vi Triu Tin, theo <em>Reuters</em>. Cc v phng tn la n o v th ht nhn ca nc ny lm th gii lo s. </p>\n<p>Mt nh ngoi giao Triu Tin vn ngi ti hng gh u ca phi on trong bi pht biu ca ng Trump, phi on ca Triu Tin ti Lin Hp Quc cho bit. Phi on t chi bnh lun ngay lp tc v bi pht biu ca ng. </p>\n<p>Trong ln u tin xut hin ti cuc hp thng nin ca cc lnh o th gii, Tng thng M s dng bi pht biu di 41 pht cn  nhm vo tham vng ht nhn Iran, s nh hng trong khu vc, nn dn ch  Venezuela v mi e do ca nhng k Hi gio cc oan. ng cng ch trch chnh ph Cuba. </p>\n<p>Nhng ngn t mnh m nht nhm vo Triu Tin. ng hi thc cc nc thnh vin Lin Hp Quc phi hp  c lp chnh quyn ng Kim cho ti khi nc ny chm dt hnh vi \"th ch\". </p>\n<p>ng cho rng vic Triu Tin theo ui v kh ht nhn v tn la n o \"e do ton b th gii bng ci gi khng th tng tng ni ca mng sng con ngi\". </p>\n<p>Trong tuyn b c th nhm m ch Trung Quc, i tc thng mi ln ca Triu Tin, ng Trump cho rng: \"Tht l mt iu xc phm khi mt s nc khng ch giao thng vi ch  ny m cn cung cp v kh, h tr v hu thun ti chnh cho mt t nc y th gii vo tnh trng nguy him bng xung t ht nhn\".</p><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"trump-canh-bao-my-co-the-phai-huy-diet-hoan-toan-trieu-tien\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/19/trump-2-4821-1505832196.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Tng thng M Donald Trump pht biu ti i Hi ng Lin Hp Quc. nh: <em>Reuters</em>.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>ng Trump cng khng  cp ch danh Nga hay Trung Quc, nhng c bnh lun r rng nhm vo Moscow v Bc Kinh, theo <em>AFP</em>. ng cho rng phi loi b nhng mi e do n ch quyn, t Ukraine ti Bin ng. \"Chng ta phi duy tr ng h lut php, tn trng cc bin gii v tn trng vn ho, v s can d ho bnh m nhng iu ny cho php\". </p>\n<p>ng Trump, ngi bc vo Nh Trng cch y 8 thng, cng ni vi cc lnh o th gii ti t chc ton cu gm 193 thnh vin rng M khng tm cch p t  ch ca mnh ln cc nc khc v s tn trng ch quyn cc nc. \"Ti s bo v li ch ca M trn tt c\", ng ni. \"Nhng khi thc hin ngha v vi cc nc khc, chng ti cng nhn thy tt c cc bn u c li ch khi tm kim mt tng lai, trong  tt c cc nc c ch quyn, thnh vng v an ton\". </p>\n<p>Bi pht biu nhn c phn ng tri chiu t cc lnh o th gii. Ngoi trng Thu in <span>Margot Wallstrom khoanh tay trong bi pht biu. \"y l bi pht biu sai lm, sai lm v thi im v sai lm v i tng khn gi\", b Wallstrom sau  ni vi <em>BBC</em>. </span></p>\n<p><span>Ngoi trng Iran Javad Zarif ng thng ip trn Twitter: \"Bi pht biu y hn th xun ngc ca ng Trump thuc v thi Trung c, khng phi ti Lin Hp Quc vo th k 21, n khng ng  p li\". </span></p>\n<p>Trong khi , Th tng Israel Benjamin Netanyahu cng phi on v tay hoan h bi pht biu. ng <span>Netanyahu </span><span>ca ngi y l bi din vn \"to bo v dng cm nht\" ng tng nghe ti cuc hp thng nin ca cc lnh o v nh ngoi giao th gii.</span></p>\n<p><strong>Trng Gip</strong></p></article></div>', 'Trump cnh bo M c th phi \'hy dit hon ton\' Triu Tin', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'trump-canh-bao-my-co-the-phai-huy-diet-hoan-toan-trieu-tien', '', '', '2017-09-19 14:12:18', '2017-09-19 14:12:18', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/trump-canh-bao-my-co-the-phai-huy-diet-hoan-toan-trieu-tien/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
