INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1404', '1', '2017-09-20 07:03:30', '2017-09-20 07:03:30', '<div><h2>Lnh o Chnh ph xung th st c s vt cht Hng phim truyn Vit Nam, lng nghe cc phn nh t ngh s.</h2><article>\n<p>Sng 20/9, Ph th tng V c am  th st Hng phim truyn Vit Nam (VFS). ng gp mt s ngh s trong khun vin hng phim nh nh b<span>in kch Nguyn Xun Thnh, </span><span>ha s Thnh Chng..., v tr chuyn vi ngi dn xung quanh.</span></p>\n<p><span>Theo cc ngh s, h khng bit trc thng tin Ph th tng s n; lnh o Chnh ph i vng cng sau v gp nhn vin bo v, lng nghe phn nh v i sng kh khn ca cc nhn vin ny sau khi hng phim c phn ho...</span></p>\n<p>Mt ngh s ni rt vui trc vic Ph th tng trc tip xung tip xc, nm bt thng tin t nhng ngi lao ng gn b lu nm vi VFS. \"<span>V n o ti VFS nhng ngy qua thu ht s ch  ca d lun. Nhiu ngh s tn tui  vit vo l n ku cu gi Hi in nh ngy 9/9, nu thc trng ca Hng phim lng ly mt thi sau c phn ha. Chng ti mong cp c thm quyn quan tm, sm gii quyt cc vn  lin quan\", ngh s ny chia s.</span></p><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"pho-thu-tuong-thi-sat-hang-phim-truyen-viet-nam\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/20/20170920110312-3-9281-1505890989.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Ph th tng V c am gp cc ngh s sng 20/9. nh: <em>VFS</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Theo ngun tin t Vn phng Chnh ph, sau cuc th st sng nay, d kin vo chiu mai (21/9), Ph th tng V c am s ch tr cuc lm vic vi cc b ngnh lin quan v i din VFS.</p>\n<p><span>Hng Phim truyn Vit Nam l hng phim nh nc c thnh lp nm 1953, trc thuc B Vn ha, Th thao v Du Lch. Lch s tn ti ca hng gn lin vi dng phim cch mng v ngh thut.</span></p>\n<p>Vic c phn ho VFS thi gian qua vng phi nhng lm xm khi thng hiu gn 60 nm ca hng c xc nh bng 0 ng. Thc t ny khin nhiu ngh s in nh k cu rt bc xc v t nm ngoi  cng k vo bn  ngh dng ngay vic c phn ho i vi VFS.</p>\n<p>Trc , thng 12/2016, Th tng  c yu cu B Vn ha, Th thao & Du lch r sot li ton b qu trnh c phn ha VFS. ng thi B ny c giao ch tr, phi hp vi cc b lin quan tnh ton xc nh gi tr thng hiu cn c vo yu t lch s, b dy truyn thng ca hng phim, nhm iu chnh tng gi tr phn vn Nh nc khi chnh thc chuyn thnh cng ty c phn.</p>\n<p>Th tng khi  cng yu cu B Ti chnh nghin cu, sa i quy nh  bn u gi quyn s dng t ti cc khu t vng do doanh nghip Nh nc nm gi  bo m st gi th trng, trnh tht thot ti sn Nh nc...</p></article></div>', 'Ph th tng th st Hng phim truyn Vit Nam', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'pho-thu-tuong-thi-sat-hang-phim-truyen-viet-nam', '', '', '2017-09-20 07:03:30', '2017-09-20 07:03:30', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/pho-thu-tuong-thi-sat-hang-phim-truyen-viet-nam/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
