INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1408', '1', '2017-09-20 03:51:28', '2017-09-20 03:51:28', '<div><h2>c chm sc hn mt thng ti trung tm cu h  Cc Phng (Ninh Bnh), 10 con cy  iu kin c ti th.</h2><article>\n<p>Trung tm Nghin cu v Bo tn ng vt hoang d (SVW), Vn quc gia Cc Phng va ti th thnh cng 10 con cy ti mt a im an ton, trong  c bn con cy vi mc <em>(Paguma larvata)</em><span>, </span><span>su cy vi hng </span><em>(Paradoxurus hermaphroditus)</em><span>. S cy ny c SVW tip nhn v cu h t Cng an tnh Ha Bnh vo u thng 8.</span></p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div data-component=\"true\" data-component-type=\"video\" data-component-value=\"167394\" data-component-typevideo=\"2\"></div></div>\n<p><em>Trung tm SVW thc hin ti th cy  a im an ton. </em></p></div>\n<p><span>Cy vi mc v cy vi hng l hai trong 11 loi cy phn b  Vit Nam, ang c  xut bo v theo theo ngh nh 32/2006/N-CP ca Th tng v qun l thc vt rng, ng vt rng nguy cp, qu, him</span><span>. C hai loi u ang i mt vi nn sn bt qu mc ly tht, da v lm vt cnh. Vic suy gim din tch t rng v ph hy mi trng sng cng e da n phn b ca loi.</span></p>\n<p><span>Theo ng Nguyn Vn Thi, gim c SVW, hai loi cy ny ang c nhn nui v mc ch thng mi. Rt nhiu nh hng li dng hnh thc ny  bun bn bt hp php. Khch n n s c qung co l ng vt hoang d bt trong rng, nhng khi c quan chc nng n kim tra, h li ni l t cc tri nui. iu</span><span> ny dn n nhng kh khn trong vic thc thi php lut. </span></p>\n<p><span>Ngoi ra, rt nhiu cy vi hng b bt ngoi t nhin  phc v nhu cu sn xut C ph Chn. Chng b i x d man v ch c cho n qu c ph. </span></p>\n<p><span>Ngoi 10 con cy va c ti th, Cng an tnh Ha Bnh cn bn giao 9 ng vt hoang d khc cho SVW, trong  mt con cy vi hng  c trung tm \"an t nhn o\" v vt thng qu nng v mt con khng th ti th do mt mt chn, c gi li phc v mc ch gio dc bo tn. </span></p>\n<p><span>By c th cn li u l loi don </span><em>(Atherurus macrourus)</em><span>,</span><span> ang tip tc c chm sc ti Vn quc gia Cc Phng.</span></p></article></div>', '10 con cy c ti th vo t nhin', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '10-con-cay-duoc-tai-tha-vao-tu-nhien', '', '', '2017-09-20 03:51:28', '2017-09-20 03:51:28', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/10-con-cay-duoc-tai-tha-vao-tu-nhien/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1409', '1', '2017-09-20 03:34:57', '2017-09-20 03:34:57', '<div><h2>Cc d n gii quyt n tc ang rt chm trin khai v th tc, TP HCM kin ngh Th tng cho ch nh thu.</h2><article>\n<p>UBND TP HCM va kin ngh Chnh ph cho php ch nh thu theo hnh thc PPP (i tc cng - t) cc d n cp bch nhm khp kn ng Vnh ai 2 (on mt, hai, bn); cc bi  xe cao tng (ti Cng vin 23/9, c x L Thng Kit, Cng vin Gia nh, bn xe but qun 8, Ch Ln, Tn Ph...).</p>\n<p>ng thi ny nhm thc hin mong mun nhanh chng nng cao hiu qu khai thc h tng giao thng hin hu, ko gim n tc v tai nn giao thng. V theo ng trnh t th tc, thnh ph s mt rt nhiu thi gian  khi cng cc d n ny.</p><table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"tp-hcm-muon-chi-dinh-thau-nhieu-du-an-giao-thong-cap-bach\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/20/so-do-giao-thong-tphcm-JPG-191-1247-9036-1505877019.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>ng Vnh ai 2 TP HCM (ng vin  trong cng) sau hn 10 nm vn cha c khp kn.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Trong khi , tin  cc bi u xe ngm ti TP HCM vn ang rt  ch. n nay, mi c d n Bi u xe Cng vin L Vn Tm c tng s vn u t hn 110 triu USD do cng ty C phn Khng gian ngm (IUS) lm ch u t c ng th vo nm 2010.</p>\n<p>Cng trnh ny c k vng l \"pht sng\" u tin nhng cha bit khi no mi hon thnh v b p chiu sut by nm qua do vng th tc. V vy, cc bi u xe cao tng c xem l gii php cp bch  gii quyt tnh trng thiu ch u xe ti TP HCM.</p>\n<p>ng Vnh ai 2 di khong 70 km, bt u t ng Nguyn Vn Linh (huyn Bnh Chnh) qua cu Ph M (qun 7), tip tc ra ng t Bnh Thi (qun 9) ni vo nt giao G Da (qun Th c). im cui ra Quc l 1 ri chy vng v Nguyn Vn Linh to thnh tuyn ng vng quanh TP HCM.</p>\n<p>Cng trnh c  ngha quan trng trong vic to ra trc giao thng  cc ca ng, hn ch phng tin vo trung tm gim n tc cho thnh ph. Tuy nhin, hn chc nm qua, tuyn ng vn cha c khp kn.</p>\n<p>Ti bui lm vic ca Th tng Nguyn Xun Phc vi lnh o TP HCM mi y, Th trng B Giao thng Vn ti Nguyn Ngc ng nh gi, d l u tu pht trin kinh t ca c nc nhng h tng giao thng ca TP HCM cha tt, ng Vnh ai 2 vn cha c khp kn, Vnh ai 3 th cha lm c on no.</p>\n<p><span>Trong kin ngh ln ny, TP HCM cng </span> ngh B Giao thng Vn ti <strong><span>iu chnh thi gian ct h cnh xung sn bay Tn Sn Nht</span></strong> vo gi cao im v tng cng s chuyn bay m, trnh tp trung ct h cnh vo gi cao im ban ngy. iu ny l  gim n tc cc tuyn ng xung quanh Tn Sn Nht.</p>\n<p>Ngoi ra, B Giao thng cng c  ngh iu chnh b sung quy hoch giao thng thy ti khu vc cng Ct Li,  ph hp vi quy hoch n nm 2020.</p>\n<p>Lnh o thnh ph cng kin ngh y ban An ton giao thng Quc gia iu chnh tiu ch nh gi tai nn giao thng ph hp v ban hnh tiu ch xc nh n tc giao thng c th  thng nht p dng trn c nc.</p>\n<p><strong>Hu Cng</strong></p></article></div>', 'TP HCM mun ch nh thu nhiu d n giao thng cp bch', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tp-hcm-muon-chi-dinh-thau-nhieu-du-an-giao-thong-cap-bach', '', '', '2017-09-20 03:34:57', '2017-09-20 03:34:57', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/tp-hcm-muon-chi-dinh-thau-nhieu-du-an-giao-thong-cap-bach/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
