INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1411', '1', '2017-09-20 03:25:04', '2017-09-20 03:25:04', '<div><h2>Do thu nhiu khon khng ng quy nh, Hiu trng trng Tiu hc ng Cng (Hi Phng) b nh ch cng tc 15 ngy  kim im. </h2><article>\n<p><span>UBND huyn An Dng (Hi Phng) va quyt nh nh ch cng tc 15 ngy i vi b L Th Thu Thy, Hiu trng trng tiu hc ng Cng,  kim tra cng tc qun l, thu chi cc khon ng gp ca ph huynh nm hc 2017-2018 v qun l, s dng vin chc, lao ng hp ng.</span></p>\n<p>Thi gian nh ch t 20/9, sau 15 ngy c kt lun chnh thc, huyn s cn c vo   x l. Nu sai phm mc  nh, b Thy s b kim im, c phc hi chc v; sai phm ln s cch chc, ng <span>L Anh Qun, Ch tch huyn An Dng thng tin. </span></p>\n<p>UBND huyn An Dng nhn c n th ca mt nam gio vin v mt ngi nguyn l th qu trng tiu hc ng Cng, phn nh hiu trng  ra mc thu ti 10 triu ng mi hc sinh. Nh chc trch  lp on cng tc xc minh, kt qu 8 trn 14 khon thu khng ng quy nh.</p>\n<p><span>Ngy 18/9, khong 40 ngi eo khu trang, mang bng zn vi ni dung xc phm, yu cu n hiu trng t chc. S vic gy n o nh hng n hc sinh v gio vin nh trng. Huyn An Dng phi b tr lc lng xung, mi tt c v hi trng UBND x lm vic</span><span>.</span></p><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"them-mot-hieu-truong-o-hai-phong-bi-dinh-chi-cong-tac\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/20/Dang-Cuong-1-jpeg-5676-1505873548.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Nhiu ph huynh c nhu cu ly li tin mua bo him cho con mnh v tin h tr gio vin ch nhim lin lc vi gia nh c nh trng gii quyt.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>V vic t co lm thu, Hiu trng Thy trn tnh c mt s khon c ku gi x hi ha, trng t chc hp gia gio vin ch nhim vi i din hi ph huynh nh trng, hi ph huynh cc lp  ly  kin.</p>\n<p>Trc vic ph huynh khi lp 1 cho rng thu cao, b Thy gii thch 1.350.000 ng l nh trng thu h cng ty Dome Vit Nam. Dome ng ra t chc cho cc chu 6 tui tham gia mt thng tri h tri nghim trc khi vo nm hc mi trn tinh thn ph huynh t nguyn,  tha thun trc  vi n v t chc. Cc khon bo him y t, sch v  dng hc tp, ng phc... ph huynh no ng  mua th trng thu, khng bt buc. </p>\n<p>Theo Hiu trng T<span>hy, v 1.000 hc sinh b sn sng ngh vic, song  ngh c quan chc nng kim tra, a ra kt lun khch quan, nhm n nh tnh hnh nh trng, c bit lm r ng c ca mt s ngi ng sau v vic</span><span>. </span></p>\n<p><span>T</span><span>rc  ngy 11/9, UBND huyn Thy Nguyn (TP Hi Phng) quyt nh nh ch cng tc 15 ngy i vi ng Nguyn Hu t, Hiu trng trng THCS Minh Tn  lm r mt s khon thu u nm khng ng quy nh.</span></p></article></div>', 'Thm mt hiu trng  Hi Phng b nh ch cng tc', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'them-mot-hieu-truong-o-hai-phong-bi-dinh-chi-cong-tac', '', '', '2017-09-20 03:25:04', '2017-09-20 03:25:04', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/them-mot-hieu-truong-o-hai-phong-bi-dinh-chi-cong-tac/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
