INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1415', '1', '2017-09-19 17:00:00', '2017-09-19 17:00:00', '<div><h2>Ch di 2-3 km nhng nhiu tuyn ng ang \"gnh\" n vi chc cao c, hng chc nghn h dn, khin kt xe ngy cng nghim trng.</h2><article>\n<p>L tuyn mi nht ti ca ng pha ng TP HCM, ni t cu Si Gn n ng Tn c Thng (qun 1), ng Nguyn Hu Cnh (phng 22, qun Bnh Thnh) di khong 3 km thi gian gn y l im \"nng\" kt xe ca TP HCM<span>. </span></p>\n<p><span>Trn con ng ny</span> hin c 3 d n cao c ln cng nhiu trng hc, bnh vin v mt s khu dn c dy c. Ngoi <span>chung c The Manor vi </span><span>hn 1.000 cn h </span><span> i vo hot ng t nhiu nm nay, h</span><span>ng lot cao c khc vi c chc nghn cn h san st nhau, sp c a vo s dng gy lo ngi n tc s ngy cng nghim trng.</span></p>\n<p><span>Nhiu chuyn gia  ln ting cnh bo, tnh trng kt xe ti y \"s khng khip\" nu t by gi khng c phng n gii quyt.</span></p>\n<p><span>Hnh nh nh cao tng chen chc nhau cng quen thuc  nhiu tuyn ng trung tm TP HCM nh Nguyn Th Minh Khai, in Bin Ph, Tn c Thng, Nam K Khi Ngha, L Li... Chng cng b cho l \"th phm\" lm kt xe. </span></p>\n<p><span>Vn  ny  c i biu HND TP HCM T Th Bch Chu nu ra v yu cu S Xy dng lm r vic cp php xy nh cao tng  khu vc trung tm v tnh trng n tc ngy cng nghim trng m cao c vn lin tc mc thm. </span></p>\n<p>Khng ch  cc khu \"t vng\", m dc nhng tuyn ng huyt mch ca thnh ph nhiu d n nh  cao tng, trung tm thng mi cng  t xy dng. Nhiu cng trnh cha xy xong, ng  kt.</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" border=\"0\" align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"cao-oc-sai-gon-dang-bop-nghet-giao-thong\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/19/cao-oc-Sai-Gon-6045-1505832706.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>ng Nguyn Hu Cnh ang \"gnh\" nhiu cao c vi hng chc nghn cn h. nh: <em>Qunh Trn.</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p> ca ng pha Nam Si Gn, <span>ng Nguyn Hu Th - trc ng chnh ni qun 7 v Nh B - cng l \"im en\" kt xe. Dc tuyn ng ny c hng chc d n chung c vi khong 100.000 cn h. </span></p>\n<p><span>Bn cnh hng lot cao c  c a vo s dng, ngay di chn cu Knh T nhiu cao c  xong phn mng v ang tip tc \"cao ln\" tng ngy. <span>Vo gi cao im, t, xe my... phi nhch tng cht mt  qua cung ng ny</span>.</span></p>\n<p> qun 4, ng Bn Vn n ch di khong 2 km nhng hin trn trc ng ny  c 12 chung c, cao c, trung tm thng mi vi hng chc nghn cn h. Ngay sau con ng ny, ng Hong Diu cng c hng chc ta chung c khc  c a vo s dng t trc.</p>\n<p>Tng t<strong>,</strong> ng Ph Quang (qun Tn Bnh) gn ca ng sn bay Tn Sn Nht di cha ti 2 km nhng c c chc cao c. Phn ln cc d n ang xy dng, ngi dn n  cha nhiu nhng xe qua y lun trong tnh trng c th kt bt c lc no.</p>\n<p>\"Vic xy dng cc chung c cao tng trn lan ang gy p lc rt ln ln h thng giao thng v khin nhiu tuyn ng tr nn qu ti. Nhiu khu vc h tng giao thng ang tr thnh \'nn nhn\' ca vic quy hoch kin trc, khng gian  th cha ph hp\", <strong><span>ng Phm nh c - Trng Phng Qun l Vn ti ng b (S Giao thng Vn ti TP HCM)</span></strong>  khng nh ti Hi ngh Quc t v An ton giao thng khu vc ng  (EASTS) ln th 12 hm 18/9.</p>\n<p>Theo ng c, thnh ph quy hoch theo nh hng xung quanh cc u mi giao thng nh nh ga, trm xe but, chung c... u gn vi vn ti hnh khch cng cng. Tuy nhin, nu xy dng  th \"nn\" qu nhiu s dn n lng ngi, phng tin, nhu cu i li tng v cng kh gii quyt bi ton n tc. V vy, cn c gii php, phng n kh thi trong quy hoch v ci thin h thng kt cu h tng hin hu.</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" border=\"0\" align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"cao-oc-tran-lan-bop-nghet-giao-thong-sai-gon-1\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/13/cao-oc-q7-2799-1505282315.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Cao c mc san st trn ng Nguyn Hu Th khin p lc giao thng ngy cng ln. nh: <em>Hu Nguyn.</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><span>Trao i vi </span><em>VnExpress</em><span>, TS.KTS Ng Vit Nam Sn cho rng vic cp php xy dng hin nay ang thc hin khng khoa hc. iu ny do S Xy dng, Quy hoch - Kin trc, Giao thng Vn ti phi hp cha tt. Cch lm hin nay l cp php theo quy hoch h tng tng lai ch khng phi theo h tng hin ti.</span></p>\n<p>\"Quy hoch cho php nh xy 30 tng nhng vi iu kin l khi con ng  c m rng ln 30 m, ch khng phi l 10 m nh hin ti. Trong khi thc t 10-20 nm na con ng  cha chc  c m rng m cao c 30 tng  mc ln ri th lm sao h tng khng qu ti, con ng 10 m lm sao gnh ni\", ng Sn phn tch.</p>\n<p><span>H qu l nh nc chu p lc v khi c cao c 30 tng ri th phi m ng  gim kt xe. Ngha l thay v h tng i trc mt bc th li phi chy theo sau nh mt vng lun qun. \"Nu mt vi con ng th cn chu c ch hng trm, hng nghn con ng th ngn sch u m lm\", ng Sn ni.</span></p>\n<p><span>Chuyn gia v xy dng dn chng, </span> cc nc pht trin, sau khi lm h s quy hoch phi c k hoch thc hin quy hoch. Trong k hoch , ngi ta s tnh ton n h tng tng nh th no, m ng ra sao, mt  dn c c th theo tng nm, tng giai on pht trin. C quan chc nng s da vo   cp php sao cho ph hp vi hin trng thc t ca h tng. Trong khi ,  Vit Nam ang khng h c cc k hoch ny.</p>\n<p>\"y l l hng rt ln dn n tnh trng  th lm chm nh th ny. Tuy nhin, n thuc tm quc gia ch khng phi ring TP HCM. Cho nn vic hn ch cp php xy dng cao c  nhng ni quy hoch v nhng ni thng kt xe l ng\", ng Sn ni v  ngh thnh ph cn c quy ch trong cp php xy dng  m bo s thng nht ca c 3 S, s trnh c tnh trng nh hin nay.</p><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" border=\"0\" align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"cao-oc-sai-gon-dang-bop-nghet-giao-thong-2\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/19/cau-Kenh-te-2034-1492574904-8430-1505832706.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Cu Knh T (ni qun 7 v 4) thng xuyn b n tc. nh: <em>B.T.</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>V vn  ny, Ch tch UBND TP HCM Nguyn Thnh Phong va yu cu khng gii quyt cp php xy dng cho nhng cng trnh cao c tp trung ng ngi trn cc trc ng, khu vc cha u t hon chnh h thng h tng giao thng theo quy hoch c duyt.</p>\n<p>S Quy hoch - Kin trc ang r sot nhng khu vc hn ch xy cao c v a ra cc tiu ch v xy dng c lin quan. Vic ny s hon thnh vo cui nm nay  bo co UBND thnh ph.</p>\n<p>Trong giai on r sot, tt c d n xy cao c trc khi c S Xy dng cp php u phi qua S Quy hoch - Kin trc v S Giao thng Vn ti  nh gi tc ng v giao thng.</p>\n<p>Vic cp php xy dng c mt t chuyn gia do S Xy dng ch tr (gm i din cc s, ngnh c lin quan nh Quy hoch - Kin trc, Ti nguyn - Mi trng, Giao thng Vn ti, Ti chnh)  xem xt tng trng hp c th. Nhng trng hp c bit th phi xin  kin S GTVT bng vn bn v tc ng giao thng.</p>\n<p><strong>Hu Nguyn</strong></p></article></div>', 'Cao c Si Gn ang \'bp nght\' giao thng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cao-oc-sai-gon-dang-bop-nghet-giao-thong', '', '', '2017-09-19 17:00:00', '2017-09-19 17:00:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/cao-oc-sai-gon-dang-bop-nghet-giao-thong/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
