INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1417', '1', '2017-09-20 08:09:15', '2017-09-20 08:09:15', '<div><h2>B cho l qun l khng tt khin va h \"by hy\", lnh o phng Cu ng Lnh (qun 1) b  xut h chc.</h2><article><table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"chu-tich-phuong-dau-tien-bi-ong-doan-ngoc-hai-de-xuat-ha-chuc\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/20/bai-xe-co-bac-3804-1505892859.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Hai bi gi xe khng php trn va h ng C Bc. nh: <em>Duy Trn.</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Chiu 20/9, ng on Ngc Hi  Ph ch tch UBND qun 1  gi vn bn n UBND TP HCM v lnh o Qun u, UBND qun 1,  xut lun chuyn ng Bi Minh Tin (Ch tch UBND phng Cu ng Lnh) theo hng h chc v.</p>\n<p>ng thi ny c ng Hi cn c theo ch th ca Thnh y TP HCM hi u nm v tng cng cng tc qun l trt t  th trn a bn.</p>\n<p>ng Tin b cho l cha hon thnh nhim v, l lnh o phng nhng bung lng qun l sut tm thng qua, khng x l dt im tnh trng ln chim va h.</p>\n<p>Cc tuyn ng C Bc, V Vn Kit, Nguyn Thi Hc thuc a bn phng Cu ng Lnh vn cn nhiu qun nhu by bn gh,  d, cu thang dn, mi hin di ng chim va h; nh hng Bin Dng 3, qun 500 Anh Em cng thng xuyn ti chim va h.</p>\n<p>c bit, trn ng C Bc tn ti hai bi gi xe  ht php hn by thng. Khu vc ny cng gy mt v sinh, m quan  th khi nhiu ngi cng bt, by bn gh, rc thi...</p><table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"chu-tich-phuong-dau-tien-bi-ong-doan-ngoc-hai-de-xuat-ha-chuc-1\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/20/nha-hang-bien-duong-3-bi-phat-8581-6023-1505892859.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Nh hng Bin Dng 3 trong ln b on lin ngnh x l. nh: <em>Duy Trn.</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>ng Hi cho bit tng l lnh o phng Cu ng Lnh nn rt r a bn. Va h ng C Bc ngy xa thng thong ch khng \"by hy\" nh hin nay.</p>\n<p><span>Hi u thng, Ph ch tch UBND qun 1 cng  xut iu chuyn Ph ch tch UBND phng Tn nh v lm chuyn vin Phng Qun l  th v  va h nhiu tuyn ng ca phng b ti chim. Mt n cn b  th ca phng ny cng b yu cu lun chuyn.</span></p>\n<p>Sau bn thng tm dng ra qun, on lin ngnh qun 1  x pht hn 200 t, nhiu nh hng, qun nhu Hin, va h khu trung tm Si Gn  thng thong hn trc.</p></article></div>', 'Ch tch phng u tin b ng on Ngc Hi  xut h chc', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chu-tich-phuong-dau-tien-bi-ong-doan-ngoc-hai-de-xuat-ha-chuc', '', '', '2017-09-20 08:09:15', '2017-09-20 08:09:15', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/chu-tich-phuong-dau-tien-bi-ong-doan-ngoc-hai-de-xuat-ha-chuc/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
