INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1421', '1', '2017-09-19 15:26:41', '2017-09-19 15:26:41', '<div><h2>Ph gim c S Ti nguyn cho rng, kt qu nghin cu cht lng khng kh ca GreenID khng c gi tr v khng nm trong quy nh nh nc.</h2><article>\n<p>Trao i vi bo ch chiu 19/9, Ph gim c S Ti nguyn v Mi trng H Ni L Tun nh cho hay, thng tin  nhim mi trng th  do Trung tm pht trin sng to xanh (GreenID) a ra khng  c s v khng nm trong quy nh ca nh nc.</p><table align=\"left\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"so-tai-nguyen-canh-bao-khong-khi-ha-noi-co-hai-la-khong-du-co-so\" data-natural-width=\"220\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/19/ong-le-tuan-dinh-2627-15058328-5817-2223-1505834791.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Ph gim c S Ti nguyn Mi trng H Ni L Tun nh. nh: <em>V Hi.</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Theo Ph gim c S Ti nguyn, c th GreenID ly s liu quan trc ti mt thi im, mt v tr nh mt im giao thng hay mt cng trnh ang ph d nn kt qu khng th phn nh ton din cht lng khng kh ca th .</p>\n<p>Tuy nhin, ng nh cng tha nhn, vo ma kh  nhim khng kh do bi  H Ni rt cao do thnh ph ang c nhiu cng trnh xy dng ln. <span> nhim khng kh bi hin nay chng ti cng a vo trong nhm c kh nng gy  nhim nghim trng, ng nh ni.</span></p>\n<p><span>Lnh o S Ti nguyn cho bit thm, hin thnh ph c 10 trm quan trc khng kh v sp ti lp t thm 70 trm, ngi dn c th truy cp vo Cng giao tip in t ca thnh ph  bit c mc   nhim khng kh ti cc im c t trm quan trc.</span></p><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"so-tai-nguyen-canh-bao-khong-khi-ha-noi-co-hai-la-khong-du-co-so-1\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/19/ket-qua-quan-trac-khong-khi-hn-1826-1742-1505832882.png\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>S liu quan trc lc 16h ngy 19/9 (cng b trn Cng giao tip in t TP H Ni) cho thy khng kh  hu ht im c quan trc t ch s tt.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Theo kt qu nghin cu cht lng mi trng Vit Nam ca GreenID, trong nhng thng u nm s ngy cht lng khng kh  mc \"rt c hi cho sc khe\" ti H Ni gia tng so vi cng k.</p>\n<p>C th, trong qu I, H Ni c 37 ngy c nng  PM 2.5 (ht bi l lng ng knh t 2,5 micromet tr xung) trong 24 gi cao hn so vi gii hn Quy chun quc gia (50 g/m3) v 78 ngy vt qu gii hn theo Hng dn ca T chc Y t Th gii (WHO) l 25 g/m3.</p><table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td>\n<p>S Ti nguyn Mi trng H Ni va  xut thnh ph cho lp t 3 trm quan trc nc mt trn cc sng T Lch, Nhu v Cu By. Cc bn lin quan  t chc kho st thc a, thng nht phng n la chn v tr lp t 3 trm.</p>\n<p>Cng theo S Ti nguyn, 3 trm quan trc t ng nc mt ti h Ty, h Hon Kim v sui Lai Sn (nm trong khu lin hip x l cht thi Sc Sn)  c lp t v a vo s dng t thng 4/2017.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></article></div>', 'S Ti nguyn: Cnh bo khng kh H Ni c hi l khng  c s', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'so-tai-nguyen-canh-bao-khong-khi-ha-noi-co-hai-la-khong-du-co-so', '', '', '2017-09-19 15:26:41', '2017-09-19 15:26:41', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/so-tai-nguyen-canh-bao-khong-khi-ha-noi-co-hai-la-khong-du-co-so/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
