INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1427', '1', '2017-09-19 10:34:53', '2017-09-19 10:34:53', '<div><h2>ng V Trng Vit cho rng vic i gia chi phi cn b lm mo m quan h o c x hi.</h2><article>\n<p>Tho lun v bo co phng chng ti phm, tham nhng, thi hnh n chiu 19/9, <span>Ch nhim y ban Quc phng An ninh V Trng Vit ghi nhn, thi gian qua, nhiu v i n c khi t, xt x c  hnh s, kinh t  c</span><span>ng c lng tin cho nhn dn. Tuy nhin, theo ng,</span><span> n th khiu ni, t co cn nhiu, m n th vng vo th kh dn, ln trn b y xung, di th khng gii quyt c, nn ngi dn bc xc.</span></p>\n<p><span>Vn  th hai ng bn khon l vic \"i gia, i ca lm h hng cn b, trong  c mt s cn b cp cao\".</span></p>\n<p><span>\"iu ny lm mo m quan h o c x hi, vi phm php lut, nhng vn ng ngoi vng php lut. </span><span>y l nhng i tng t ngi nhc n, t bo co ni n. Nhng theo quan im ca ti trong d lun x hi cn nng n\", ng Vit ni.</span></p>\n<p>Ch nhim y ban Quc phng An ninh cng lo ngi vn  o c ngh nghip ca mt b phn cn b cng chc  khi t php. Nhn dn thy 9-10 vic tt, nhng ch mt vi vic khng tt th s mt nim tin. V vy, cn phi ht sc coi trng o c ngh nghip.</p>\n<p>\"Ti gp nhiu b co, t nhn, c bit mt s cn b nhn danh Nh nc  iu tra, thm vn, xt x, nhng cha c khm phc v phong cch, thi , trnh , nn vic la chn thm phn xt x vi cc v n phi ht sc lu \", ng ni.</p><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"chu-nhiem-uy-ban-quoc-phong-an-ninh-dai-gia-lam-hu-hong-can-bo\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/19/Vo-Trong-Viet-6096-1505815944.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Ch nhim U ban Quc phng An ninh V Trng Vit. nh: <em>QH</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><strong>\"Ti sao cha kt lun thanh tra ti sn gim c S Yn Bi?\"</strong></p>\n<p>Ph ban Dn nguyn  Vn ng  ngh nhng <span>v vic ln qua thanh tra phi cng khai rng ri, ng thi gian quy nh. Hin nay nhiu v vic thanh tra xong c  y. </span></p>\n<p><span>\"Nh v Yn Bi, sao dn rt quan tm m mi cha cng b? U ban Kim tra Trung ng cng b rt ng thi hn, ch r sai phm, x l tng ngi, nh vy l rt hay, to s quan tm rt c bit v ng tnh t ngi dn\", ng ng ni. Theo ng, nhiu vic lm tn cng sc, c n lc nhng v chm tr cng b m ngi dn cm thy c khut tt, hiu qu phng chng tham nhng km.</span></p>\n<p>Kim ton v thanh tra l hai c quan quan trng nht  kim sot tham nhng, tuy nhin s v chuyn qua hai n v ny t \"<span>chng t vn  pht hin, x l v trch nhim cn hn ch\".</span></p>\n<p>Ph ban Dn nguyn cng so snh, hin nay n v trt t tr an, c bit l git ngi, trng n c lm rt tt. S kp thi ny khin ngi dn khm phc cng an, nhiu ngi ni t nc yn bnh, khng c khng b v cng an rt gii. Nhng tin  x l, gii quyt n tham nhng cn chm, ko di. T l tr li h s l 37%, ch yu do to tr, c v to tr 3 ln ko di 6 nm.</p>\n<p>\"Cng l chm tr l cng l bt cng, doanh nghip ph sn v vic ny. Ch ny U ban Thng v Quc hi cn c  kin su  doanh nghip cn lm n. V chm xung Cn Gi 9 ngi cht ch vng kt lun gim nh m n nay cha gii quyt, trong khi doanh nghip c hng nghn cng nhn\", ng ng ni.</p>\n<p>ng cng dn v n con du Hong Th Vn<span> git m chng,  tm giam 6 nm, nhng \"con du git m chng m c gia nh nh chng li ku oan cho con du\", thi gian tm giam li qu di. V vy ng  ngh, nu a phng khng lm c th rt ln trn iu tra ch khng th  lu nh th. \"y l bt cng gy hnh nh xu cho nn t php\", ng ni.</span></p>\n<p><span>Theo Ph ban Dn nguyn, thc t, mi nm c khong 300 - 400 n tuyn kh thi hnh. C v 20 nm nay tip dn thy khng thi hnh c nh ngi nh 3m m tuyn n chia i, v n ly hn tuyn chng tng trn v tng di khng c ng ra. Hay v mi nht l 200ha rng cao su  Ty Ninh, to giao 7 h dn tr t cho UBND nhng khng ni x l ti sn trn t l cy cao su nh th no. V vy n  ko di 7 nm khng thi hnh c. </span></p>\n<p><span>\"By ra nh th sut ngy U ban vc h s sang t php hi  kin. Khng gii quyt c, dn bc xc, khiu kin. Chnh cc ng ch lm ra khiu kin, bc xc\", ng ng khng nh v  ngh </span><span>phi tng kt xem cn bao nhiu v n tuyn mt ng m thc t mt no.</span></p></article></div>', 'Ch nhim y ban Quc phng An ninh: i gia lm h hng cn b', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chu-nhiem-uy-ban-quoc-phong-an-ninh-dai-gia-lam-hu-hong-can-bo', '', '', '2017-09-19 10:34:53', '2017-09-19 10:34:53', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/chu-nhiem-uy-ban-quoc-phong-an-ninh-dai-gia-lam-hu-hong-can-bo/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
