INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1429', '1', '2017-09-19 09:45:52', '2017-09-19 09:45:52', '<div><h2>H thng cp ngm cung cp in ton b trung tm Si Gn nhiu ln b k gian ct trm thit b, c th gy hu qu ln.</h2><article>\n<p>Ngy 19/9, lm vic vi on i biu Quc hi TP HCM, ng V nh Thy - Gim c Cng ty truyn ti in 4 (PTC4) - cho bit, truyn ti in TP HCM c chc nng truyn ti in cao p t 220kV n 500kV, cung cp in cho thnh ph v chim hn 12,5% tng sn lng in truyn ti quc gia.</p>\n<p>Trong h thng li in cung cp cho TP HCM, cp in ngm 220kV Nh B - Tao n l h thng xng sng, cp in cho ton b khu vc trung tm gm qun 1, 3, 5, 10.</p>\n<p>\"D  xy dng v din tp phng n, gii php thay th phng nga mt in trm Tao n, song vn c nhng s c k gian ct trm thit b khin ngnh in tht tim\", ng Thy ni.</p><table align=\"center\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" border=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"tp-hcm-lo-mat-dien-toan-trung-tam-vi-nan-trom-cap-vat\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/19/Cap-ngam-tram-Tao-Dan-9692-1505812360.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>H thng trm bin p Tao n. <em>nh: PTC4.</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>V vn  ny, Gim c Truyn ti in TP HCM Bi Vn Hong cho hay, ng dy cp ngm Nh B  Tao n c on phi i di ln cc cy cu. Va qua, ti khu vc cu Knh T (qun 4), k gian  chui vo ph tm chn, ct ly dy ng tip a.</p>\n<p>\"Theo gi th trng, on dy ng  ch bn c khong mt triu ng nhng k thut lp tr li phi mt hng chc triu, thm ch hng t ng, cha k nu c s c xy ra th thit hi khng tnh ni\", ng Hong lo lng.</p>\n<p>Ngoi ra, t nm 2012 n nay trn a bn TP HCM xy ra 16 trng hp mt cp thit b trn h thng li in, ch yu mt thanh dn tr in ng dy 500kV cao th. c bit,  khu vc vng v nh huyn Nh B, c tr in b mt hng chc thanh dn, gy nguy c ng  tr in 500kV.</p>\n<p>Theo ng Hong, hin ch c h thng ng dy 500kV t mt (thi c Th tng V Vn Kit ch o xy dng) c a vo danh mc cng trnh trng im lin quan an ninh quc gia. Ring h thng cp ngm 220kV Nh B  Tao n, cng nh nhiu h thng truyn ti in 500kV t 2, 3 cha c a vo danh mc.</p>\n<p>V vy, nu bt c th phm trm thit b in cng ch x pht nh, rt kh truy cu trch nhim hnh s, khng  rn e.</p>\n<p>Truyn ti in TP HCM  ngh on i biu kin ngh Th tng xem xt, a cc h thng ny vo danh mc cng trnh quan trng lin quan an ninh quc gia. Khi , ngi no ly cp mt con c cng s b xem xt trch nhim hnh s v ti Xm phm an ninh quc gia.</p>\n<p>Ngnh in thnh ph cng kin ngh x l dt im cc trng hp vi phm hnh lang an ton ca cc tuyn ng dy 500kV. Ngoi ra, h  ngh Cng an TP HCM sm k quy ch phi hp bo v, xy dng phng n phng chng khng b li truyn ti in.</p>\n<p>Ph trng on i biu Quc hi TP HCM Phan Nguyn Nh Khu ng  vi kin ngh ca truyn ti in. Tuy nhin, i biu Khu lo ngi, theo d bo nm 2020 ri vo tnh trng thiu in gay gt nn ngnh in ngay t by gi phi c gii php d tr.</p>\n<p><strong>Tuyt Nguyn</strong></p></article></div>', 'TP HCM lo mt in ton trung tm v nn trm cp vt', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tp-hcm-lo-mat-dien-toan-trung-tam-vi-nan-trom-cap-vat', '', '', '2017-09-19 09:45:52', '2017-09-19 09:45:52', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/tp-hcm-lo-mat-dien-toan-trung-tam-vi-nan-trom-cap-vat/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
