INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1431', '1', '2017-09-19 07:13:55', '2017-09-19 07:13:55', '<div><h2>Theo Hip hi vn ti hng ho Hi Phng, mt chuyn hng container t Hi Phng n H Ni c chi ph ng b l 3,6 triu ng.</h2><article>\n<p>Ngy 19/9, ti cuc lm vic gia T cng tc ca Th tng vi lnh o thnh ph Hi Phng, ng Nguyn Vn Thanh - Ch tch hip hi vn ti t Vit Nam,  kin ngh Chnh ph xem xt vic xo b hai trm thu ph trn Quc l 5 (c) ni H Ni - Hi Phng.</p><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"hai-tram-thu-phi-bot-quoc-lo-5-bi-de-nghi-xoa-bo\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/19/IMG-5496-JPG-7630-1505805152.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>ng Nguyn Vn Thanh, Ch tch hip hi vn ti t Vit Nam, kin ngh xo b hai trm thu ph trn Quc l 5 ni H Ni - Hi Phng. nh:<em> V.V.T</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>Theo ng Thanh, hip hi vn ti hng ho Hi Phng phn nh ang gp nhiu kh khn; c ti 30-50% phng tin dng hot ng, tr ph hiu  khng phi np cc khon ph.</p>\n<p>Trong s cc nguyn nhn dn n tnh trng trn, ng Thanh ni, c vic chi ph vn ti ng b qu cao. C th, mt chuyn hng container t Hi Phng n H Ni c chi ph ng b l 3,6 triu ng; ng st l 2,8 triu ng; hng khng l 2,6 triu ng.</p>\n<p>Gi i ng b qu cao, do ph chng ln ph. Vi ph BOT hin nay, mi tn hng t Hi Phng chuyn ln H Ni c chi ph trn 30 nghn ng, ng Thanh ni.</p>\n<p>Ch tch hip hi vn ti t Vit Nam cho hay, bn cnh Quc l 5 c, doanh nghip v ngi dn c th i ng cao tc nhng \"ph t qu\". Theo ng, chnh v ph cao tc qu cao, nn khi Th trng Ti chnh  Hong Anh Tun hi gim c cng nh V (Hi Phng) l cc doanh nghip vn ti thng chn i cao tc hay Quc l 5 c, cu tr li l: \"Khong 80% phng tin khng chn cao tc\".</p>\n<p>\"Cch lm trit  nht l xo b hai trm thu ph trn Quc l 5 c, tuy nhin chng ti bit kin ngh ny kh thc hin v s to gnh nng ti chnh cho Nh nc\", ng Thanh ni v cho bit, Hip hi a ra thm 2 phng n. Mt l, gim ph qua trm. Mc ph cho xe tiu chun hin l 40 nghn ng mi lt, qu cao so vi ch 10 nghn ng trc y. Hai l, min ph ng b thu theo u phng tin i vi xe container v xe ch khch chy tuyn c nh.</p>\n<p><span>Chung  kin vi Hip hi vn ti t, i din Hip hi dt may Vit Nam cng cho rng, ph cu ng qu cao cng vi ph s dng c s h tng cng bin ca Hi Phng tng trong thi gian qua  \"khin cho doanh nghip pha Bc gp nhiu kh khn</span><span>\".</span></p>\n<div>\n<div data-component=\"true\" data-component-type=\"video\" data-component-value=\"165897\" data-component-typevideo=\"2\"></div></div>\n<p>V tr trm BOT Quc l 5. Video: <em>on Loan - T L</em></p>\n<p><span>Trao i vi bo ch bn l cuc lm vic, B trng, Ch nhim Vn phng Chnh ph Mai Tin Dng, cho bit  ghi nhn kin ngh ca Hip hi vn ti t v s sm bo co Th tng xem xt. </span></p>\n<p><span>Theo ng, y l lnh vc thuc qun l nh nc ca B Giao thng, do vy T cng tc ca Th tng cng s trao i vi B ny  cng tham gia gii quyt.  kin c nhn ti l  xut ca Hip hi c phn hp l. Ch trng ca Chnh ph, ca Th tng hin l n lc gim chi ph chnh thc v khng chnh thc ca doanh nghip, ng Dng ni.</span></p><table align=\"center\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"hai-tram-thu-phi-bot-quoc-lo-5-bi-de-nghi-xoa-bo-1\" data-natural-width=\"500\" src=\"https://i-vnexpress.vnecdn.net/2017/09/19/thu-phi-7376-1505135629-4675-1505805152.jpg\"></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Ti x dng tin l mua v qua trm thu ph trn Quc l 5. nh:<em> Huy Mnh</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><span>T ngy 4/9, trm thu ph s 1 Quc l 5 lin tc xy ra tnh trng nhiu li xe dng tin l (loi 200 ng, 500 ng) mua v qua trm v c hnh vi c n v qun l trm cho l gy n tc giao thng.</span></p>\n<p>Cng an tnh Hng Yn  triu tp mt s ti x v doanh nghip lin quan ti s c n tc giao thng, mt trt t  trm thu ph trn Quc l 5.</p><table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\"><tbody><tr><td>\n<p>Quc l 5 l tuyn ng huyt mch ni H Ni - Hi Phng, di khong 100 km, c hai trm thu ph ti Hng Yn v Hi Phng. Mc ph qua trm BOT hin thp nht l 40.000 ng, cao nht l 180.000 ng mi lt.</p>\n<p>T u nm 2016, d n nng cp quc l 5 theo hnh thc BOT c chuyn giao cho Vidifi; nh u t chu trch nhim sa cha, bo tr tuyn ng ny bng ngun kinh ph thu c t cc trm thu ph. Tuyn cao tc H Ni - Hi Phng di 105 km cng do Vidifi u t, thng xe ton tuyn vo cui nm 2015.</p>\n<p>Trc nhiu  kin cho rng khng th thu ph trn quc l 5 b cho chi ph u t cao tc H Ni - Hi Phng, ng Nguyn c Kin - Ph ch nhim y ban Kinh t gii thch Nh nc ang n nh u t 4.000 t ng u t cao tc.  l tin gii phng mt bng m ng l Nh nc phi b ra, song do ngn sch khng c nn phi  cho doanh nghip thu ph quc l 5 b p.</p></td></tr></tbody></table></article></div>', 'Hai trm thu ph BOT Quc l 5 b  ngh xa b', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hai-tram-thu-phi-bot-quoc-lo-5-bi-de-nghi-xoa-bo', '', '', '2017-09-19 07:13:55', '2017-09-19 07:13:55', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/hai-tram-thu-phi-bot-quoc-lo-5-bi-de-nghi-xoa-bo/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
