INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1503', '1', '2017-09-19 16:37:00', '2017-09-19 16:37:00', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"89\">\n<p> Hoang mang trc nghin cu n chui kt hp ung sa s gy hi sc khe </p>\n<p>Theo ngun tin t Timesofindia, sa v chui c l l s kt hp ph bin m chng ta thng thy, nht l vo bui sng. Tuy nhin theo cc chuyn gia, chui v sa kt hp cng nhau c th khng phi l s kt hp tt nht, trong khi s dng ring bit, c hai u v cng b dng.</p>\n<p>S kt hp gia chui v sa, nhn th c v rt l tng, bi c hai dng nh c th b p s thiu ht dinh dng ca nhau. </p>\n<p>Tuy nhin theo nghin cu, kt hp chui v sa cng nhau khng ch lm ri lon h tiu ha m cn lm nh hng n xoang mi. iu ny dn n tc nghn xoang, cm lnh, ho v d ng khc nh pht ban trn c th.</p>\n<p>Nhiu ngi tin rng s kt hp ca hai loi thc phm ny c th gii quyt cc vn  v ri lon tiu ha th thc t, n c th dn n hin tng nn ma, tiu chy v mt sc nu dng trong thi gian di.</p>\n<p>Theo l thuyt Ayurvedic  xut pht t n , n chui kt hp ung sa s gy nh hng n sc khe c th, lm gin on cc chc nng din ra trong c th. Cng vi iu ny, Ayurveda ni thm rng kt hp n chui ung sa c th khin c th cm thy nng n v lm chm hot ng ca no.</p>\n<p>Cng theo l thuyt Ayurvedic, cch tt nht  tn dng dinh dng ca hai loi thc phm ny, chnh l s dng chng ring bit. </p>\n<p>Bn c th n chui nh mt ba n nh trc hoc sau khi tp th dc, v ch dng sa sau khong 20 pht. Hoc bn cng c th thm chui vo cng thc sa chua nu bn thc s mun tiu th n vi mt sn phm sa.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505880585758.jpg\" w=\"500\" h=\"366\" alt=\"Chuy&#xEA;n gia n&#xF3;i g&#xEC; v&#x1EC1; chuy&#x1EC7;n &#x103;n chu&#x1ED1;i k&#x1EBF;t h&#x1EE3;p u&#x1ED1;ng s&#x1EEF;a - vi&#x1EC7;c m&#xE0; nhi&#x1EC1;u ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i v&#x1EAB;n l&#xE0;m m&#x1ED7;i s&#xE1;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"Chuy&#xEA;n gia n&#xF3;i g&#xEC; v&#x1EC1; chuy&#x1EC7;n &#x103;n chu&#x1ED1;i k&#x1EBF;t h&#x1EE3;p u&#x1ED1;ng s&#x1EEF;a - vi&#x1EC7;c m&#xE0; nhi&#x1EC1;u ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i v&#x1EAB;n l&#xE0;m m&#x1ED7;i s&#xE1;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"8943c500-9db9-11e7-a370-c9cc62f96717\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505880585758.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p>Thng tin ny khin nhiu ngi cm thy hoang mang. c bit l rt nhiu ngi c thi quen n chui kt hp ung sa mi sng, hay nh dn th hnh thng c thi quen kt hp 2 thc phm ny trc khi i tp gym v y vn l 2 thc phm em li dinh dng, nng lng cao cho c th. </p>\n<p>Vy chng ta c nn n chui kt hp ung sa trong ch  n ung hng ngy hay khng?</p>\n<p> Chuyn gia dinh dng khng nh nghin cu kt hp sa v chui cha c bng chng khoa hc c th </p>\n<p>Tr li v vn  ny, ThS.BS Dzon Th Tng Vy (Nguyn Trng khoa Dinh dng, Bnh vin 198, Vin ph Vin Dinh dng Lm sng) cho bit: \"Chng ta khng th kt lun vic kt hp sa v chui trong mt ba n l khng tt cho sc khe nu ch da vo mt bi bo nc ngoi. </p>\n<p>Thng tin y liu c chnh thng khng? Ngun tin ng bi liu c ng tin cy khng? Nghin cu cng b cng i hi phi tht r rng, c th nh nghin cu thc hin trn bao nhiu ngi? C mc bnh no khng hay hon ton khe mnh?...\".</p>\n<p>BS Tng Vi cng khng nh, cha c nghin cu no ti Vit Nam c th khng nh n chui kt hp ung sa gy hi sc khe. Nu mun khng nh th chng ta phi da trn bng chng nghin cu thc t.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-2-1505880585763.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"375\" alt=\"Chuy&#xEA;n gia n&#xF3;i g&#xEC; v&#x1EC1; chuy&#x1EC7;n &#x103;n chu&#x1ED1;i k&#x1EBF;t h&#x1EE3;p u&#x1ED1;ng s&#x1EEF;a - vi&#x1EC7;c m&#xE0; nhi&#x1EC1;u ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i v&#x1EAB;n l&#xE0;m m&#x1ED7;i s&#xE1;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" title=\"Chuy&#xEA;n gia n&#xF3;i g&#xEC; v&#x1EC1; chuy&#x1EC7;n &#x103;n chu&#x1ED1;i k&#x1EBF;t h&#x1EE3;p u&#x1ED1;ng s&#x1EEF;a - vi&#x1EC7;c m&#xE0; nhi&#x1EC1;u ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i v&#x1EAB;n l&#xE0;m m&#x1ED7;i s&#xE1;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"8917fa10-9db9-11e7-ad93-41df1fc652ef\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-2-1505880585763.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p>Theo BS Tng Vi, i khi nhiu ngi bnh c ung sa, n chui s gip tnh trng sc khe c ci thin r rt hn. Sa cha hm lng ng v vitamin tng i cao. </p>\n<p>Trong khi chui rt lnh v rt tt cho sc khe (loi chui  gi c cht bung, em dm hng, thay v tm p ha cht). Xt v thnh phn dinh dng, hai loi thc phm ny u tt cho sc khe nn khi kt hp vi nhau s em li ngun dinh dng di do.</p>\n<p>Chuyn gia cho bit thm, hin nay vo ba sng, c l c rt t trng hp ch n chui kt hp ung sa. ng l chng ta nn n chui kt hp ung sa vo ba sng v ba sng vn c coi l ba n quan trng nht trong ngy. </p>\n<p>Vic n chui v ung sa vo ba sng s b sung nhng cht dinh dng quan trng  lm vic trong mt ngy.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-3-1505880585765.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"438\" alt=\"Chuy&#xEA;n gia n&#xF3;i g&#xEC; v&#x1EC1; chuy&#x1EC7;n &#x103;n chu&#x1ED1;i k&#x1EBF;t h&#x1EE3;p u&#x1ED1;ng s&#x1EEF;a - vi&#x1EC7;c m&#xE0; nhi&#x1EC1;u ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i v&#x1EAB;n l&#xE0;m m&#x1ED7;i s&#xE1;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" title=\"Chuy&#xEA;n gia n&#xF3;i g&#xEC; v&#x1EC1; chuy&#x1EC7;n &#x103;n chu&#x1ED1;i k&#x1EBF;t h&#x1EE3;p u&#x1ED1;ng s&#x1EEF;a - vi&#x1EC7;c m&#xE0; nhi&#x1EC1;u ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i v&#x1EAB;n l&#xE0;m m&#x1ED7;i s&#xE1;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"89434fd0-9db9-11e7-81b4-cf79a2d9c36d\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-3-1505880585765.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p>\"Mi sng, chng ta c th n bn, ph, xi ty thch. Sau  hy ung thm mt ly sa tm 200ml, nu khng ung c nhiu th b sung khong 100ml cng  em li lng dng cht di do cho c th. Ung sa xong, bn c th s dng thm chui hoc cc loi hoa qu khc. </p>\n<p>C th s dng linh hot 100ml sa v 1 qu chui  b sung a dng dinh dng, tng cng nng lng trong ngy sau khi n sng\", BS Vi ni.</p>\n<p>Nhng vi ngi ln, bn cn n mt cht g , sau  mi ung sa  hp thu c ht cht dinh dng trong sa. Nu trong d dy khng c g m ung sa ngay th sa i xung d dy, rut rt nhanh, cc cht dinh dng trong sa khng hp thu ht c.</p>\n<p>\"Nu  ung sa ngt, li n thm qu chui cng c v ngt, bn  np vo c th kh nhiu ng. iu ny thc s khng tt cho ngi bo ph, tiu ng hoc nguy c mc tiu ng cao. Tt nht l bn nn n thc n khc ri mi tiu th nhng thc phm ny. </p>\n<p>Bn cng nn b sung tri cy linh hot nh xoi, da hu thay v ch n mi chui  ba n y  v phong ph hn\", BS Vi khng nh.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-4-1505880585768.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"370\" alt=\"Chuy&#xEA;n gia n&#xF3;i g&#xEC; v&#x1EC1; chuy&#x1EC7;n &#x103;n chu&#x1ED1;i k&#x1EBF;t h&#x1EE3;p u&#x1ED1;ng s&#x1EEF;a - vi&#x1EC7;c m&#xE0; nhi&#x1EC1;u ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i v&#x1EAB;n l&#xE0;m m&#x1ED7;i s&#xE1;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 4.\" title=\"Chuy&#xEA;n gia n&#xF3;i g&#xEC; v&#x1EC1; chuy&#x1EC7;n &#x103;n chu&#x1ED1;i k&#x1EBF;t h&#x1EE3;p u&#x1ED1;ng s&#x1EEF;a - vi&#x1EC7;c m&#xE0; nhi&#x1EC1;u ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i v&#x1EAB;n l&#xE0;m m&#x1ED7;i s&#xE1;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 4.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"8944af60-9db9-11e7-87c1-c5d43a753c95\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-4-1505880585768.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p>V i tng tp th hnh c nn kt hp chui v sa trong ba n hay khng, BS Vi cho rng, ch  n cho ngi tp gym i khi nhiu nng lng  tng c, do  cn dng sa c nhiu cht m nh m whey  d tiu ha v tng cng hp thu. </p>\n<p>Nu n trc khi tp th bn cng cn n nh, sau  mi n chui ung sa (lu  c th thay i linh hot loi tri cy). n xong mt lc cng mi nn tp luyn.</p>\n<p>Ngoi ra, BS Vi lu , ngi b au d dy m ung sa lc i s khng tt cho sc khe. Nn n cho, ph ri ung mt ly sa s hp l hn. </p>\n<p>Ngi b au d dy cng khng nn n chui tiu v n vo s gy kch thch, khin tnh trng bnh thm ti t. Bn c th thay chui tiu bng nhng loi hoa qu khc, trnh kch thch d dy.</p>\n<p>Ngi b bnh tiu ng khng nn kt hp sa v chui trong cng ba n s khin ng huyt tng cao. Ngi b bnh thn, nht l suy thn giai on cui cng khng nn n chui v c hm lng kali cao, khng tt cho ngi suy thn.</p>\n<p>Ngi b suy thn c ur mu cao cng nn s dng sa c hm lng m thp. Ngi b to bn nn n chui v chui gip nhun trng nhng cng khng nn n ty tin, nn n 1 qu hoc na qu sau ba n 30 pht.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">Ph n yu t nhiu bnh, phn ln l do kh huyt: ng  nhng sai lm nhn chm bn!</div></div>', 'Chuyn gia ni g v chuyn n chui kt hp ung sa - vic m nhiu ngi vn lm mi sng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-chuyen-an-chuoi-ket-hop-uong-sua-viec-ma-nhieu-nguoi-van-lam-moi-sang', '', '', '2017-09-19 16:37:00', '2017-09-19 16:37:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/chuyen-gia-noi-gi-ve-chuyen-an-chuoi-ket-hop-uong-sua-viec-ma-nhieu-nguoi-van-lam-moi-sang/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
