INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1506', '1', '2017-09-19 16:33:21', '2017-09-19 16:33:21', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"13\">\n<p>Mt s trang mng x hi tra 20/09 ng ti thng th thnh ng Vn Lm s ngh thi u cho CLB Hi Phng. Tuy nhin, trao i vi VTC News, HLV trng CLB Hi Phng Trng Vit Hong cho bit, ng cha nhn c bt k thng bo no v vic ny v cng khng bit thng tin ny t u ra.</p>\n<p>\"Ti cha c thng tin ny. Vn Lm vn ang xin ngh  H Ni  cha chn\", HLV Trng Vit Hong ni.</p>\n<p>Sau s c b tr l S Mnh e da, th thnh ng Vn Lm  ri khi Hi Phng  m bo an ton. Th thnh Vit kiu sau  c Ph ch tch VFF Trn Quc Tun cu mang khi ng Tun ng   Vn Lm ti  trong tr s Lin on bng  Vit Nam.</p>\n<p>Cng ti y, anh c s h tr iu tr chn thng ca chuyn gia vt l tr liu ngi c Pablo Sawicky ng thi c s dng c s vt cht ca i tuyn Vit Nam tp luyn.</p>\n<p>D tuyn b s k lut ni b Vn Lm khi th thnh ny tr v Hi Phng v t  ri i, song pha i bng t cng cng sng sng to iu kin  Vn Lm n nh tm l, sm tr li thi u.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">Tun Anh i din vi \"thm ha\" khi dnh 4 chn thng lin mt lc</div></div>', 'HLV Trng Vit Hong: \'Cha c thng tin Vn Lm xin ngh  Hi Phng\'', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hlv-truong-viet-hoang-chua-co-thong-tin-van-lam-xin-nghi-o-hai-phong', '', '', '2017-09-19 16:33:21', '2017-09-19 16:33:21', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/hlv-truong-viet-hoang-chua-co-thong-tin-van-lam-xin-nghi-o-hai-phong/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1507', '1', '2017-09-19 16:30:00', '2017-09-19 16:30:00', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"19\">\n<p><span>Hn ci hi xem phim T tng Lu G, bn  rt n tng vi mn \"vy tai\" c bit ca ng. Bn cng  th ng nguy i tai mnh nhng i sao - n c  l 1 ch y.</span>\n<br/></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505878644566.gif\" w=\"600\" h=\"400\" alt=\"&#x110;&#xE2;y l&#xE0; &#x111;i&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1EB7;c bi&#x1EC7;t m&#xE0; 85% ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i tr&#xEA;n th&#x1EBF; gi&#x1EDB;i mu&#x1ED1;n c&#xF3; c&#x169;ng kh&#xF4;ng th&#x1EC3; &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"&#x110;&#xE2;y l&#xE0; &#x111;i&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1EB7;c bi&#x1EC7;t m&#xE0; 85% ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i tr&#xEA;n th&#x1EBF; gi&#x1EDB;i mu&#x1ED1;n c&#xF3; c&#x169;ng kh&#xF4;ng th&#x1EC3; &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"0452b4e0-9db5-11e7-a8db-1d1d88eac0e4\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505878644566.gif\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">T tng Lu G ng nguy i tai trong b phim cng tn.</p></div></div>\n<p>em thc mc i hi gii chuyn gia th c bit rng, tai l 1 b phn c th m ta khng d g iu khin c.</p>\n<p>C tai c trung tm dy thn kinh ring trong cung no v vng ny  con ngi rt nh nn khng \"vy vy\" c nh cc loi cn, mo...</p>\n<p>Nghin cu su hn, gii chuyn gia khng nh, vic iu khin i tai ng nguy ph thuc nhiu vo nhm c tai Auriculares - v ch c 15% dn s th gii mi c kh nng c bit ny m thi.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505878647359.png\" w=\"620\" h=\"849\" alt=\"&#x110;&#xE2;y l&#xE0; &#x111;i&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1EB7;c bi&#x1EC7;t m&#xE0; 85% ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i tr&#xEA;n th&#x1EBF; gi&#x1EDB;i mu&#x1ED1;n c&#xF3; c&#x169;ng kh&#xF4;ng th&#x1EC3; &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" title=\"&#x110;&#xE2;y l&#xE0; &#x111;i&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1EB7;c bi&#x1EC7;t m&#xE0; 85% ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i tr&#xEA;n th&#x1EBF; gi&#x1EDB;i mu&#x1ED1;n c&#xF3; c&#x169;ng kh&#xF4;ng th&#x1EC3; &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"0587d980-9db5-11e7-a370-c9cc62f96717\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505878647359.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Nhm c tai Auriculares - yu t gip tai bn \"vy vy\" c.</p></div></div>\n<p>Nhm c tai Auriculares gm c trc tai - gip tai c ng v pha trc; c trn tai - gip tai ngng ln; v c sau tai - gip tai c ng v pha sau.</p>\n<p>y l phn c pha ngoi tai, c chc nng xoay v iu chnh i tai  tp trung thnh gic v pha nhng m thanh c bit. Ging nh ch mo - s vnh i tai ln  xc nh v tr con mi khi chng rnh chut vy.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-2-1505878647363.gif\" w=\"640\" h=\"360\" alt=\"&#x110;&#xE2;y l&#xE0; &#x111;i&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1EB7;c bi&#x1EC7;t m&#xE0; 85% ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i tr&#xEA;n th&#x1EBF; gi&#x1EDB;i mu&#x1ED1;n c&#xF3; c&#x169;ng kh&#xF4;ng th&#x1EC3; &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" title=\"&#x110;&#xE2;y l&#xE0; &#x111;i&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1EB7;c bi&#x1EC7;t m&#xE0; 85% ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i tr&#xEA;n th&#x1EBF; gi&#x1EDB;i mu&#x1ED1;n c&#xF3; c&#x169;ng kh&#xF4;ng th&#x1EC3; &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"05a859d0-9db5-11e7-a370-c9cc62f96717\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-2-1505878647363.gif\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p>Nhiu ngi cho rng, c tai ny xut hin  hu ht ng vt c v gip chng xc nh v tr con mi.</p>\n<p>Loi ngi xa cng s hu nhm c tai trn nhng v tin ha 1 thi gian di, con ngi ngy nay khng cn vt v sn mi na... nn phn c tai ny tr nn yu v dn bin mt, ch cn xut hin  1 s ngi trn th gii m thi.</p>\n<p><i>Ngun</i>: <b>Cracked, Hearinghealthmatter</b></p>\n<div type=\"link\">Ch g k l: V ming n, t cho u vo \"thng lng\" n 2 ln</div></div>', 'y l iu c bit m 85% ngi trn th gii mun c cng khng th c', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'day-la-dieu-dac-biet-ma-85-nguoi-tren-the-gioi-muon-co-cung-khong-the-duoc', '', '', '2017-09-19 16:30:00', '2017-09-19 16:30:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/day-la-dieu-dac-biet-ma-85-nguoi-tren-the-gioi-muon-co-cung-khong-the-duoc/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
