INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1509', '1', '2017-09-19 16:23:03', '2017-09-19 16:23:03', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"25\">\n<p>Knh truyn hnh <i>NDTV</i> a tin gio vin v gim c mt trng t thc nm  ngoi  th trn Ajitgarh, bang Rajasthan - n  buc n sinh lp 12  li trng vi l do tng tit ri cng hip nn nhn.</p>\n<p> V vic chn ng xy ra trong hn 2 thng tri n khi n sinh trn mang thai.</p>\n<p>Cnh st cho bit nn nhn khng h h rng v chuyn b p ph thai hay cng hip. Tuy nhin, khi tnh trng sc khe tr nn ti t hi cui tun qua, nn nhn mi c a n TP Jaipur, th ph bang Rajasthan. </p>\n<p>N sinh ny c a vo khoa thn kinh ca bnh vin ti 17-9 (gi a phng).</p>\n<p>n khi cc bc s ni vi cha m c gi v qu trnh ph thai \"chui\" m c  tri qua, nn nhn mi k li s vic. \"C gi b phu thut trn 2 ln. V khng c chm sc ng cch v thiu oxy, no ca bnh nhn b tn thng. </p>\n<p>C v nh y l tn thng vnh vin\" - bc s DS Meena, gim c bnh vin, tr li knh <i>NDTV</i>.</p>\n<p><span>Khi thng tin v v vic b phanh phui, cc bc ph huynh gin d yu cu x l ngi trng c khong 400 hc sinh theo hc.</span></p>\n<p><span> Hin ti ngi trng ny  b chnh quyn qun ng ca. Cnh st cho bit gio vin Jagat Gujjar v gim c Jagdish Yadav  b bt v ang b thm vn.</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>Ngoi vic iu tra v cng hip n sinh trn, c quan chc nng cn mun kim tra xem cc nghi phm c nhm vo nhng hc sinh khc khng. </p>\n<p>Tuy nhin, h khng th ghi li li khai ca nn nhn v tnh trng sc khe ca c gi khng cho php.</p>\n<p>Cnh st trng qun Sikar, ng Vinit Kumar, cho bit h cng ang lc sot phng khm ni nn nhn b a n  ph thai.</p>\n<p> (Theo NDTV)</p>\n<div type=\"link\">Nghi n xe khch b k i taxi bn v knh khi chy  Qung Ninh</div></div>', 'N sinh b p ph thai n tn thng no', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nu-sinh-bi-ep-pha-thai-den-ton-thuong-nao', '', '', '2017-09-19 16:23:03', '2017-09-19 16:23:03', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/nu-sinh-bi-ep-pha-thai-den-ton-thuong-nao/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1510', '1', '2017-09-19 16:23:00', '2017-09-19 16:23:00', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"33\">\n<p>Ti Hi ngh, Ban Thng v Thnh y H Ni  trnh  n quy hoch Thnh y nhim k 2020 - 2025, cc chc danh lnh o on i biu Quc hi (BQH), HND, UBND TP H Ni nhim k 2021 - 2026 v cc nhim k tip theo.</p>\n<p> n ny  c Ban Thng v Thnh y tho lun k trn c s r sot, nh gi ton din tnh hnh, phn tch cht lng, nng lc, phm cht i ng cn b Thnh ph; ng thi nghin cu, cn c cc nguyn tc c cu chun b nhn s ti  n nhn s i hi ng b Thnh ph kha XVI v phng hng cng tc nhn s lnh o cp y, on BQH, HND, UBND TP cc nhim k va qua.</p>\n<p>Trn tinh thn trch nhim, pht huy dn ch trong tho lun, bo m nguyn tc tp trung, on kt, khch quan, thng nht, cc i biu  tp trung tho lun, c  kin v gii thiu nhn s vo quy hoch Thnh y v cn b lnh o, qun l nhim k 2020 - 2025, 2021 - 2026 ca Thnh ph.</p>\n<p>Vic thc hin quy trnh quy hoch ny l nhng bc quan trng trong nhim v xy dng i ng cn b nhim k 2020 - 2025, 2021 - 2026 v nhng nhim k tip theo nhm p ng yu cu chun b, o to, bi dng cn b lnh o cp y, lnh o on BQH, HND, UBND TP, xy dng i ng cn b ch cht  phc v nhim v pht trin Th . </p>\n<p>* Xem link gc <b>TI Y</b></p>\n<div type=\"link\">Gia Lai kt lun sai phm chi tip khch ti HND tnh</div></div>', 'H Ni gii thiu nhn s quy hoch lnh o ch cht nhim k 2020-2025', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ha-noi-gioi-thieu-nhan-su-quy-hoach-lanh-dao-chu-chot-nhiem-ky-2020-2025', '', '', '2017-09-19 16:23:00', '2017-09-19 16:23:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/ha-noi-gioi-thieu-nhan-su-quy-hoach-lanh-dao-chu-chot-nhiem-ky-2020-2025/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1511', '1', '2017-09-19 16:22:02', '2017-09-19 16:22:02', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"26\">\n<p>Khong 12h30 hm nay (20/9), mt chic xe  t con lu thng trn ng Tn c Thng, phng Bn Ngh, Qun 1, TP HCM bt ng b cy   bp trong trn ma ln nh trt nc, khin 1 ngi ph n ngi sau xe b thng. </p>\n<p>Theo thng tin ban u, khong thi gian trn, ti x Bnh Quc Tin (30 tui, ng TP HCM) iu khin xe  t mang bin kim sot: 51F - 69538 ch theo mt ngi ph n lu thng trn ng Tn c Thng hng t ng inh Tin Hong v cu Khnh Hi.</p>\n<p>Khi n khc cua trn ng Tn c Thng th bt ng b mt cy c th bn ng bt gc, ng  bp  t. Ngi ph n ngi pha sau  t b thng c ngi dn a i cp cu.</p>\n<p>Ti hin trng trng, chic xe  t b  bp, bin dng, nhiu mnh knh vng t tung, lc lng chc nng ang phong ta hin trng  x l s c.</p>\n<p>c bit, cy c th trn l cy s kh, c ng knh 1,50 m, cao gn 20 m. Khi xy ra s c, tri c ma ln v gi git mnh.</p>\n<p>Nhn tin bo, lc lng chc nng cng nhn vin cy xanh c mt x l hin trng. n hn 14h cng ngy, hin trng vn cha c gii quyt xong./.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">Ngi \"cu c c mp  vnh H Long\": Phi gh cht v mt 2 gi a c ln thuyn</div></div>', 'Ma ln, cy   bp  t trn ng ph Si Gn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'mua-lon-cay-do-de-bep-o-to-tren-duong-pho-sai-gon', '', '', '2017-09-19 16:22:02', '2017-09-19 16:22:02', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/mua-lon-cay-do-de-bep-o-to-tren-duong-pho-sai-gon/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1512', '1', '2017-09-19 16:15:00', '2017-09-19 16:15:00', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"31\">\n<p>Thng 9/1997, mt m hnh mu xe tng Black Eagle ln u tin c trng by ti bui trin lm qun i VTTV ln 2  Omsk. </p>\n<p>Black Eagle l thnh qu ca vic nng cp mu tng chin u T-80U khi nh sn xut vn gi b khung thn v thm vo mt cp bnh b sung. Ngi ta cn thay th thp pho c bng b thp pho mi, c ln. Black Eagle hin l loi tng chin u thp nht th gii.</p>\n<p>Thng s k thut ca Black Eagle n nay vn cn nm trong vng b n, ch bit rng n c trng lng c tnh t 50 - 65 tn, di 7 m, rng 3,6 m v c bit l chiu cao ch 2 m - iu ny a n tr thnh chic xe tng chin u ch lc ln nht trong lch s.</p>\n<p>Tuy \"ln\", nhng sc mnh ca xe tng Black Eagle l khng th xem thng, nu khng mun ni l mnh khng khip. </p>\n<p>c pht trin trn c s dng tng T-80U nn thn xe ca Black Eagle c nt tng ng ln, nhng di hn v c nhiu hn mt cp bnh chu nng  kp li cch xa pha sau xe. Gip composite ca n rt dy (400 mm) v trang b gip phn ng n Kaktus.  dc pha trc xe v thp pho c thit k  tng ti a  bo v.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505882321240.jpg\" w=\"600\" h=\"395\" alt=\"Si&#xEA;u t&#x103;ng l&#xF9;n nh&#x1EA5;t trong l&#x1ECB;ch s&#x1EED; c&#x1EE7;a Nga c&#xF3; s&#x1EE9;c m&#x1EA1;nh kh&#x1EE7;ng khi&#x1EBF;p nh&#x1B0; th&#x1EBF; n&#xE0;o? - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"Si&#xEA;u t&#x103;ng l&#xF9;n nh&#x1EA5;t trong l&#x1ECB;ch s&#x1EED; c&#x1EE7;a Nga c&#xF3; s&#x1EE9;c m&#x1EA1;nh kh&#x1EE7;ng khi&#x1EBF;p nh&#x1B0; th&#x1EBF; n&#xE0;o? - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"93fe5d30-9dbd-11e7-83b9-859caeefd647\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505882321240.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"2\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Tuy \"ln\", nhng sc mnh ca xe tng Black Eagle l khng th xem thng</p></div></div>\n<p>Ngoi ra, khi a vo trang b, Black Eagle c th trang b h thng phng v ch ng Drozd-2 hoc Arena v h thng gy nhiu quang hc Shtora-6 v Shtora-8B. C mt s ngun tin cn cho rng Black Ealge c trang b radar c th pht hin my bay v trc thng cch n 16 km.</p>\n<p>V ha lc, nguyn mu u tin ca Black Eagle xut hin vi pho chnh 125 mm 2A46M. Tuy nhin, k hoch ca LKZ v sau l KTBM mun lp cho n khu 135 mm hoc 140 mm hoc 152 mm vi tm bn hiu qu n 10 km. Bn cnh cc loi n xuyn gip thng thng, pho 152 mm cn phng c tn la chng tng qua nng.</p>\n<p>Bn cnh , Black Eagle cn c trang b h thng np n t ng kiu mi c lp t trong phn khung lt ca thp pho, c th np n rt nhanh gip tng tc  bn lin tip (10-12 vin/pht). Hm n ca i bng en c thit k tch bit vi khoang chnh, v vy nu nh hm n b n th t li cng khng b mnh n vng trng.</p>\n<p>ng ch , Black Eagle dng thp pho \"ngoi c\" hnh hp c thit k ging phng Ty. Nng pho ln km n cng khung b di hn cho nn Black Ealge phi s hu ng c cc khe. </p>\n<p>Nh sn xut cng trang b cho siu tng Black Eagle mt ng c tuc bin kh khong 1.500 m lc. Vi bnh cha nhin liu b sung, mu tng ny c th di chuyn trong trong phm vi 1.000 km.</p>\n<p>Tuy s hu nhiu u im v l nim t ho ca nc Nga, d n siu tng Black Eagle vn \"cht yu\" v cng ty chu trch nhim thit k siu tng  trong tnh cnh ph sn nm 2002.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">Pho binh Nga \"n n\" vo tu chin Trung Quc ti cng Vladivostok</div></div>', 'Siu tng \"ln nht trong lch s\" ca Nga c sc mnh khng khip nh th no?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'sieu-tang-lun-nhat-trong-lich-su-cua-nga-co-suc-manh-khung-khiep-nhu-the-nao', '', '', '2017-09-19 16:15:00', '2017-09-19 16:15:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/sieu-tang-lun-nhat-trong-lich-su-cua-nga-co-suc-manh-khung-khiep-nhu-the-nao/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
