INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1514', '1', '2017-09-19 16:10:51', '2017-09-19 16:10:51', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"50\">\n<p><span>Lin quan n v vic khch hng   Nng \"t\" i l Nissan  Nng bn xe gian ln chiu 18/9, phng vin nhn c thng tin t pha Cng ty TNHH Nissan Vit Nam.</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>Theo ni dung m pha Nissan Vit Nam cung cp, khch hng k hp ng mua xe mu trng, mi 100% ti i l Nissan  Nng, sau  khch hng pht hin xe c mu sn gc l mu xanh, c ph lp sn trng bn ngoi v khch hng cho rng y l phin bn dnh cho taxi.</p>\n<p>Sau khi nhn thng tin, pha Cng ty TCIE  nh my lp rp Nissan Sunny ti Vit Nam phn hi nh sau: Tt c xe  t Cng ty TCIE sn xut bn trn th trng l xe mi 100%.</p>\n<p>Thng s k thut v cht lng xe tun theo tiu chun Nissan v theo Giy chng nhn cht lng kiu loi  c c quan c thm quyn  Vit Nam cp.</p>\n<p>\"Cng ty TCIE khng sn xut phin bn no phc v ring cho taxi. i l Nissan  Nng s gii thch cho khch hng c bit nhm gii quyt dt im cc khiu ni ca khch hng theo ng quy trnh v chnh sch ca Nissan\", ni dung pha Nissan Vit Nam cho bit.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505898584884.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"495\" alt=\"V&#x1EE5; nghi v&#x1EA5;n mua xe m&#x1EDB;i b&#x1ECB; b&#xE1;n cho taxi c&#x169;, &#x111;&#x1EA1;i l&#xFD; mu&#x1ED1;n b&#x1ED3;i th&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;ng 80 tri&#x1EC7;u &#x111;&#x1ED3;ng nh&#x1B0;ng kh&#xE1;ch h&#xE0;ng t&#x1EEB; ch&#x1ED1;i - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"V&#x1EE5; nghi v&#x1EA5;n mua xe m&#x1EDB;i b&#x1ECB; b&#xE1;n cho taxi c&#x169;, &#x111;&#x1EA1;i l&#xFD; mu&#x1ED1;n b&#x1ED3;i th&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;ng 80 tri&#x1EC7;u &#x111;&#x1ED3;ng nh&#x1B0;ng kh&#xE1;ch h&#xE0;ng t&#x1EEB; ch&#x1ED1;i - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"72a0d750-9de3-11e7-99f0-ebffd5c9ed61\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505898584884.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"6\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Anh L Thnh Ti (chng ch An) ch ch vt nt ca mu sn xe sau hn mt thng s dng. Vt nt ca sn l ra bn trong l mu xanh. Anh Ti cho bit: \"y l li nghim trng, chng t chic xe ny  b nh tro, sn ph li. Ti c bit, thc cht  l chic xe phin bn t hng ca taxi, c ngy trang li  giao cho khch hng nh l xe gia nh. y l hnh vi gian ln, cn phi x l mt cch nghim khc\". nh: c Hong</p></div></div>\n<p>Trc , v chng ch Dng Th Thy An (tr ng Hong Diu, qun Hi Chu,  Nng) v anh Hong Vn Li (tr phng Chnh Gin, qun Thanh Kh) c mua xe Nissan Sunny 1.5XL ti i l Nissan  Nng (875 Nguyn Hu Th, qun Cm L,  Nng).</p>\n<p>Trong qu trnh s dng, nhng ngi ni trn pht hin ra chic xe m i l giao cho h c sn pha trong l mu xanh, c ph mt lp sn trng  bn ngoi.</p>\n<p>\"y l li nghim trng, chng t chic xe ny  b nh tro, sn ph li. Ti c bit, thc cht  l chic xe phin bn t hng ca taxi, c ngy trang li  giao cho khch hng nh l xe gia nh. y l hnh vi gian ln, cn phi x l mt cch nghim khc\", v chng ch An bc xc ni.</p>\n<p>i din i l Nissan  Nng l ng L Ch Thin, Ph Tng G Cng ty CP  t Quang Phi Hng cho bit nu li sn phm th chng ti s sa cha min ph v ang nm trong din bo hnh.</p>\n<p>\"C th v hai xe ny th s c sn li theo ng tiu chun ca hng. Trong qu trnh ch sn xe, i l sn sng cho khch hng mn xe khc  i li. Tuy nhin, khch hng li mun i xe mi hoc tr tin li. Nhng khi chng ti dn i cho xem xe mi  i li th mt s khch li khng chu, mun ly tin li. </p>\n<p>Gi tr xe li ch c nh my mi quyt nh c, chng ti l nh phn phi, nu xe b li, h hng th s bo dng, bo hnh thi. Nu hai bn gii quyt khng tha ng c th ra Ta. Quyt nh ca Ta l quyt nh cui cng. Chng ti cng mun gii quyt dt im\", ng Thin cho bit.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505898586069.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"454\" alt=\"V&#x1EE5; nghi v&#x1EA5;n mua xe m&#x1EDB;i b&#x1ECB; b&#xE1;n cho taxi c&#x169;, &#x111;&#x1EA1;i l&#xFD; mu&#x1ED1;n b&#x1ED3;i th&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;ng 80 tri&#x1EC7;u &#x111;&#x1ED3;ng nh&#x1B0;ng kh&#xE1;ch h&#xE0;ng t&#x1EEB; ch&#x1ED1;i - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" title=\"V&#x1EE5; nghi v&#x1EA5;n mua xe m&#x1EDB;i b&#x1ECB; b&#xE1;n cho taxi c&#x169;, &#x111;&#x1EA1;i l&#xFD; mu&#x1ED1;n b&#x1ED3;i th&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;ng 80 tri&#x1EC7;u &#x111;&#x1ED3;ng nh&#x1B0;ng kh&#xE1;ch h&#xE0;ng t&#x1EEB; ch&#x1ED1;i - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"733af470-9de3-11e7-a370-c9cc62f96717\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505898586069.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Anh Li bn chic xe Nissan Sunny 1.5XL m anh cho rng mnh b la!. nh: c Hong</p></div></div>\n<p>Sau hn mt tun, lin lc li vi khch hng, anh Li cho bit  c bui lm vic li vi i l v hai bn ng  k vo bin bn cam kt \"n b\". Theo , pha i l chp nhn n b thit hi cho anh Li 80 triu ng. \"Ti c k vo bin bn, nhng cha nhn tin\", anh Li ni.</p>\n<p>Cng mc n b cho v chng ch An nh trng hp anh Li, nhng v chng ch An khng ly s tin ny. \"Chng ti buc i l phi hon tin li cho chng ti ch khng n b\", ch An cho bit.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">15h chiu nay, gi xng tng ln th 5 lin tip</div></div>', 'V nghi vn mua xe mi b bn cho taxi c, i l mun bi thng 80 triu ng nhng khch hng t chi', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vu-nghi-van-mua-xe-moi-bi-ban-cho-taxi-cu-dai-ly-muon-boi-thuong-80-trieu-dong-nhung-khach-hang-tu-choi', '', '', '2017-09-19 16:10:51', '2017-09-19 16:10:51', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/vu-nghi-van-mua-xe-moi-bi-ban-cho-taxi-cu-dai-ly-muon-boi-thuong-80-trieu-dong-nhung-khach-hang-tu-choi/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
