INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1531', '1', '2017-09-19 11:45:53', '2017-09-19 11:45:53', '<div itemprop=\"articleBody\" readability=\"23\">\n<div readability=\"3\">\n<p><strong>8 \"tr l ao lng v vt HCV\": Ch nh khin SEA Games 29 \"k l cha\"</strong></p>\n<p><strong>ng  nn th thao khu vc mang hn danh ao lng na</strong></p>\n<p><strong>5 chic HCV lch s ca Vit Nam  SEA Games 29</strong></p></div>\n<p><strong>SEA Games 29 </strong> kt thc nhng nhng d m v nhng chuyn bn l ca gii u vn cha ht nng. V mi y n lt vn  chia tin thng ca cc VV ot huy chng ca on th thao Singapore  b xi ln.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Ch&#x1EA5;n &#x111;&#x1ED9;ng &#x201C;ao l&#xE0;ng&#x201D; SEA Games: Chia ti&#x1EC1;n th&#x1B0;&#x1EDF;ng &amp;#34;n&#xF3;ng&amp;#34; &#x1EDF; Singapore - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-08-31/1504192042-sea-games3-660.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Chuyn chia tin thng sau SEA Games 29 gy ra scandal  Singapore</p>\n<p>Lin on in kinh Singapore mi y  b t co c nhng \"d ngh\" v tin thng ca cc VV ot HCV  SEA Games 2017 va qua. Nh v ch marathon Soh Rui Yong  gi n khiu ni ti Hi ng Olympic quc gia Singapore, cho bit 20% s tin thng m anh ginh c nh chin thng ti Malaysia  b yu cu chuyn ti cho Lin on in kinh Singapore.</p>\n<p>Theo mt chng trnh c tn Gii thng triu , Lin on in kinh Singapore s trch ra 20% s tin thng ca VV ot huy chng  dng vo cng tc hun luyn v pht trin c s h tng tp luyn. Soh Rui Yong  ginh c 10.000 dollar Singapore t HCV  SEA Games 29 v anh s buc phi a 2.000 dollar <em>Singapore</em> cho Lin on.</p>\n<p>Soh cho t Today Online bit: Ti  quyt nh phn ng vi lut ca lin on do s u  ni b, qun l yu km v thiu h tr VV ca lin on in kinh Singapore khi cc VV i thi u. Nu 20% s tin thng ca ti l biu hin ca s thin ch v s gip  ca lin on cng nh tm nhn tng lai, ti khng th a s tin ny cho h khi m h t ra thiu trung thc.</p>\n<p>L th ca Soh  nhanh chng c nhiu VV khc ng h. Shanti Pereira, ngi ot HCV ni dung 200m n  SEA Games 28, cho bit HLV ca c v gim c k thut ca Lin on in kinh Volker Herrmann  ci nhau d di xung quanh a im tp luyn, v Pereira c lc b da ui khi i chy 4x100m tip sc n.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><img alt=\"Ch&#x1EA5;n &#x111;&#x1ED9;ng &#x201C;ao l&#xE0;ng&#x201D; SEA Games: Chia ti&#x1EC1;n th&#x1B0;&#x1EDF;ng &amp;#34;n&#xF3;ng&amp;#34; &#x1EDF; Singapore - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505713189-mg_0939-e1434133068702-660.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Soh Rui Yong, ngi phn i kch lit lut 20% ca lin on in kinh Singapore</p>\n<p>Dipna Lim-Prasad, ngi ot HCB  ni dung 400m v 400m vt ro, cho bit HLV ca c l Luis Cunha cng  b Herrmann e da trong qu trnh chun b cho SEA Games.</p>\n<p>Soh  xut rng thay v phi np, anh v cc VV ot HCV  SEA Games 29 nn c quyn c nhn  10.000 dollar Singapore, hoc 20% s tin ca h s c tng cho mt qu t thin m h la chn.</p>\n<p>i tuyn in kinh Singapore  k <u>SEA Games 29</u>  ginh 2 HCV trn tng s 45 b huy chng. u nm nay Lin on in kinh Singapore  phi t chc bu Hi ng ch tch mi, sau khi n ra scandal pht hin mt y vin  ngm ra lnh cho th k ca mnh thu thp bng chng  lt gh ca ch tch ng nhim.</p><table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"500\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" readability=\"16\">\n<p>SEA Games 29 din ra \"thnh cng\" trong mt nc ch nh Malaysia nhng bo gii bn ngoi th khng cm thy thng li ny c cht g thuyt phc v cng tc t chc, c bit l mt s v trng ti thin v ch nh.</p>\n<p>T Bangkok Post ca Thi Lan tng t ra chua cay: Vi rt nhiu quan chc, vn ng vin, nh bo v khn gi Thi Lan, SEA Games 29 l k SEA Games ti t nht v mt t chc ln trng ti.</p>\n<p>Bangkok Post sau   cp ti vic Malaysia  cho kh nhiu mn l xut hin  d b tng s huy chng vng. Mn ua trt bng l mt trong s , ln u thi u  SEA Games v mang li cho Malaysia 3 HCV.</p>\n<p>Bi vit ca Bangkok Post, di nhan  Mt truyn thng xu x c tip din  Malaysia, cng tha nhn rng vic nc ch nh tm  mi cch  ng u bng tng sp huy chng l mt vn   tn ti t lu, rng c Thi Lan cng khng khc g. y l mt trng hp kiu nc khc lm c, nc mnh cng lm c, bi vit t cu kt.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Ch&#x1EA5;n &#x111;&#x1ED9;ng &#x201C;ao l&#xE0;ng&#x201D; SEA Games: Chia ti&#x1EC1;n th&#x1B0;&#x1EDF;ng &amp;#34;n&#xF3;ng&amp;#34; &#x1EDF; Singapore - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-08-31/1504192075-46556-660.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Sau SEA Games 29, Bangkok Post tng c bi vit ta : \"Mt truyn thng xu x tip tc  Malaysia\"</p></td></tr></tbody></table><div>\n<div>\n<div><img alt=\"&#x110;i&#x1EC1;n kinh Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam: &#x110;&#x1EEB;ng l&#xF3;a m&#x1EAF;t v&#x1EDB;i ng&#xF4;i &#x111;&#x1EA7;u khu v&#x1EF1;c\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-08-30/1504104641-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\n<div>\n<div>in kinh Vit Nam: ng la mt vi ngi u khu vc</div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p>in kinh Vit Nam khng c php ng qun trn chin thng sau SEA Games 29.</p></div>\n<div>Bm xem &gt;&gt;</div></div></div></div>\n<p></p></div>', 'Chn ng ao lng SEA Games: Chia tin thng \"nng\"  Singapore', '<div><a href=\"http://www.24h.com.vn/the-thao/sea-games-29-te-hai-tiep-tuc-truyen-thong-xau-xi-c101a900217.html\" title=\"Ch&#7845;n &#273;&#7897;ng &ldquo;ao l&agrave;ng&rdquo; SEA Games: Chia ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng &amp;#34;n&oacute;ng&amp;#34; &#7903; Singapore\"><img width=\"130\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-08-31/1504192133-sea-games3-640.jpg\" alt=\"Ch&#7845;n &#273;&#7897;ng &ldquo;ao l&agrave;ng&rdquo; SEA Games: Chia ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng &amp;#34;n&oacute;ng&amp;#34; &#7903; Singapore\" title=\"Ch&#7845;n &#273;&#7897;ng &ldquo;ao l&agrave;ng&rdquo; SEA Games: Chia ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng &amp;#34;n&oacute;ng&amp;#34; &#7903; Singapore\"></a><br>(Tin th&#7875; thao) Chuy&#7879;n chia ti&#7873;n th&#432;&#7903;ng &#7903; SEA Games 29 &#273;&atilde; g&acirc;y ra scandal l&#7899;n v&#7899;i th&#7875; thao Singapore.</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chan-dong-ao-lang-sea-games-chia-tien-thuong-nong-o-singapore', '', '', '2017-09-19 11:45:53', '2017-09-19 11:45:53', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/chan-dong-ao-lang-sea-games-chia-tien-thuong-nong-o-singapore/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
