INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1537', '1', '2017-09-19 06:17:50', '2017-09-19 06:17:50', '<div readability=\"32\">\n<div readability=\"5\">\n<p><strong>Derby bng r Si Gn \"te la\": SAO Vit kiu  mu &amp; nhp vin</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Bng xp hng tennis 18/9: Federer - Nadal tranh s 1, kch n hi hay</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Sharapova l qu kh c c, mc  c ca n ch m nhn</strong></p></div>\n<p><em>Video Nadal nng cup v ch Grand Slam th 16</em></p>\n<p><em>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div data-config=\"id=zplayer_1dd491&amp;flash=%2Fzplayer%2FzPlayerView.swf%3Fver%3D20170920&amp;hideNextPrevButtons=1&amp;ad_skipButtonAd=PREROLL,POSTROLL&amp;hideExtraButtons=1&amp;ad_skipButtonTime=5&amp;ad_preroll=https%3A%2F%2Fpubads.g.doubleclick.net%2Fgampad%2Fads%3Fsz%3D528x297%26iu%3D%2F124557882%2F24h%2Fvn%2Fdesktop%2Fsport%2Fpreroll%26impl%3Ds%26gdfp_req%3D1%26env%3Dvp%26output%3Dvast%26unviewed_position_start%3D1%26url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.24h.com.vn%252Fthe-thao%252Fnadal-con-duong-tro-thanh-vi-dai-nhat-moi-thoi-dai-c101a904288.html%26description_url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.24h.com.vn%252Fthe-thao%252Fnadal-con-duong-tro-thanh-vi-dai-nhat-moi-thoi-dai-c101a904288.html%26correlator%3D1505958313%26ambient%3D1&amp;ad_prerollOnly=0&amp;ad_prerollTime=31&amp;ad_prerollType=adsense&amp;ad_overlay=https%3A%2F%2Fpubads.g.doubleclick.net%2Fgampad%2Fads%3Fsz%3D528x60%26iu%3D%2F124557882%2F24h%2Fvn%2Fdesktop%2Fsport%2Foverlay%26impl%3Ds%26gdfp_req%3D1%26env%3Dvp%26output%3Dvast%26unviewed_position_start%3D1%26url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.24h.com.vn%252Fthe-thao%252Fnadal-con-duong-tro-thanh-vi-dai-nhat-moi-thoi-dai-c101a904288.html%26description_url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.24h.com.vn%252Fthe-thao%252Fnadal-con-duong-tro-thanh-vi-dai-nhat-moi-thoi-dai-c101a904288.html%26correlator%3D1505958313%26ambient%3D1&amp;ad_overlayTime=15&amp;ad_overlayStart=10&amp;ad_overlayType=adsense&amp;ad_postroll=https%3A%2F%2Fpubads.g.doubleclick.net%2Fgampad%2Fads%3Fsz%3D528x297%26iu%3D%2F124557882%2F24h%2Fvn%2Fdesktop%2Fsport%2Fpostroll%26impl%3Ds%26gdfp_req%3D1%26env%3Dvp%26output%3Dvast%26unviewed_position_start%3D1%26url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.24h.com.vn%252Fthe-thao%252Fnadal-con-duong-tro-thanh-vi-dai-nhat-moi-thoi-dai-c101a904288.html%26description_url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.24h.com.vn%252Fthe-thao%252Fnadal-con-duong-tro-thanh-vi-dai-nhat-moi-thoi-dai-c101a904288.html%26correlator%3D1505958313%26ambient%3D1&amp;ad_postrollOnly=0&amp;ad_postrollTime=30&amp;ad_postrollType=adsense&amp;file=http://video.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/videoclip/2017-09-11/1505085985-traocup_usopen_01.mp4&amp;fileAlt=&amp;image=http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-11/1505085985-traocup_usopen_01.jpg&amp;volume=40&amp;ad_volume=40&amp;mute=mute&amp;ad_mute=mute&amp;autoNext=6&amp;title=Nadal &amp; con &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;ng tr&#x1EDF; th&#xE0;nh v&#x129; &#x111;&#x1EA1;i nh&#x1EA5;t m&#x1ECD;i th&#x1EDD;i &#x111;&#x1EA1;i&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;postId=254e2d976250331b08269059b6202c05&amp;newsId=904288&amp;ad_skipButton=1\"></div></div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div></div></em></p>\n<p>Rafael Nadal mang trong mnh nhng hoi bo ln lao. N vt xa mc tiu tr thnh c c cu bi trong s nghip ca mnh nh Novak Djokovic. N cng khng tm thng Andy Murray - ngi c s nghip phn u ly mt ln c leo ln ngi v s 1 th gii. Vi <strong>Nadal</strong>, mc tiu ca anh l vt qua Roger Federer ca hin ti v Pete Sampras ca qu kh  tr thnh tay vt v i nht mi thi i.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"Nadal &amp; con &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;ng tr&#x1EDF; th&#xE0;nh v&#x129; &#x111;&#x1EA1;i nh&#x1EA5;t m&#x1ECD;i th&#x1EDD;i &#x111;&#x1EA1;i - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505732236-federer-nadal-australian-open-2017-trophy.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Nadal v Federer trong cuc ua tay vt xut sc nht mi thi i</p>\n<p>Cng nh hoi bo y m anh  v ang c s tr li chi la trong nm 2017. Hy tng tng mt tay vt nh cao, 2 nm lin giam mnh trong nhng tht bi cng chn thng lin min, cn bao nhiu ng lc quyt tm  c th tr li mt cch ngon mc nh Nadal? C nhn vo Novak Djokovic  hiu rng, tr li ngai vng sau nhiu nm lu lc v chn thng kh khn bit nhng no.</p>\n<p>Nadal, sau chc v ch US Open 2017, n hm nay  s hu 16 danh hiu Grand Slam. Anh cn cch v tr tay vt ginh nhiu chc v ch Grand Slam nht lch s 3 danh hiu na. D nhin, i th ln nht s nghip ca Rafa,  chnh l Roger Federer ang nm gi k lc ny. Tay vt ngi Thy S l mt thin ti thc s trong lnh vc ca mnh. Nhng sau US Open, gii m iu nhn ra k th s 1 ca Tu tc hnh -  l thi gian, ang dn chin thng.  tui 36, ngy FedEx gii ngh c l khng cn xa na.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p>Nhng <em>Nadal </em>th khc. Tay vt ngi Ty Ban Nha ny ch mi bc sang tui 31. Trong th gii ca cc tay vt tennis hin ti, khng c nhiu i th  kh nng nh bi Rafa. Nu nh bn thn Federer gi y cng tht th trc Nadal, th hai tay vt cn li trong Big Four l Djokovic v Murray cng cha bit n bao gi mi tr li. V nu c, h c l cng khng d g h gc c Rafa.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n</p><div>\n<div><img alt=\"Nadal &amp; con &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;ng tr&#x1EDF; th&#xE0;nh v&#x129; &#x111;&#x1EA1;i nh&#x1EA5;t m&#x1ECD;i th&#x1EDD;i &#x111;&#x1EA1;i - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505732271-14.jpg\" /><div>\n<div><img alt=\"Nadal &amp; con &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;ng tr&#x1EDF; th&#xE0;nh v&#x129; &#x111;&#x1EA1;i nh&#x1EA5;t m&#x1ECD;i th&#x1EDD;i &#x111;&#x1EA1;i - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\" /></div></div></div></div>\n<p>Nadal th hin phong  ng kinh ngc trong nm 2017</p>\n<p>Trong khi , cc tay vt tr hn li khng cho thy nhng bc tin  ln  h gc mt nh v ch thc th. Alexander Zverev c l l tay vt tim nng nht, nhng im yu ca Zverev chnh l kinh nghim nh cao. D nhin, no ai c th i hi mt chng trai mi 20 tui kinh nghim v bn lnh trong nhng gii u ln. V  l nguyn nhn dn n tht bi ca Zverev  cc gii u quan trng trong nm 2017 ny.</p>\n<p>Ch i Zverev trng thnh cng kh tng t nh ch Marin Cilic, Dominic Thiem, Grigor Dimitrov hay Milos Raonic to nn sc bt trong s nghip vy. Tt c u cn n thi gian, thm ch l rt nhiu. Cho n ngy , c l Rafael <u>Nadal </u> chm ngng 20 danh hiu Grand Slam, thm ch vt qua Roger Federer v Pete Sampras  tr thnh tay vt xut sc nht mi thi i.</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><img alt=\"Tin HOT th&#x1EC3; thao 18/9: Hamilton t&#x1EF1; tin &#x111;&#xE1;nh b&#x1EA1;i Vettel, v&#xF4; &#x111;&#x1ECB;ch F1 n&#x103;m 2017\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505672346-hamilton-640x480.jpg\" /></div>\n<div>\n<div>Tin HOT th thao 18/9: Hamilton t tin nh bi Vettel, v ch F1 nm 2017</div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p>Lewis Hamilton xem nh  ct ui c knh ch Sebastian Vettel.</p></div>\n<div>Bm xem &gt;&gt;</div></div></div></div>\n<p></p></div>', 'Nadal & con ng tr thnh v i nht mi thi i', '<div><a href=\"http://www.24h.com.vn/the-thao/nadal-con-duong-tro-thanh-vi-dai-nhat-moi-thoi-dai-c101a904288.html\" title=\"Nadal &amp; con &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh v&#297; &#273;&#7841;i nh&#7845;t m&#7885;i th&#7901;i &#273;&#7841;i\"><img width=\"130\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505732442-rafael-nadal-trophy-ap-1640x480.jpg\" alt=\"Nadal &amp; con &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh v&#297; &#273;&#7841;i nh&#7845;t m&#7885;i th&#7901;i &#273;&#7841;i\" title=\"Nadal &amp; con &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng tr&#7903; th&agrave;nh v&#297; &#273;&#7841;i nh&#7845;t m&#7885;i th&#7901;i &#273;&#7841;i\"></a><br>Rafael Nadal th&#7875; hi&#7879;n s&#7913;c m&#7841;nh v&#432;&#7907;t tr&#7897;i trong n&#259;m 2017. Xa h&#417;n, tay v&#7907;t ng&#432;&#7901;i T&acirc;y Ban Nha c&oacute; th&#7875; t&#7841;o ra nh&#7919;ng &#273;i&#7873;u phi th&#432;&#7901;ng cho &#273;&#7871;n khi anh g&aacute;c v&#7907;t.</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nadal-con-duong-tro-tha