INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1541', '1', '2017-09-19 07:00:00', '2017-09-19 07:00:00', '<div itemprop=\"articleBody\" readability=\"81\">\n<p><strong>Th gin v truyn cm hng t chy</strong></p>\n<p><em>Nhn thy nhiu ngi trong cng ng tham gia chy  truyn cho ti rt nhiu cm hng. By gi, ti c th ra ngoi v chy 20 dm vo mt bui sng ch nht no  ngon lnh, </em>ngi sng lp mng x hi Facebook Mark Zuckenberg cho bit v li ch m marathon  mang li cho mnh.</p>\n<p>Nm 2016, t ph cng ngh ny t t ra th thch cho mnh mang tn Mt nm chy b. Mi ngy, anh chy t nht mt dm d cng vic c bn rn c no. Khng ch chy mt mnh, Mark cn lp ra c mt nhm cng khai  chia s v hnh trnh ca mnh cng nh nhng iu th v m n mang n.</p>\n<p>Ch sau mt thi gian ngn, ngi sng lp Facebook thch th cho bit vic chy b gip u c ca anh thoi mi hn, tinh thn lc quan, to thm nng lng cng nh xua tan nhng mt mi trong cng vic. i vi anh, mn th thao n gin ny l cch tt nht  nng cao sc khe cng nh rn luyn tinh thn.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"Marathon: Ch&#x1EA1;y &#x111;&#x1EC3; r&#xE8;n &#xFD; ch&#xED; v&#xE0; tinh th&#x1EA7;n v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t kh&#xF3; - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-20/1505877863-marathon-chay-de-ren-y-chi-va-tinh-than-vuot-kho--1-.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Ngi chy marathon lun c nhng mc tiu mi  vt qua</p>\n<p>Khng phi ngu nhin, hu ht ngi thnh t trn th gii u thng xuyn chy marathon. Chy vi km l cch tt nht  bt u mt ngy mi, gip mi ngi c u c thoi mi, minh mn, qua  nng cao hiu qu cng vic. Xa hn, vic duy tr thng xuyn cn gip mi ngi trnh xa cc thi quen xu.</p>\n<p>C nhiu nghin cu khoa hc cho thy li ch ln nht ca vic chy b l gim nguy c bnh tt. Nhng ngi chy b thng xuyn t c kh nng mc cc loi bnh l nh bo ph, huyt p, tim mch, tiu ng, cholesterol, ung th, vim khp Vi ph n, chy marathon l phng php tuyt vi  gim cn, to nn vc dng cn i.</p>\n<p><strong>Rn luyn  ch v xy dng tinh thn vt kh</strong></p>\n<p>V hnh thc, marathon rt n gin. Nhng mun thc hin, mi ngi cn c  ch, s t tin v k hoch r rng.  hon thnh mi chng ua t 10 km cho n hng chc km, mi ngi chy phi c lng quyt tm, tinh thn vt kh, bn b v n lc ht mnh. Kt qu t c l phn thng v gi i vi tt c mi ngi.</p>\n<p> Vit Nam, phong tro marathon ang ngy cng lan rng, vic chy dn tr thnh la chn yu thch ca nhiu ngi bi nhng li ch to ln m n mang li. i vi nhiu ngi, chy cn gip h rn luyn tnh k lut, xy dng mc tiu r rng, t , thay i bn thn cng nh thay i cch nhn nhn cuc sng. Khi no mun t thch thc gii hn bn thn, h bt u mt cung ng, mt c ly chy mi. Vi tinh thn , mi ngi cng nhau s to thnh mt cng ng khe mnh, tin ti mt x hi c tinh thn th thao, kht khao tin v pha trc.  l gi tr cao p nht m marathon mang li cho mi ngi. Ch cn c  ch, bt c ai cng c th tp luyn mn th thao ny.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"Marathon: Ch&#x1EA1;y &#x111;&#x1EC3; r&#xE8;n &#xFD; ch&#xED; v&#xE0; tinh th&#x1EA7;n v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t kh&#xF3; - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-20/1505877863-marathon-chay-de-ren-y-chi-va-tinh-than-vuot-kho--2-.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Cc gii marathon l c hi tuyt vi  qung b cho cc a im t chc</p>\n<p>n nay, ti Vit Nam  c nhiu gii chy b c t chc nh HCMC Run, Vietnam Challenge Trail Run, Danang Intenational Marathon, Vietnam Mountain Marathon Nhng nhn chung, con s ny cn t so vi nhu cu ca mi ngi trong bi cnh cc nhm cng ng c chung nim am m trn ng chy c thnh lp ngy cng nhiu nh Vietrunners, LDR (Long Distance Runners), DNR (DaNang Runners), HCR (Hue Citadel Runners), Runclub, SRC</p>\n<p><strong>C hi tuyt vi  qung b hnh nh a phng</strong></p>\n<p>Vi nhng nh t chc, mn th thao ny l c hi tuyt vi  qung b hnh nh ca mt a phng, doanh nghip ti khch du lch cc nc. Trn th gii, c khng t nhng gii ln n rt ln do cc t chc, doanh nghip ti tr nh ING New York City Marathon, Bank of America Chicago Marathon. y u l 2 trong 6 gii marathon chnh ln nht ca th gii, hay Standard Chartered Marathon c t chc trn khong 10 thnh ph khp chu .</p>\n<p>Tuy nhin,  Vit Nam, mi lin kt gia cc t chc  hnh thnh cc gii marathon quy m cha cao, cha c cc gii c doanh nghip ng hnh qua nhiu nm, xuyn sut  to nn im nhn. Nu c nhng gii chy quc t quy m c t chc  cc thnh ph ln, nhng im n du lch ca Vit Nam nh H Ni, Tp. H Ch Minh,  Nng chng ta c th gip qung b hnh nh n tng v Vit Nam n vi th gii v qua , to nn phong tro c nh hng rng khp, truyn ti nhng thng ip sng tch cc n mi ngi. Bi marathon khng n thun l vic x giy ra chy, m  l mt hnh trnh  chng ta qua tng bc vt qua chnh mnh v hng n nhng mc tiu ln hn trong cuc sng vn lun i hi lng kin tr v n lc.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p></div>', 'Marathon: Chy  rn  ch v tinh thn vt kh', '<div><a href=\"http://www.24h.com.vn/the-thao/marathon-chay-de-ren-y-chi-va-tinh-than-vuot-kho-c101a904672.html\" title=\"Marathon: Ch&#7841;y &#273;&#7875; r&egrave;n &yacute; ch&iacute; v&agrave; tinh th&#7847;n v&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute;\"><img width=\"130\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-20/1505877889-marathon-chay-de-ren-y-chi-va-tinh-than-vuot-kho--1-.jpg\" alt=\"Marathon: Ch&#7841;y &#273;&#7875; r&egrave;n &yacute; ch&iacute; v&agrave; tinh th&#7847;n v&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute;\" title=\"Marathon: Ch&#7841;y &#273;&#7875; r&egrave;n &yacute; ch&iacute; v&agrave; tinh th&#7847;n v&#432;&#7907;t kh&oacute;\"></a><br>Tinh th&#7847;n tho&#7843;i m&aacute;i, n&acirc;ng cao s&#7913;c kh&#7887;e, gi&#7843;m nguy c&#417; b&#7879;nh t&#7853;t&hellip; l&agrave; nh&#7919;ng l&#7907;i &iacute;ch thi&#7871;t th&#7921;c m&agrave; marathon mang l&#7841;i. Xa h&#417;n, vi&#7879;c s&#7843;i b&#432;&#7899;c tr&ecirc;n &#273;&#432;&#7901;ng ch&#7841;y l&agrave; c&aacute;ch &#273;&#7875; m&#7885;i ng&#432;&#7901;i c&ugrave;ng nhau n&acirc;ng cao ch&#7845;t l&#432;&#7907;ng cu&#7897;c s&#7889;ng, t&#7841;o n&ecirc;n x&atilde; h&#7897;i l&agrave;nh m&#7841;nh.</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'marathon-chay-de-ren-y-chi-va-tinh-than-vuot-kho', '', '', '2017-09-19 07:00:00', '2017-09-19 07:00:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/201