INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1543', '1', '2017-09-19 01:49:15', '2017-09-19 01:49:15', '<div itemprop=\"articleBody\" readability=\"67\">\n<div readability=\"3\">\n<p><strong>Mayweather \"quy tng bng\" trong bin tin gia dn m n</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Bng xp hng huy chng i hi th thao trong nh v v thut chu  2017</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Bng xp hng huy chng ASEAN Para Games 2017</strong></p></div>\n<p>Chiu 20/9: Nguyn Vn Hng v M Phng Quang khp li cc ni dung thi u ca mn c t bng 2 tm HCB v HC hng cn 72kg. Chung cuc, cc lc s c t  gp 4 HCV, 4 HCB v 2 HC vo thnh tch ca on TTNKT Vit Nam.</p>\n<p><strong>Bi mang v thm 2 HCV (Para Games)</strong></p>\n<p>Trnh Th Bch Nh SB5 ginh HCV 100m ch n, thnh tch 1 pht 55 giy 47, cng  ni dung ny ngi ng i Nguyn Th Sari ot HCB. Bn cnh  knh ng Vi Th Hng  c thm tm HCV na cho mnh sau khi ginh tm HCV u tin cho TTVN ti Para Games 2017.</p>\n<p>C t mang v 2 huy chng. Nguyn Vn Hng - HCB - hng cn 72 kg nam - thnh tch 167kg. M Phng Quang - HC - hng cn 72kg nam - thnh tch 164kg.</p>\n<p><strong>Vng Chu ginh HCV th 2 (Para Games)</strong></p>\n<p>Gn nh ngay lp tc, VV in kinh Vng Chu mang v cho on TTVN tm HCV th 2  ni dung in kinh, F42 Nm a vi thnh tch 605 im.</p>\n<p>Chng ta cng c c nhng tm huy chng khc ca cc thnh vin sau. HCB Trn Vn c (T46) in kinh 1.500m nam, ng Vn Cng HCB mn bi 400m t do hng thng tt S8, Phm Thnh t, HC 400m t do (S9).</p>\n<p><strong>Nguyn Hong Minh \"m hng\" ginh HCV u tin (Para Games)</strong></p>\n<p>Ngay u bui sng (20/9), on th thao khuyt tt Vit Nam n tin vui t Nguyn Hong Minh ginh HCV ni dung in kinh 1.500m hng thng tt T12, vi thi gian 4 pht 41 giy 30.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"C&#x1EAD;p nh&#x1EAD;t &#x110;o&#xE0;n Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam &#x1EDF; AIMAG &amp; Para Games 20/9: &#x110;i&#x1EC1;n kinh, b&#x1A1;i gi&#x1EAD;t 4 HCV - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-20/1505873360-hoangminh.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Nguyn Hong Minh ginh tm HCV u tin cho Vit Nam ngy 20/9</p>\n<p><strong>ASEAN Para Games: Hy vng vng t  ng ua xanh</strong></p>\n<p> ngy thi u hm nay (20/9), on th thao ngi khuyt tt Vit Nam ti <strong>ASEAN Para Games 2017</strong> ang din ra ti Kuala Lumpur (Malaysia) s thi u 8 mn, bao gm: C t, in kinh, Cu lng, Bng  khim th, C Vua, Bi, Bng Bn v Boccia.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"C&#x1EAD;p nh&#x1EAD;t &#x110;o&#xE0;n Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam &#x1EDF; AIMAG &amp; Para Games 20/9: &#x110;i&#x1EC1;n kinh, b&#x1A1;i gi&#x1EAD;t 4 HCV - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-20/1505862017-1505820449-1505785690-vothanhtung1.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Ch tin thng trn t cc VV bi li Vit Nam  Para Games hm nay</p>\n<p>Trong s , Bi s l mn c k vng ln lao s mang v vinh quang l nhng tm HCV cho chng ta.  nh thi u di nc ti Bukit Jalil, Nguyn Vn Hanh s tranh ti  2 ni dung l 100m ch v 100m bm nam. Trong khi , 2 ng i khc gii vi anh l Trnh Th Bch Nh v Vi Th Hng s cng thi u  ni dung 100m ch n.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Lch thi u c th ca on th thao ngi khuyt tt Vit Nam ti ASEAN Para Games hm nay (20/9):</em></strong></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"C&#x1EAD;p nh&#x1EAD;t &#x110;o&#xE0;n Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam &#x1EDF; AIMAG &amp; Para Games 20/9: &#x110;i&#x1EC1;n kinh, b&#x1A1;i gi&#x1EAD;t 4 HCV - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-20/1505862017-21686171_1648021598603777_326044736759985035_n.jpg\" /></p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n</p><div>\n<div><img alt=\"C&#x1EAD;p nh&#x1EAD;t &#x110;o&#xE0;n Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam &#x1EDF; AIMAG &amp; Para Games 20/9: &#x110;i&#x1EC1;n kinh, b&#x1A1;i gi&#x1EAD;t 4 HCV - 4\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-20/1505862017-21751767_1648021611937109_8199452690677791905_n.jpg\" /><div>\n<div><img alt=\"C&#x1EAD;p nh&#x1EAD;t &#x110;o&#xE0;n Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam &#x1EDF; AIMAG &amp; Para Games 20/9: &#x110;i&#x1EC1;n kinh, b&#x1A1;i gi&#x1EAD;t 4 HCV - 5\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\" /></div></div></div></div>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"C&#x1EAD;p nh&#x1EAD;t &#x110;o&#xE0;n Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam &#x1EDF; AIMAG &amp; Para Games 20/9: &#x110;i&#x1EC1;n kinh, b&#x1A1;i gi&#x1EAD;t 4 HCV - 6\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-20/1505862017-21559104_1648021621937108_8441154250457023082_n.jpg\" /></p>\n<p><strong>IMAG 5: Ch futsal sa sai v tin vui t billard-snooker cng 2 mn v</strong></p>\n<p>T futsal nam Vit Nam  gy tht vng khi  lt trn ra qun ti bng A  IMAG nm nay hm 16/9, chng ta  thua ngc T i Loan (Trung Quc) 1-2 d  m t s  pht 11 do cng ca Ngc Sn.</p>\n<p>Hm nay (20/9), ti Ashgabat (Turkmenistan), T futsal nam Vit Nam s i u vi i th l T Qun o Solomon. y l i th khng d chi khi h ang dn u bng khi ton thng c 2 trn  u gp Hong Kong (Trung Quc), thng 4-1 v gp i Loan (Trung Quc), thng 4-3.</p>\n<p>Chnh v th, T futsal Vit Nam phi rt cn trng nhng cng cn t quyt tm chin thng v ch khi c 3 im trc T Qun o Solomon, thy tr Miguel Rodrigo mi mong thp li hy vng l 1 trong 2 i  bng A vo bn kt.</p>\n<p>Ti mn Billiard  Snooker, lc 20h00 ti nay (gi Vit Nam), n c th Hunh Th Ngc Huyn (Vit Nam) s u trn vng 1/8 tranh v vo t kt ni dung pool 9 bi vi i th n t Philippines  Amit Rubilen.</p>\n<p>Ti mn kurash, mt mn v c truyn ca Uzbekistan, on Vit Nam c 2 n i din s tranh ti hm nay l Trn Th Thanh Thy v  Th Hoi Uyn. Ti t kt ni dung trn 87kg, Thanh Thy s ng  Ilmatova Rinata (Uzbekistan), cn  t kt ni dung 87kg, Hoi Uyn chm trn Bagheri Zahra (Iran).</p>\n<p>Mt mn v khc l muay Thi cng gp mt nhiu gng mt n t Vit Nam tranh ti hm nay. Lc 16h30 (gi VN), Bi Yn Ly s bc vo trn bn kt n di 51kg gp Gwa Wei Ying Cheryl (Singapore).</p>\n<p>Sau , Nguyn Thanh Tng s i u Khatthamarasri Anueng (Thi Lan)  trn tranh chp v vo chung kt nam ni dung 71kg. Trng Th Hng Nga s tranh ti vi Boorboorajdary Zahra (Iran)  bn kt n ni dung 63,5kg.</p>\n<p>Mn Taekwondo, Vit Nam cng rt c nhiu k vng hm nay. H Th Nguyn s u vi Mohamed Juwana Mohamed Moosa Ali (Bahrain)  vng 1/8 hng cn 62kg n.</p>\n<p>VV  ginh HCB SEA Games 29, V Quc Hng s quyt u vi Rozyew Muhammet (Turkmenistan)  vng 1/8 hng cn 58kg nam. Sau , Bc Th Khim s gp Bibalayeva Gulim (Kazakhstan) cng  vng ny nhng ti hng cn 62kg n.</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><img alt=\"Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam &#x111;&#xF3;n &#x201D;c&#x1A1;n m&#x1B0;a V&#xE0;ng&#x201D; qua m&#x1EB7;t Th&#xE1;i Lan t&#x1EA1;i Para Games\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505819524-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\n<div>\n<div>Vit Nam n cn ma Vng qua mt Thi Lan ti Para Games</div>\n<div readability=\"2\">\n<p>Vi 10 tm HCV ngy thi u 19/9, TTVN tm thi vt qua on Thi Lan.</p></div>\n<div>Bm xem &gt;&gt;</div></div></div></div>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p>\n<p></p></div>', 'Cp nht on Vit Nam  AIMAG & Para Games 20/9: in kinh, bi git 4 HCV', '<div><a href=\"http://www.24h.com.vn/the-thao/cap-nhat-doan-the-thao-viet-nam-o-aimag-para-games-20-9-cho-tin-vui-tu-boi-loi-futsal-c101a904612.html\" title=\"C&#7853;p nh&#7853;t &#272;o&agrave;n Vi&#7879;t Nam &#7903; AIMAG &amp; Para Games 20/9: &#272;i&#7873;n kinh, b&#417;i gi&#7853;t 4 HCV\"><img width=\"130\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-20/1505861900-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"C&#7853;p nh&#7853;t &#272;o&agrave;n Vi&#7879;t Nam &#7903; AIMAG &amp; Para Games 20/9: &#272;i&#7873;n kinh, b&#417;i gi&#7853;t 4 HCV\" title=\"C&#7853;p nh&#7853;t &#272;o&agrave;n Vi&#7879;t Nam &#7903; AIMAG &amp; Para Games 20/9: &#272;i&#7873;n kinh, b&#417;i gi&#7853;t 4 HCV\"></a><br>(Tin th&#7875; thao) &#272;o&agrave;n th&#7875; thao ng&#432;&#7901;i khuy&#7871;t t&#7853;t Vi&#7879;t Nam c&oacute; c&#417; h&#7897;i mang v&#7873; th&ecirc;m nh&#7919;ng t&#7845;m HCV qu&yacute; gi&aacute; &#7903; c&aacute;c n&#7897;i dung b&#417;i l&#7897;i trong ng&agrave;y h&ocirc;m nay (20/9) &#7903; Para Games t&#7841;i Malaysia. Trong khi &#273;&oacute;, t&#7841;i &#272;&#7841;i h&#7897;i th&#7875; thao trong nh&agrave; &amp; V&otilde; thu&#7853;t ch&acirc;u &Aacute; (IMAG), nhi&#7873;u n&#7897;i dung h&#7913;a h&#7865;n c&#7911;a ch&uacute;ng ta c&#361;ng s&#7869; tranh t&agrave;i. M&#7899;i nh&#7845;t, hai n&#7897;i dung b&#417;i v&agrave; &#273;i&#7873;n kinh mang v&#7873; cho TTVN th&ecirc;m 4 t&#7845;m HCV s&aacute;ng nay.</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'cap-nhat-doan-viet-nam-o-aimag-para-games-209-dien-kinh-boi-giat-4-hcv', '', '', '2017-09-19 01:49:15', '2017-09-19 01:49:15', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/cap-nhat-doan-viet-nam-o-aimag-para-games-209-dien-kinh-boi-giat-4-hcv/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
