INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1545', '1', '2017-09-19 01:00:00', '2017-09-19 01:00:00', '<div itemprop=\"articleBody\" readability=\"38\">\n<p>Khng thi u chuyn nghip t thng 7/2015 sau khi chia tay CLB Fluminese, nhng Ronaldinho vn gi c k nng iu luyn ca mnh. Bng chng l ngi sao Brazil ang to sng rc r  gii Premier Futsal 2017, khin cc CV trn khn i lun phi h vang ting Dinho. Trn m mn gii, Ronaldinho ghi c 4 bn trong chin thng 4-3 ca Delhi Dragon trc Mumbai Warriors, i bng c Ryan Giggs.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"Ronaldinho th&#x103;ng hoa &#x1EDF; gi&#x1EA3;i Premier Futsal 2017 - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505727591-1.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Trn th hai ca i, cu cu th Barca m t s ngay  pht u tin v hon tt c p  pht 28 trong chin thng 4-2 trc Chennai Singhams</p>\n<p><em>Khi c Ronaldinho trong i hnh th bn chng cn g phi lo lng c. Nhn thy anh y ra sn l chng ta bit s c nhng tuyt phm, nhng giy pht khin khn gi phi pht in</em>, cu th Ismail Hamdaoni ni v ngi ng i danh ting ca mnh.</p>\n<p>Vi 6 im sau hai trn, Delhi Dragon ang l mt trong nhng ng c vin sng gi cho chc v ch Premier Futsal 2017, ua tranh quyt lit vi Bengaluru Royals, i bng c chn st Paul Scholes, huyn thoi mt thi ca Manchester United v cu th Vit Nam Danh Pht.</p>\n<p> gii u ny, Vit Nam c hai cu th d gii Premier Futsal 2017. Ngoi Danh Pht cn Thnh t khoc o Telugu Tigers cng Deco.</p>\n<p>Premier Futsal l gii u do cu danh th Real Luis Figo ng sng lp. y l ma gii th hai, c s gp mt ca su i. Tham d sn chi ny l cc cu cu th danh ting, cc ngi sao futsal ng i v cc ti nng giu trin vng c cc chuyn gia tuyn trch hng u th gii chiu m.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"Ronaldinho th&#x103;ng hoa &#x1EDF; gi&#x1EA3;i Premier Futsal 2017 - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505727591-2.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Premier Futsal 2017 tip tc l sn chi ng cp quy t cc chn st danh ting</p>\n<p>Premier Futsal ang trn ng tr thnh gii u futsal hng u th gii. Nm 2016, sn chi ny thu ht gn 750 triu ngi xem. Ma gii nm nay, gii u tr li vi nhiu kch tnh v hp dn hn, ngi hm m Vit Nam may mn c theo di trn vn gii u khi truyn hnh K+ mua c quyn v pht sng trc tip Premier Futsal 2017 trn knh K+PM.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"Ronaldinho th&#x103;ng hoa &#x1EDF; gi&#x1EA3;i Premier Futsal 2017 - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505727591-3.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Lch pht sng Premier Futsal 2017 trc tip v duy nht trn knh K+PM</p>\n<p>Nh vy, t ngy 15/9 n ngy 1/10, khn gi s c thm mt gii u ng cp th gii  theo di, bn cnh Ngoi hng Anh v La Liga vn ang bng n trn cc knh K+.</p>\n<p> khng b l din bin hp dn ca Premier Futsal, Ngoi hng Anh, La Liga v cc gii u th thao hp dn khc c lch pht sng dy c, khn gi c th ng k lp t K+ ti link: https://goo.gl/khAjio hoc lin h hotline 19001592. Thu bao K+ d dng theo di trc tip v xem li cc trn u yu thch mi lc mi ni qua cc knh K+, ng dng truyn hnh trc tuyn myK+ v gi cc myK+ NOW trn tivi, in thoi thng minh, my tnh bng, my tnh xch tay</p><table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" width=\"660\"><tbody><tr><td valign=\"top\" readability=\"10\">\n<p>Khn gi th thao s c mt tun bng n vi cc trn u khng th b l trn K+.  Ngoi hng Anh l cc cp u th v: West Ham  Tottenham, Leicester  Liverpool, Southampton  M.U, ManCity  Crystal Palace v trn u c K+ pht sng c quyn l Stoke City  Chelsea.</p>\n<p>Trong khi , vng 6 La Liga s tr li vi cc trn cu tm im gia Alt.Madrid  Sevilla, Alaves  Real Madrid, Girona  Barcelona Song song vi  l cc trn u  giai on nc rt cui ma ca Chinese Super League.</p>\n<p>Trong khi ch i tennis ATP tr li vi gii Chengdu Open (K+ pht sng trc tip t 29/9  01/10), khn gi s khng th b qua gii Golf PGA Tour Championship c pht sng t 21/9  24/9 trn knh K+PC.</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p></div>', 'Ronaldinho thng hoa  gii Premier Futsal 2017', '<div><a href=\"http://www.24h.com.vn/the-thao/ronaldinho-thang-hoa-o-giai-premier-futsal-2017-c101a904256.html\" title=\"Ronaldinho th&#259;ng hoa &#7903; gi&#7843;i Premier Futsal 2017\"><img width=\"130\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505729145-zs.jpg\" alt=\"Ronaldinho th&#259;ng hoa &#7903; gi&#7843;i Premier Futsal 2017\" title=\"Ronaldinho th&#259;ng hoa &#7903; gi&#7843;i Premier Futsal 2017\"></a><br>C&#7847;u th&#7911; ng&#432;&#7901;i Brazil ghi 6 trong t&#7893;ng s&#7889; 8 b&agrave;n th&#7855;ng, gi&uacute;p &#273;&#7897;i b&oacute;ng Delhi Dragon th&#7855;ng hai tr&#7853;n ra qu&acirc;n t&#7841;i Premier Futsal 2017, gi&#7843;i &#273;&#7845;u &#273;ang thu h&uacute;t s&#7921; ch&uacute; &yacute; c&#7911;a fan t&uacute;c c&#7847;u tr&ecirc;n to&agrave;n th&#7871; gi&#7899;i v&agrave; c&#7843; kh&aacute;n gi&#7843; Vi&#7879;t Nam tr&ecirc;n s&oacute;ng truy&#7873;n h&igrave;nh K+.</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ronaldinho-thang-hoa-o-giai-premier-futsal-2017', '', '', '2017-09-19 01:00:00', '2017-09-19 01:00:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/ronaldinho-thang-hoa-o-giai-premier-futsal-2017/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
