INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1549', '1', '2017-09-18 17:08:51', '2017-09-18 17:08:51', '<div readability=\"31\">\n<div readability=\"5\">\n<p><strong>Ng nga: Cu SAO MU u boxing, m trn kinh in 1 t </strong></p>\n<p><strong>Sharapova qu quyt: Li dng scandal doping kim 360 t ng</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Siu v s 1 m u 5 trn, chiu 5 v: 30 pht knock-out 12 i th</strong></p></div>\n<p><em>Huyn thoi 5 v thua nh i trc tay m c phch Muhammad Ali (1974)</em></p>\n<div align=\"center\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div></div>\n<div>\n<div data-config=\"id=zplayer_d84a51&amp;flash=%2Fzplayer%2FzPlayerView.swf%3Fver%3D20170920&amp;hideNextPrevButtons=1&amp;ad_skipButtonAd=PREROLL,POSTROLL&amp;hideExtraButtons=1&amp;ad_skipButtonTime=5&amp;ad_preroll=https%3A%2F%2Fpubads.g.doubleclick.net%2Fgampad%2Fads%3Fsz%3D528x297%26iu%3D%2F124557882%2F24h%2Fvn%2Fdesktop%2Fsport%2Fpreroll%26impl%3Ds%26gdfp_req%3D1%26env%3Dvp%26output%3Dvast%26unviewed_position_start%3D1%26url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.24h.com.vn%252Fthe-thao%252Fsieu-vo-sy-1-dem-dau-5-tran-chieu-5-vo-dinh-quy-ke-om-han-ngan-thu-c101a904544.html%26description_url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.24h.com.vn%252Fthe-thao%252Fsieu-vo-sy-1-dem-dau-5-tran-chieu-5-vo-dinh-quy-ke-om-han-ngan-thu-c101a904544.html%26correlator%3D1505958427%26ambient%3D1&amp;ad_prerollOnly=0&amp;ad_prerollTime=31&amp;ad_prerollType=adsense&amp;ad_overlay=https%3A%2F%2Fpubads.g.doubleclick.net%2Fgampad%2Fads%3Fsz%3D528x60%26iu%3D%2F124557882%2F24h%2Fvn%2Fdesktop%2Fsport%2Foverlay%26impl%3Ds%26gdfp_req%3D1%26env%3Dvp%26output%3Dvast%26unviewed_position_start%3D1%26url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.24h.com.vn%252Fthe-thao%252Fsieu-vo-sy-1-dem-dau-5-tran-chieu-5-vo-dinh-quy-ke-om-han-ngan-thu-c101a904544.html%26description_url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.24h.com.vn%252Fthe-thao%252Fsieu-vo-sy-1-dem-dau-5-tran-chieu-5-vo-dinh-quy-ke-om-han-ngan-thu-c101a904544.html%26correlator%3D1505958427%26ambient%3D1&amp;ad_overlayTime=15&amp;ad_overlayStart=10&amp;ad_overlayType=adsense&amp;ad_postroll=https%3A%2F%2Fpubads.g.doubleclick.net%2Fgampad%2Fads%3Fsz%3D528x297%26iu%3D%2F124557882%2F24h%2Fvn%2Fdesktop%2Fsport%2Fpostroll%26impl%3Ds%26gdfp_req%3D1%26env%3Dvp%26output%3Dvast%26unviewed_position_start%3D1%26url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.24h.com.vn%252Fthe-thao%252Fsieu-vo-sy-1-dem-dau-5-tran-chieu-5-vo-dinh-quy-ke-om-han-ngan-thu-c101a904544.html%26description_url%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.24h.com.vn%252Fthe-thao%252Fsieu-vo-sy-1-dem-dau-5-tran-chieu-5-vo-dinh-quy-ke-om-han-ngan-thu-c101a904544.html%26correlator%3D1505958427%26ambient%3D1&amp;ad_postrollOnly=0&amp;ad_postrollTime=30&amp;ad_postrollType=adsense&amp;file=http://video.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/videoclip/2017-09-19/1505816270-foreman.mp4&amp;fileAlt=&amp;image=http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505816270-foreman.jpg&amp;volume=40&amp;ad_volume=40&amp;mute=mute&amp;ad_mute=mute&amp;autoNext=6&amp;title=V&#xF5; s&#x1EF9; 1 &#x111;&#xEA;m &#x111;&#x1EA5;u 5 tr&#x1EAD;n: D&#xED;nh qu&#x1EF7; k&#x1EBF;, &#xF4;m h&#x1EAD;n ng&#xE0;n thu tr&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;c Muhammad Ali&amp;autoPlay=0&amp;postId=d98ef01cd04dd7af5eb5183da6f304fe&amp;newsId=904544&amp;ad_skipButton=1\"></div></div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div>\n<div></div></div></div>\n<p>Nu nh khng u vi Muhammad Ali, c l gi y tay m 68 tui <strong>George Foreman</strong> vn tr thnh v s \"c c cu bi\" nh ci cch Floyd Mayweather ginh c. George Foreman tng tri qua 81 trn trong s nghip, vi 76 chin thng, thua 5, c ti 68 trn knock-out i th, 2 ln v ch quyn Anh hng nng th gii, ginh 1 HCV Olympic v cng ni ting v i t khi  tri qua 5 i v.</p>\n<p>Trn u th 41 trong s nghip, ng  vi Ali ti Cng ha Zaire (gi l Congo, Trung Phi) nm 1974 l trn thua u tin ca George, n tht ng qun nhng khin ng phi \"khc ct ghi tm\" mi mi.</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"V&#xF5; s&#x1EF9; 1 &#x111;&#xEA;m &#x111;&#x1EA5;u 5 tr&#x1EAD;n: D&#xED;nh qu&#x1EF7; k&#x1EBF;, &#xF4;m h&#x1EAD;n ng&#xE0;n thu tr&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;c Muhammad Ali - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505817911-george.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>George (tri) thua trn u tin trong s nghip v ri vo by ca huyn thoi Ali (phi)</p>\n<p>Ali thi im  l mt tay m gii ngang tm vi George, hai v s gp nhau  ginh 4 chic ai hng nng. C huyn thoi Ali thi im   c 2 trn thua nn rt \"bit ngi bit ta\", ngc li George hiu thng v c phn mc cn bnh \"ngi sao\" nn khng coi ai ra g.</p>\n<p>Trc khi bay qua Phi Chu   gng cng <em>George Foreman, Ali  ti New York</em>  xin  kin ca \"co gi\" trong ngh l cu v s DAmato. ng ny  vch cho Ali thy cch duy nht  h i th l lm cch no cho George Foreman tc ti ni in ln.</p>\n<p>Trong trng hp , theo DAmato, George Foreman s tr nn mt phng hng v ch cn gi ngi ra cho i th m m thi. DAmato cn dn Ali l cn thit phi dn n lc ph u Goerge Foreman ngay trong pht m mn trn u.</p>\n<p>Lm theo ng nh nhng li tin bi ni, Ali chi dn p ngay t u  uy hip tinh thn i th, sau , dng chin thut \"phng th cht\" da dy n n khin George Foreman khng c c hi tung nhng c m mnh nh ba t.</p>\n<p>Trong khi p dng cch trnh n d dng , Ali li lin tc \"ci u\" hng chc tc i th. Qu nhin, Foreman oai hng dnh k, tay m ny lin tc tn cng bng nhng c m ht tay v sau  mi nh hai tay, mt sc.  l thi im Ali tung ra hng lot c n  h i th  hip 8 trong trn u d tnh n 15 hip.</p>\n<p> l trn thua u tin ca Goerge Foreman sau 5 nm vi 40 trn thng nh ch tre. \"<u>Goerge ln</u>\" cng tha nhn  l mt trong nhng trn u khin ng phi n hn sut i song  cng l bi hc gip ng trng thnh hn  phn cn li s nghip boxing ly lng  tr thnh tay m c t l knock-out tt nht lch s.</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><img alt=\"Si&#xEA;u v&#xF5; s&#x1EF9; 1 &#x111;&#xEA;m &#x111;&#x1EA5;u 5 tr&#x1EAD;n, 5 &#x111;&#x1EDD;i v&#x1EE3;: H&#x1EA1; &#x201D;Qu&#xE1;i v&#x1EAD;t&#x201D; ch&#x1EC9; 45 gi&#xE2;y\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505733979-thumbnail.jpg\" /></div>\n<div>\n<div>Siu v s 1 m u 5 trn, 5 i v: H Qui vt ch 45 giy</div>\n<div readability=\"2\">\n<p>Ni v kh nng knock-out i th chng vnh, Foreman t c i th snh kp.</p></div>\n<div>Bm xem &gt;&gt;</div></div></div></div></div>', 'V s 1 m u 5 trn: Dnh qu k, m hn ngn thu trc Muhammad Ali', '<div><a href=\"http://www.24h.com.vn/the-thao/sieu-vo-sy-1-dem-dau-5-tran-chieu-5-vo-dinh-quy-ke-om-han-ngan-thu-c101a904544.html\" title=\"V&otilde; s&#7929; 1 &#273;&ecirc;m &#273;&#7845;u 5 tr&#7853;n: D&iacute;nh qu&#7927; k&#7871;, &ocirc;m h&#7853;n ng&agrave;n thu tr&#432;&#7899;c Muhammad Ali\"><img width=\"130\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505818073-thumbnail.jpg\" alt=\"V&otilde; s&#7929; 1 &#273;&ecirc;m &#273;&#7845;u 5 tr&#7853;n: D&iacute;nh qu&#7927; k&#7871;, &ocirc;m h&#7853;n ng&agrave;n thu tr&#432;&#7899;c Muhammad Ali\" title=\"V&otilde; s&#7929; 1 &#273;&ecirc;m &#273;&#7845;u 5 tr&#7853;n: D&iacute;nh qu&#7927; k&#7871;, &ocirc;m h&#7853;n ng&agrave;n thu tr&#432;&#7899;c Muhammad Ali\"></a><br>(Tin th&#7875; thao, Tin boxing) &#272;&#7889;i th&#7911; l&agrave;m &#273;&#7911; tr&ograve; &#273;&#7875; khi&ecirc;u kh&iacute;ch, kh&ocirc;ng th&#7875; ti&#7871;t ch&#7871; c&#7843;m x&uacute;c n&oacute;ng n&#7843;y George Foreman ph&#7843;i tr&#7843; gi&aacute; &#273;&#7855;t v&#7899;i tr&#7853;n thua &#273;&#7847;u ti&ecirc;n tr&#432;&#7899;c Muhammad Ali sau 40 tr&#7853;n to&agrave;n th&#7855;ng.</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'vo-sy-1-dem-dau-5-tran-dinh-quy-ke-om-han-ngan-thu-truoc-muhammad-ali', '', '', '2017-09-18 17:08:51', '2017-09-18 17:08:51', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/18/vo-sy-1-dem-dau-5-tran-dinh-quy-ke-om-han-ngan-thu-truoc-muhammad-ali/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
