ri\" cho Alvarez thng 118-110 v  l l do hai tay m ha. </p>\n<p> c rt nhiu nghi vn tiu cc v bn v nhn hi l  lm sai lch kt qu trn u song ti thi im ny, n vn dng li  s phng on. B Adalaide Byrd khc  mt \"xin li\" gii thch n gin ch v mnh thiu tp trung trong khi lm nhim v nn lm nh hng kt qu trn u.</p>\n<p>Nhng ngi sai th  c my tnh, thng k sau trn cho thy cc ch s ca \"Cu b vng\" Kazakhstan nhnh hn nhiu so vi i th song kt qu khng thay i.  l iu khin nhiu ngi ni boxing gi y qu cng nhc v nhm chn, nht l cc v s UFC.</p>\n<p>Rt nhiu nhn vt cm cn ca lng UFC nh ch tch Dana White, \"G in\" McGregor...  c dp ci nho gii boxing, c nhiu ngi cn dng nhng ngn t chi ra ht sc nng n.</p>\n<p><em>Tng hp nhng Twitter h thp boxing ca cc v s UFC</em></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"&amp;#34;Tr&#xF2; h&#x1EC1;&amp;#34; tr&#x1EAD;n Golovkin-Alvarez: McGregor &amp; UFC h&#x1EA3; h&#xEA; nh&#x1EA1;o b&#xE1;ng boxing - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505730154-golovkin-canelo661.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Do qua trang mng x hi ca cc v s, c rt nhiu li \"tng s v\" boxing. McGregor gi boxing l \"tr chi in r\"</p>\n<p></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"&amp;#34;Tr&#xF2; h&#x1EC1;&amp;#34; tr&#x1EAD;n Golovkin-Alvarez: McGregor &amp; UFC h&#x1EA3; h&#xEA; nh&#x1EA1;o b&#xE1;ng boxing - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505730154-golovkin-canelo662.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Ch tch UFC Dana White th nhm n cc nh t chc</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n</p><div>\n<div><img alt=\"&amp;#34;Tr&#xF2; h&#x1EC1;&amp;#34; tr&#x1EAD;n Golovkin-Alvarez: McGregor &amp; UFC h&#x1EA3; h&#xEA; nh&#x1EA1;o b&#xE1;ng boxing - 4\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-18/1505730154-golovkin-canelo663.jpg\" /><div>\n<div><img alt=\"&amp;#34;Tr&#xF2; h&#x1EC1;&amp;#34; tr&#x1EAD;n Golovkin-Alvarez: McGregor &amp; UFC h&#x1EA3; h&#xE