INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1553', '1', '2017-09-18 17:08:39', '2017-09-18 17:08:39', '<div itemprop=\"articleBody\" readability=\"44\">\n<div readability=\"8\">\n<p>ua xe F1, Singapore GP: Nga chin t st, Mi tn bc\" chm vinh quang</p>\n<p>Bng xp hng F1 - Singapore GP: Hamilton n 7, \"ct ui\" Vettel</p>\n<p>Video F1, Singapore GP: Thy chin 2 xe b mng, 8 tay ua b cuc</p></div>\n<p><strong>Singapore GP </strong>nm 2017 l mt chng ua c mng cho Ferrari khi c ngi ginh pole Sebastian Vettel v tay li xut pht th 4 Kimi Raikkonen u phi ri cuc ua sm ngay t vng ua u tin sau v va chm vi Max Verstappen cng s gp mt bt c d ca Fernando Alonso. ng ch  y mi ch l ln th 2 trong 11 nm qua nga chin phi nhn DNF kp, ln trc cng din ra ngay gn y, ti Mexico nm 2015. Trc , h  c ti 183 cuc ua m khng gp phi iu .</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"&#x110;ua xe F1, Singapore GP: &#x201C;Th&#x1EA7;n may m&#x1EAF;n&#x201D; ngo&#x1EA3;nh m&#x1EB7;t, c&#x1A1;n &#xE1;c m&#x1ED9;ng m&#xE0;u &#x111;&#x1ECF; - 1\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505815048-318--2.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Ferrari c DNF kp th 2 trong 11 nm</p>\n<p>Vi Verstappen y li l chng ua th 7 trn tng 14 chng m anh phi b cuc gia chng, 3 trong s  n  vng ua u tin. V vy cng khng c g kh hiu khi anh vn l tay ua hon thnh t vng ua nht trong s nhng tay li hin ti nm 2017. Cn vi ngi ng i Daniel Ricciardo, anh tip tc nm gi vn may v gia tng chui podium ti vnh Marina ln con s 4 khi anh v ch th 2 sau Hamilton v c c podium th 7 ma gii ny.</p>\n<p>Hamilton xut pht th 5 nhng li nhn c may mn v ginh chin thng th 3 lin tip, cng l ln th 3 anh ln ngi  Singapore. S ln v nht ca tay li ngi Anh  chm n ct mc 60, tin them 1 bc na ti k lc ca huyn thoi Michael Schumacher. y l ln th 2 trong s nghip Hamilton  ginh chin thng khi xut pht  di v tr th 4. Ln duy nht cn li l British GP 2014 khi anh bt u  hng 6. Alonso v Raikkonen hin ang l 2 chuyn gia trong vic ny khi  6 ln h v nht khi bt u ngoi top 4.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"&#x110;ua xe F1, Singapore GP: &#x201C;Th&#x1EA7;n may m&#x1EAF;n&#x201D; ngo&#x1EA3;nh m&#x1EB7;t, c&#x1A1;n &#xE1;c m&#x1ED9;ng m&#xE0;u &#x111;&#x1ECF; - 2\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505815048-318--3.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Lewis Hamilton ngy cng bay cao trn BXH c nhn</p>\n<p>Khong cch v im s sau <em>Singapore GP</em> gia Hamilton v Vettel gi  l 28 im trong khi ch cn 6 chng ua na l ma gii khp li. y l khong cch ln nht k t chng ua u tin v c th ni cuc ua song m ny  gn i ti hi kt ca n. Nhng nu bn mun tin v mt php mu, th n  tng xy ra, v u c lin quan vi Vettel.</p>\n<p> c ti 2 ln, Vettel  vt qua khong cch im ln  ln ngi v ch mt cch khng th n tng hn. Ln u l nm 2010 khi anh km Hamilton 31 im sau 13 chng ua v nm 2012 khi anh b Alonso dn ti 42 im sau 11 vng ua. V ch th 3  Singapore l Valtteri Bottas, ngi  cn bng s podium trong ma gii vi Vettel vi ln th 10 c bc ln bc nhn gii. D vy, chin thng 1-2 ti Singapore vn cn l mt iu xa x i vi tt c cc i ua.</p>\n<p>Trong khi c nhng tay li gp nn th cng c nhng ngi c hng li,  l ba tay ua Carlos Sainz ca Toro Rosso (v ch th 4 khi anh cha bao gi v cao hn hng 6), Jolyon Palmer (v ch th 6 khi anh cha bao gi v cao hn hng 10 v Stoffel Vandoorne (v ch th 7 khi anh cha bao gi v cao hn hng 10).</p>\n<p align=\"center\"><img alt=\"&#x110;ua xe F1, Singapore GP: &#x201C;Th&#x1EA7;n may m&#x1EAF;n&#x201D; ngo&#x1EA3;nh m&#x1EB7;t, c&#x1A1;n &#xE1;c m&#x1ED9;ng m&#xE0;u &#x111;&#x1ECF; - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505815048-318--4.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Palmer v Vandoorne c thnh tch tt nht trong s nghip</p>\n<p>Sergio Perez cn ch  v tr th 5, v anh  ghi c im  tt c 10 chng ua Singapore GP  din ra d anh cha bao gi xut pht  trong top 10 mt ln no c. Cn v tr th 10 ca Esteban Ocon  m bo cho ln th 11 c chng ghi im kp trong nm cho Force India. Ocon v Hamilton gi y l hai tay ua duy nht cn li hon thnh c  100% qung ng ca 14 chng ua, mt thnh tch khng th xem thng.</p>\n<p>Ni n Singapore, cuc ua nm nay ch c 12 tay li hon thnh cuc ua, t nht trong s 10 cuc ua trong 1 thp k qua, nhng y khng phi l iu bt ng bi y l cuc ua ma m u tin trong lch s.</p>\n<p>Ngoi ra, cuc ua ny cng c chiu di ngn nht khi ch hon thnh c 58 trn 61 vng theo nh k hoch.  c 2 ln khc Singapore GP phi s dng ng h m ngc  kt thc chng ua,  l nm 2012 v 2014, khi  ch 59 v 60 vng ua c hon thnh. Trong s nhng nn nhn  cuc ua ny, ci tn ng tic nht chc chn l Fernando Alonso khi anh b loi ngay t nhng vng u tin. Ln DNF ny ng ngha vi vic tay li ngi Ty Ban Nha mi ch 3 ln trong nm 2017 c th nhn thy c ch.</p>\n<p align=\"center\">\n</p><div>\n<div><img alt=\"&#x110;ua xe F1, Singapore GP: &#x201C;Th&#x1EA7;n may m&#x1EAF;n&#x201D; ngo&#x1EA3;nh m&#x1EB7;t, c&#x1A1;n &#xE1;c m&#x1ED9;ng m&#xE0;u &#x111;&#x1ECF; - 4\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505815048-318--5.jpg\" /><div>\n<div><img alt=\"&#x110;ua xe F1, Singapore GP: &#x201C;Th&#x1EA7;n may m&#x1EAF;n&#x201D; ngo&#x1EA3;nh m&#x1EB7;t, c&#x1A1;n &#xE1;c m&#x1ED9;ng m&#xE0;u &#x111;&#x1ECF; - 5\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/24h_banner_image_library/in-image-close.svg\" /></div></div></div></div>\n<p>Alonso khng gp may  Singapore</p>\n<p>V cui cng, khng th khng nhc ti Nico Hulkenberg, ngi  chnh thc nm gi mt k lc khng h mong mun,  l tay ua chy nhiu chng nht nhng vn cha mt ln ginh c podium trong s nghip.</p>\n<p>Tay li ngi c  tri qua 129 GP (nhiu hn ngi gi k lc c Adrian Sutil 1 GP) m khng th mt ln lt vo top 3 tay ua nhanh nht. D vy vi vic Renault ngy cng cho thy s ci thin nhanh chng ca mnh, ngy chng ta c thy Hulkenberg trn podium c l khng cn qu xa na.</p>\n<p>Hy tip tc theo di nhng din bin tip theo ca ma gii F1 nm 2017 vi im n th 15 l ti Sepang, Malaysia.</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><img alt=\"&#x110;ua xe F1: C&#xF4;ng ngh&#x1EC7; t&#x1ED1;i t&#xE2;n nh&#x1B0;ng lu&#x1EAD;t l&#x1EC7; l&#x1ED7;i th&#x1EDD;i\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-09/1504950833-314--1.jpg\" /></div>\n<div>\n<div>ua xe F1: Cng ngh ti tn nhng lut l li thi</div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p>F1 l ni quy t ca hu ht tt c nhng cng ngh mi nht c p dng.</p></div>\n<div>Bm xem &gt;&gt;</div></div></div></div>\n<p></p></div>', 'ua xe F1, Singapore GP: Thn may mn ngonh mt, cn c mng mu ', '<div><a href=\"http://www.24h.com.vn/the-thao/dua-xe-f1-singapore-gp-than-may-man-ngoanh-mat-con-ac-mong-mau-do-c101a904520.html\" title=\"&#272;ua xe F1, Singapore GP: &ldquo;Th&#7847;n may m&#7855;n&rdquo; ngo&#7843;nh m&#7863;t, c&#417;n &aacute;c m&#7897;ng m&agrave;u &#273;&#7887;\"><img width=\"130\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505814989-318--1.jpg\" alt=\"&#272;ua xe F1, Singapore GP: &ldquo;Th&#7847;n may m&#7855;n&rdquo; ngo&#7843;nh m&#7863;t, c&#417;n &aacute;c m&#7897;ng m&agrave;u &#273;&#7887;\" title=\"&#272;ua xe F1, Singapore GP: &ldquo;Th&#7847;n may m&#7855;n&rdquo; ngo&#7843;nh m&#7863;t, c&#417;n &aacute;c m&#7897;ng m&agrave;u &#273;&#7887;\"></a><br>(Tin &#273;ua xe c&ocirc;ng th&#7913;c 1 - Tin F1) K&#7871;t qu&#7843; cu&#7889;i c&ugrave;ng c&#361;ng l&agrave; m&#7897;t &#273;i&#7873;u th&#7921;c s&#7921; b&#7845;t ng&#7901; khi Lewis Hamilton c&oacute; &#273;&#432;&#7907;c chi&#7871;n th&#7855;ng th&#7913; 7 trong m&ugrave;a gi&#7843;i, c&ugrave;ng v&#7899;i &#273;&oacute; l&agrave; nhi&#7873;u th&ocirc;ng s&#7889; &#273;&aacute;ng ch&uacute; &yacute; kh&aacute;c.</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dua-xe-f1-singapore-gp-than-may-man-ngoanh-mat-con-ac-mong-mau-do', '', '', '2017-09-18 17:08:39', '2017-09-18 17:08:39', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/18/dua-xe-f1-singapore-gp-than-may-man-ngoanh-mat-con-ac-mong-mau-do/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
