3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505827838-_mg_2913.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Ngay  hip u u tin, trn derby bng r Si Gn  nng hn d kin vi nhiu pha va chm ca cu th hai i.</p>\n<p></p>\n<p><img alt=\"Derby b&#xF3;ng r&#x1ED5; S&#xE0;i G&#xF2;n &amp;#34;t&#xF3;e l&#x1EED;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#x1EC7;t ki&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1ED5; m&#xE1;u &amp; nh&#x1EAD;p vi&#x1EC7;n - 3\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505827838-_mg_2852.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Trn u nhiu ln phi tm dng trc nhng phn ng ca Tun Trung bn pha Ho Chi Minh City Wings sau khi cc trng ti lin tc bt li cu th ch nh.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Derby b&#xF3;ng r&#x1ED5; S&#xE0;i G&#xF2;n &amp;#34;t&#xF3;e l&#x1EED;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#x1EC7;t ki&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1ED5; m&#xE1;u &amp; nh&#x1EAD;p vi&#x1EC7;n - 4\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505827838-_mg_2856.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Trng ti lin tc nhc nh Tun Trung phi bnh tnh...</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Derby b&#xF3;ng r&#x1ED5; S&#xE0;i G&#xF2;n &amp;#34;t&#xF3;e l&#x1EED;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#x1EC7;t ki&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1ED5; m&#xE1;u &amp; nh&#x1EAD;p vi&#x1EC7;n - 5\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505827838-_mg_2926.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>n cui hip u th hai, c nh thi u H Xun Hng hong ht trc pha chi ci ch ca Richardson bn pha Ho Chi Minh City Wings vi Anthony V bn pha Saigon Heat.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Derby b&#xF3;ng r&#x1ED5; S&#xE0;i G&#xF2;n &amp;#34;t&#xF3;e l&#x1EED;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#x1EC7;t ki&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1ED5; m&#xE1;u &amp; nh&#x1EAD;p vi&#x1EC7;n - 6\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505827838-_mg_2938.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Pha chi xu ca Richardson khin cu th Vit kiu bn pha Saigon Heat b rch mt v  kh nhiu mu.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Derby b&#xF3;ng r&#x1ED5; S&#xE0;i G&#xF2;n &amp;#34;t&#xF3;e l&#x1EED;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#x1EC7;t ki&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1ED5; m&#xE1;u &amp; nh&#x1EAD;p vi&#x1EC7;n - 7\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505827838-_mg_2942.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Anthony V ca Saigon Heat c cc bc s s cu trn sn khin trn u tm dng hn 10 pht.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Derby b&#xF3;ng r&#x1ED5; S&#xE0;i G&#xF2;n &amp;#34;t&#xF3;e l&#x1EED;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#x1EC7;t ki&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1ED5; m&#xE1;u &amp; nh&#x1EAD;p vi&#x1EC7;n - 8\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505827838-_mg_2972.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Sau , cu th Vit kiu c a ngay n bnh vin gn nht  khu vt rch kh ln trn mt.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Derby b&#xF3;ng r&#x1ED5; S&#xE0;i G&#xF2;n &amp;#34;t&#xF3;e l&#x1EED;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#x1EC7;t ki&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1ED5; m&#xE1;u &amp; nh&#x1EAD;p vi&#x1EC7;n - 9\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505827838-_mg_2995.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Sau pha bng ca Richardson vi Anthony V, cu th Saigon Heat v Ho Chi Minh City Wings cn nhiu ln gy hn, in hnh l tnh hung Lewis bn pha Saigon Heat chi ci ch khin Tun Trung nm bt ng kh lu trn sn  hip th ba.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Derby b&#xF3;ng r&#x1ED5; S&#xE0;i G&#xF2;n &amp;#34;t&#xF3;e l&#x1EED;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#x1EC7;t ki&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1ED5; m&#xE1;u &amp; nh&#x1EAD;p vi&#x1EC7;n - 10\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505827838-_mg_3022.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Cc trng ti chu kh nhiu p lc trong trn derby bng r Si Gn  VBA 2017.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Derby b&#xF3;ng r&#x1ED5; S&#xE0;i G&#xF2;n &amp;#34;t&#xF3;e l&#x1EED;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#x1EC7;t ki&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1ED5; m&#xE1;u &amp; nh&#x1EAD;p vi&#x1EC7;n - 11\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505827838-_mg_3027.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>HLV Ricky ca ch nh Ho Chi Minh City Wings cng nhiu ln chy vo sn  phn ng trng ti.</p>\n<p><img alt=\"Derby b&#xF3;ng r&#x1ED5; S&#xE0;i G&#xF2;n &amp;#34;t&#xF3;e l&#x1EED;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#x1EC7;t ki&#x1EC1;u &#x111;&#x1ED5; m&#xE1;u &amp; nh&#x1EAD;p vi&#x1EC7;n - 12\" onclick=\"return openNewImage(this, \'\')\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505827838-_mg_3078.jpg\" /></p>\n<p>Mt ngi sao Vit kiu khc l Vit Arnold cng nhiu ln l nn nhn ca cc pha bng tr a  trn u c xem l nng nht ca VBA 2017. Trn derby bng r Si Gn kt thc vi chin thng t s cch bit 67-59 cho i khch Saigon Heat. Vi trn thng ny, Saigon Heat vn dn u bng xp hng VBA 2017 vi 3 trn ton thng.</p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<div><img alt=\"B&#xF3;ng r&#x1ED5;: C&#xF3; &#x201C;Gia C&#xE1;t L&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;ng&#x201D;, v&#x1EAB;n kh&#xF4;ng ng&#xF3;c n&#x1ED5;i &#x111;&#x1EA7;u\" src=\"http://anh.24h.com.vn//upload/1-2017/images/2017-03-03/image_dai_dien_gif1488505478-bongro.jpg\" /></div>\n<div>\n<div>Bng r: C Gia Ct Lng, vn khng ngc ni u</div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p>S xut hin ca Johnson vn cha th gip LA Lakers thot khi vng bn  NBA.</p></div>\n<div>Bm xem &gt;&gt;</div></div></div></div>\n<p></p></div>', 'Derby bng r Si Gn \"te la\": SAO Vit kiu  mu & nhp vin', '<div><a href=\"http://www.24h.com.vn/the-thao/derby-bong-ro-toe-lua-sao-viet-kieu-do-mau-nhap-vien-c101a904581.html\" title=\"Derby b&oacute;ng r&#7893; S&agrave;i G&ograve;n &amp;#34;t&oacute;e l&#7917;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#7879;t ki&#7873;u &#273;&#7893; m&aacute;u &amp; nh&#7853;p vi&#7879;n\"><img width=\"130\" height=\"100\" src=\"http://image.24h.com.vn/upload/3-2017/images/2017-09-19/1505827888-anh-dai-dien.jpg\" alt=\"Derby b&oacute;ng r&#7893; S&agrave;i G&ograve;n &amp;#34;t&oacute;e l&#7917;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#7879;t ki&#7873;u &#273;&#7893; m&aacute;u &amp; nh&#7853;p vi&#7879;n\" title=\"Derby b&oacute;ng r&#7893; S&agrave;i G&ograve;n &amp;#34;t&oacute;e l&#7917;a&amp;#34;: SAO Vi&#7879;t ki&#7873;u &#273;&#7893; m&aacute;u &amp; nh&#7853;p vi&#7879;n\"></a><br>Tr&#7853;n &#273;&#7845;u gi&#7919;a Saigon Heat v&agrave; Ho Chi Minh City Wings &#7903; VBA 2017 c&#7921;c n&oacute;ng v&#7899;i nh&#7919;ng pha va ch&#7841;m c&#7911;a c&#7847;u th&#7911; hai b&ecirc;n.</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'derby-bong-ro-sai-gon-toe-lua-sao-viet-kieu-do-mau-nhap-vien', '', '', '2017-09-18 17:08:33', '2017-09-18 17:08:33', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/18/derby-bong-ro-sai-gon-toe-lua-sao-viet-kieu-do-mau-nhap-vien/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
