INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1557', '1', '2017-09-19 23:37:01', '2017-09-19 23:37:01', '<div>\n<p>CPU-Z l mt chun tng hp khc bao gm c cc bi kim tra a lung v n lung. ng ngc nhin, i9 7980XE qun l li tt hn i9 7900X, mc d c cng tc  4.5GHz Turbo Max 3,0.  y, i9 7980XE t c im benchmark a nhn l 11323, hn khong 20% so vi AMD\'s 1950X v tr thnh b x l u tin trn hn 10.000 im.</p><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/20/5(1).jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/20/6(1).jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Chuyn sang CInebench r15.  y, i9-7980XE hiu nng a lung gp i ca chip 7900X v vt qua AMD 12950 khong 37%. </p><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/20/7(1).jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>im benchmark ca 7-zip l mt bi kim tra a lung, mc d c hai thnh phn  nh gi hiu sut l nn v gii nn. Trong khi , bi kim tra nn c xu hng ng h cc dng chip Intel, th gii nn li c xu hng ng h AMD.  y, i9 7980XE vt tri hn so vi sn phm hng u ca Threadripper n 30%.</p><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/20/8(1).jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Th nghim tng hp cui cng chng ta l 3DMARK Fire Strike. Core i9 7980XE t 32.000 im benchmark, im s cao nht m chng ta tng thy t bt k b x l dnh cho my tnh  bn no, cao hn 17% so vi con chip u bng ca AMD.</p>\n<p>Thng s k thut ca B x l Intel Core X Series:</p><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/20/untitled1(1).png\" /></td></tr><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div>', 'R R: im benchmark hy dit ca CPU Intel Core i9 7980XE', '<div><img src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/20/intel-core-x-cpu-skylake-x-and-kaby-lake-x-x299-hedt-platform-launch_1.jpg\" width=\"130\" height=\"100\"> ICTnews - M&ugrave;a h&egrave; n&#259;m nay, Intel &#273;&atilde; c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; th&#7901;i &#273;i&#7875;m ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh m&#7851;u chip Intel Core i9 m&#7899;i c&#7911;a h&atilde;ng l&agrave; b&#7897; ba Core i9-7940X (14 l&otilde;i), Core i9-7960X (16 l&otilde;i) v&agrave; Core i9-7980XE Extreme Edition (18 l&otilde;i) s&#7869; b&aacute;n ra v&agrave;o th&aacute;ng 10. T&#7845;t c&#7843; c&aacute;c m&#7851;u chip x&#7917; l&yacute; tr&ecirc;n &#273;&#7873;u &#273;&#432;&#7907;c b&aacute;n ra c&ugrave;ng bo m&#7841;ch ch&#7911; X299. ]]&gt;</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ro-ri-diem-benchmark-huy-diet-cua-cpu-intel-core-i9-7980xe', '', '', '2017-09-19 23:37:01', '2017-09-19 23:37:01', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/ro-ri-diem-benchmark-huy-diet-cua-cpu-intel-core-i9-7980xe/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
