INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1559', '1', '2017-09-19 23:21:01', '2017-09-19 23:21:01', '<div><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/21/he_thong_ky_thuat_attt.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>T l t chc s dng cng ngh, bin php k thut  bo v h thng mng (phn chia theo cc cng ngh, bin php k thut) nm 2016 (Ngun: Sch Trng CNTT-TT Vit Nam 2017)</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Nm 2016, cc cng ngh, bin php k thut  bo v h thng mng c cc t chc s dng gm c: phn mm chng virus mc mng (69,4% t chc s dng); tng la (63,9%); kim sot truy cp (49,4%); lc ni dung web (48,7%); b lc chng th rc (45,4%); h thng pht hin xm nhp trong mng (42,2%); h thng phng chng tn cng DoS/DDoS (39,7%); bo mt mng khng dy (32,9%); h thng qun l s kin an ton thng tin (19,1%).</p>\n<p>Cng vi , t l t chc c kh nng ghi nhn cc hnh vi tn cng mng (k c cha thnh cng) vo h thng thng tin ca t chc  tng t mc 46% ca nm 2015 ln t 62% trong nm 2016. T l t chc s dng ch k s cho cc giao dch in t nm 2016 l 54%, tng 8% so vi nm 2015. Tng s chng th s cng cng ang hot ng tnh n cui nm 2016 l 800.171 chng th s, tng 66.325 chng th s (tng ng khong 9%) so vi nm 2015.</p><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/21/thi_phan_cks.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p>Th phn dch v chng th s cng cng Vit Nam nm 2016 (Ngun: Sch Trng CNTT-TT Vit Nam 2017).</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p>V th phn dch v chng th s cng cng, trong s 8 doanh nghip trin khai kinh doanh dch v ny, nm 2016 th phn ca BKAV-CA vn ln nht, chim 29,9%; tip  l FPT-CA, chim 27,4%; SMARTSIGN chim 18,4%; SAFE-CA chim 9,6%; NEWTEL-CA chim 6,1%; NACENCOMM chim 4,8%; VIETTEL-CA chim 2,2%; v VNPT-CA chim 1,6%.</p>\n<p>Cng theo Sch Trng CNTT-TT Vit Nam 2017, t l t chc c n v/b phn chuyn trch v an ton thng tin nm 2016 l 65,6%, tng 34,9% so vi nm 2015. Nm 2016, hn 65% t chc c cn b chuyn trch v CNTT, tng gn 19% so vi nm 2015.</p>\n<p>S liu thng k trong Sch Trng CNTT-TT Vit Nam 2017 cng ch ra rng nm 2016 t l t chc c k hoch o to, tp hun v an ton thng tin l 63,6%, tng 22,8% so vi nm 2015. T l t chc nh k tuyn truyn, ph bin, nng cao nhn thc ca ngi s dng v an ton thng tin  tng t 48,1% trong nm 2015 ln 66,2% vo nm 2016.</p></div>', '62% t chc c kh nng ghi nhn hnh vi tn cng mng vo h thng', '<div><img src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/06/29/ransomware.jpg\" width=\"130\" height=\"100\"> ICTnews - Theo S&aacute;ch Tr&#7855;ng CNTT-TT Vi&#7879;t Nam 2017 v&#7915;a &#273;&#432;&#7907;c B&#7897; TT&amp;TT c&ocirc;ng b&#7889; ph&aacute;t h&agrave;nh, n&#259;m 2016 t&#7881; l&#7879; t&#7893; ch&#7913;c c&oacute; kh&#7843; n&#259;ng ghi nh&#7853;n c&aacute;c h&agrave;nh vi t&#7845;n c&ocirc;ng m&#7841;ng (k&#7875; c&#7843; ch&#432;a th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng) v&agrave;o h&#7879; th&#7889;ng th&ocirc;ng tin c&#7911;a t&#7893; ch&#7913;c l&agrave; 62%, t&#259;ng 16% so v&#7899;i 2015. ]]&gt;</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', '62-to-chuc-co-kha-nang-ghi-nhan-hanh-vi-tan-cong-mang-vao-he-thong', '', '', '2017-09-19 23:21:01', '2017-09-19 23:21:01', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/62-to-chuc-co-kha-nang-ghi-nhan-hanh-vi-tan-cong-mang-vao-he-thong/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
