INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1561', '1', '2017-09-19 11:44:01', '2017-09-19 11:44:01', '<div>\n<p>Sau khi ngi dng ti v ci t ng dng  b chn m c Red Alert 2.0 trn thit b di ng, m c ny s i ngi dng m mt ng dng ngn hng, nu pht hin y l ng dng c giao din m n c th m phng, m c ny s gi lp ng dng ban u bng giao din ngi dng gi mo. Giao din gi mo s a ra thng bo cho ngi dng v vic c li trong khi ng nhp v yu cu ngi dng xc thc li ti khon ca mnh.</p>\n<p>Ngay khi ngi dng nhp thng tin ng nhp vo giao din ngi dng gi mo, Red Alert 2.0 s ghi li v gi thng tin ny ti my ch iu khin v chim quyn kim sot ti khon. c bit, k c i vi cc ng dng s dng xc thc 2 bc (qua SMS, cuc gi) m c Red Alert 2.0 vn c th vt qua vi chc nng chn tin nhn, cuc gi trn cc thit b di ng b nhim m c.</p>\n<p>Do m c Red Alert 2.0 c vit ht sc tinh vi vi cc tnh nng  n trm thng tin ca ngi dng mt cch d dng, li ang rao trn ch en nn c kh nng nhiu i tng s mua  thc hin cc chin dch tn cng khc nhau, Cc An ton thng tin nhn nh.</p><table align=\"center\"><tbody><tr><td><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/20/ngan_hang_ma_doc_1.jpg\" /></td></tr><tr><td>\n<p><i>Hn 60 ng dng ngn hng trc tuyn v mng x hi ang l mc tiu tn cng (Ngun nh: Cc An ton thng tin)</i></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p> bo m an ton thng tin v phng trnh nguy c b tn cng bi m c, Cc An ton thng tin khuyn ngh ngi dng khng ti v ci t ng dng thng qua cc kho lu tr, lin kt khng r ngun gc; kim tra bn quyn ng dng trc khi ci t bt k ng dng no.</p>\n<p>Ngi dng cng c khuyn ngh khng ty tin tr li nhng cu hi yu cu thng tin ngi dng, mt khu ng nhp, thng tin ti chnh, th tn dng. c bit cn lu  khi cc thng ip yu cu  hin th di dng hnh nh ph trn nn ng dng ang chy.</p>\n<p>Bn cnh , ngi dng nn ci t ng dng chng m c ca nh cung cp c uy tn  c th hn ch nguy c b ly nhim m c; thng xuyn theo di knh cnh bo ca cc c quan chc nng v cc t chc ln v an ton thng tin nhm i ph kp thi vi cc nguy c tn cng mng.</p>\n<p>i vi ngn hng v cc t chc ti chnh, Cc An ton thng tin khuyn ngh cc n v ny cn kim tra, r sot cc ng dng trc tuyn  ng ti trn cc kho ng dng, cc ng dng ci t trn my ngi dng  trnh trng hp gi mo; cnh bo n ngi dng ang s dng cc ng dng do ngn hng, t chc mnh pht trin; ng thi hng xuyn theo di knh cnh bo ca cc c quan chc nng v cc t chc ln v an ton thng tin nhm i ph kp thi vi cc nguy c tn cng mng.</p>\n<p>Cng vn ca Cc An ton thng tin cng nu r, khi trin khai cc ni dung nu trn, trong trng hp cn thit, n v c th lin h vi Cc An ton thng tin theo s in thoi: 024.3943.6684, th in t ais@mic.gov.vn  c phi hp, h tr.</p></div>', 'Cnh bo m c Red Alert 2.0 trn nn Android tn cng ng dng ngn hng trc tuyn', '<div><img src=\"http://image1.ictnews.vn/_Files/2017/09/20/ngan_hang_ma_doc2.jpg\" width=\"130\" height=\"100\"> ICTnews - H&ocirc;m nay, ng&agrave;y 20/9/2017, C&#7909;c An to&agrave;n th&ocirc;ng tin - B&#7897; TT&amp;TT &#273;&atilde; c&oacute; c&ocirc;ng v&#259;n c&#7843;nh b&aacute;o c&aacute;c t&#7893; ch&#7913;c t&agrave;i ch&iacute;nh, ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng th&#432;&#417;ng m&#7841;i v&#7873; m&atilde; &#273;&#7897;c Red Alert 2.0 tr&ecirc;n n&#7873;n t&#7843;ng Android t&#7845;n c&ocirc;ng &#7913;ng d&#7909;ng ng&acirc;n h&agrave;ng tr&#7921;c tuy&#7871;n. ]]&gt;</div>', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'canh-bao-ma-doc-red-alert-2-0-tren-nen-android-tan-cong-ung-dung-ngan-hang-truc-tuyen', '', '', '2017-09-19 11:44:01', '2017-09-19 11:44:01', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/19/canh-bao-ma-doc-red-alert-2-0-tren-nen-android-tan-cong-ung-dung-ngan-hang-truc-tuyen/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
