INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1600', '1', '2017-09-20 16:58:57', '2017-09-20 16:58:57', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"41\">\n<p><b>Cuc khu chin gay gt</b></p>\n<p>Hm th Ba (19/9), trong bi pht biu u tin ca mnh ti i Hi ng Lin Hp Quc, tng thng M Donald Trump  da \"xa s hon ton\" Triu Tin nu Bnh Nhng tip tc e da M v ng minh.</p>\n<p>ng Trump cng s dng t \"ngi tn la\"  ma mai Nh lnh o Kim Jong Un.</p>\n<p>Ngoi trng Triu Tin Ri Yong Ho tr li phng vin trc ca mt khch sn gn tr s Lin Hp Quc (LHQ), vi hm  \"ch c sa on ngi c i\"  p tr bi pht biu ca tng thng M.</p>\n<p>\"Nu ng ta [Donald Trump] ngh c th khin chng ti ngc nhin bng nhng li e da y, th ng ta nhm ri,\" ng Ri ni.</p>\n<p>T u nm ti nay, Triu Tin  th 2 tn la n o xuyn lc a (ICBM) v 2 tn la bay qua khng phn Nht Bn. V th ht nhn ln th 6 ngy 3/9 ca Triu Tin cng lm chn ng th gii, gy nn nhiu tranh ci t cc nc, c bit l M v ng minh.</p>\n<p><span><b>Gi cu tr nhn o t Hn Quc</b></span></p>\n<p><span>Hm nay (21/9), Hn Quc  thng qua k hoch cu tr tr gi 8 triu USD cho Triu Tin, trong bi cnh tnh hnh cng thng bn o ang leo thang v cuc khu chin gia Bnh Nhng v Washington vn tip din.</span></p>\n<p>Reuters dn ngun tin Trung Quc cho bit, Ngoi trng Vng Ngh hm th Nm (21/9)  pht biu: \"Chng ti ku gi cc bn hy thc s bnh tnh, ng  mi vic vt qu tm kim sot.\"</p>\n<p>Trong cuc gp vi ngi ng cp Hn Quc, Kang Kyung-wha, ng Vng yu cu Hn Quc d b H thng Phng th Tn la Tm cao Giai on cui (THAAD), vi l do h thng ny l mi e da ln ti an ninh Trung Quc.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\" data-style=\"align-right\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/moon-jae-in-ap2-1505984113430.jpg\" w=\"380\" h=\"285\" alt=\"Ngo&#x1EA1;i tr&#x1B0;&#x1EDF;ng Tri&#x1EC1;u Ti&#xEA;n cay nghi&#x1EC7;t &#x111;&#xE1;p tr&#x1EA3; ph&#xE1;t bi&#x1EC3;u c&#x1EE7;a &#xF4;ng Trump t&#x1EA1;i LHQ - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"Ngo&#x1EA1;i tr&#x1B0;&#x1EDF;ng Tri&#x1EC1;u Ti&#xEA;n cay nghi&#x1EC7;t &#x111;&#xE1;p tr&#x1EA3; ph&#xE1;t bi&#x1EC3;u c&#x1EE7;a &#xF4;ng Trump t&#x1EA1;i LHQ - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"94602f90-9eaa-11e7-85fd-43ff56fe36e0\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/moon-jae-in-ap2-1505984113430.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">T l ng h ng Moon Jae-in gim mnh sau khi ng  cu tr Triu Tin. nh: AP</p></div></div>\n<p>Quyt nh h tr Triu Tin khng c hng ng ti Hn Quc, lm gim t l ng h ca ngi dn vi Tng thng Hn Quc Moon Jae-in. </p>\n<p>Nht Bn v M by t mi quan ngi vi quyt nh ny, bi LHQ va a ra cm vn mi vi Bnh Nhng hm 11/9.</p>\n<p>B trng B Thng nht Hn Quc, ng Cho Myong-gyon, cho bit gi cu tr trn khng lin quan ti mu thun a chnh tr trn bn o. Thi im thc hin vic cu tr s c xc nhn sau. </p>\n<p>Hn Quc d nh gi cc loi thc phm dinh dng tr gi 4,5 triu USD cho tr em v ph n c thai thng qua Chng trnh Lng thc Th gii (WFP) ca LHQ. Cc loi thuc men v vc xin tr gi 3,5 triu USD cng s c gi n Triu Tin qua Qu Nhi ng Lin Hp quc (UNICEF). </p>\n<p>Gim c Vn phng khu vc ng -Thi Bnh Dng ca UNICEF Karin Hulsof cho bit tr em Triu Tin ang sng trong hon cnh kh khn. </p>\n<p>B ni: \"Hin ti, c tnh c khong 200.000 tr em Triu Tin ang b suy dinh dng nghim trng, chm pht trin v c nguy c t vong cao.\" </p>\n<p>Ln cui cng Hn Quc gi cu tr cho Triu Tin l thng 12/2015, thng qua Qu Dn s Lin Hp Quc (UNFPA) di thi cu tng thng Park Geun-hye.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">V sao nhiu ngi thy \"nn\" trc bi pht biu u tin ca ng Trump ti LHQ?</div></div>', 'Ngoi trng Triu Tin cay nghit p tr pht biu ca ng Trump ti LHQ', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ngoai-truong-trieu-tien-cay-nghiet-dap-tra-phat-bieu-cua-ong-trump-tai-lhq', '', '', '2017-09-20 16:58:57', '2017-09-20 16:58:57', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/ngoai-truong-trieu-tien-cay-nghiet-dap-tra-phat-bieu-cua-ong-trump-tai-lhq/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
