INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1602', '1', '2017-09-20 16:56:30', '2017-09-20 16:56:30', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"60\">\n<p>Ti l Lm Trn. Vi thng trc, startup ca ti  nhn c s h tr t vn m tng tc khi nghip Viisa (Vietnam Innovative Startup Accelerator). Ti nhm n mc tiu s a startup hot ng trn phm vi ton cu, tuy nhin vic ny rt kh v thc t  Vit Nam, cng cha c startup no lm c. </p>\n<p>Ti vn ang vt ln vi vic xy dng quy trnh tng ngy. V ti ngh mnh nn chia s cu chuyn cng nh quan im c nhn v vn  ti sao Vit Nam cha c startup no thnh cng trong vic tng quy m ln mc ton cu.</p>\n<p>Trc ht ti mun lm r khi nim startup ton cu l g?</p>\n<p>Theo ti, y l mt cng ty  hot ng ti hn 15 quc gia trn th gii vi doanh thu hng nm ln hn 1 t USD. Nhiu ngi s ngh n Flappy Bird hoc VNG nhng ti khng cho l nh vy.</p>\n<p>Flappy Bird l mt cn lc nhng n khng tn ti lu. Tr chi ny c ti v v ph bin ti hn 15 quc gia nhng cng khng c thng tin no cho thy n mang v cho Nguyn H ng 1 t USD doanh thu.</p>\n<p>VNG l mt cu chuyn thnh cng ca Vit Nam. Tuy nhin n nay, h vn cha ra mt mt sn phm no  phm vi ton cu. Bn thn cng ty cng khng kim c 1 t USD doanh thu mi nm v c v nh h ang i kh xa mc tiu ny.</p>\n<p>Sau khi  trnh by xong v trng hp ca Flappy Bird v VNG, ti xin a ra mt vi l do khin cc startup Vit Nam kh t ti phm vi ton cu.</p>\n<p><strong>L do 1: T duy</strong></p>\n<p> Vit Nam, chng ta him thy cc  tng mang tnh cch mng. Phn ln mi ngi thng nhn vo nhng m hnh  thnh cng  nc ngoi v tm cch a phng ha  mang v Vit Nam. Tuy nhin, cc  tng ny him khi em li hng t USD v bn cht th trng trong nc qu nh.</p>\n<p>Cng c mt s doanh nhn ngh n vic xy dng startup mang tm khu vc, nhng h cha dm vt ra khi phm vi ng Nam , v ch ring vic m rng hot ng ti Thi Lan, Malaysia, Indonesia, Singapore hay Philippines  rt phc tp.</p>\n<p>Mt s rt t th ngh n Hn Quc, Nht Bn, Hng Kng v i Loan; cn vi ngi hng xm Trung Quc, tt nht hy ch n khi Elon Musk thnh lp mt  ch ring trn sao Ha.</p>\n<p><strong>L do 2: H sinh thi</strong></p>\n<p>D tt hay xu, hu ht tt c nhng nh u t ti  gp u khuyn ti nn thnh lp cng ty  Singapore hoc Hong Kong. Nguyn nhn l do mt s quy nh hnh chnh gy cn tr, khin nh u t cm thy ri ro v khng mun rt tin vo startup  Vit Nam.</p>\n<p>Mc d mc  tng trng GDP ca Vit Nam kh hp dn, nhng vn cha c khung php l  gim bt s lo ngi ny. Phn ln dng tin chy vo Singapore v cc startup trong nc cng phi sang y  k kt mt s hp ng u t.</p>\n<p>Nu th tc m mt doanh nghip mi ti Vit Nam d dng nh  Singapore, vic rt tin ra khi lnh th Vit Nam cng khng kh khn v doanh nghip c th s dng ha n in t th dng tin  v Vit Nam c l s nhiu hn.</p>\n<p>Khng t ln mi ngi ni vi ti rng tht tuyt vi khi bt u s nghip ti Vit Nam.  y c ngun nhn lc cng ngh thng tin gi r nu so vi San Francisco. iu ny ng nhng khng th m bo chng ta c th xy dng nhng  ch t USD. </p>\n<p>Bn cnh yu t chi ph, cn tnh n nhng vn  khc nh nng sut lao ng, kinh nghim, ngoi ng...</p>\n<p>Ngoi ra hin nay, tht kh cho cc lp trnh vin trong nc tm c mt cng vic thc s th v. Nhng ngi u t c xu hng dch chuyn sang cc quc gia khc nh Singapore hay Hoa K, ni h c th nhn c mc lng tt hn. V vy rt t cng ty Vit Nam gi c nhn ti  li.</p>\n<p><strong>L do 3: Tnh quc t ha</strong></p>\n<p>M rng hot ng sang cc nc khc ng ngha vi vic startup phi i mt vi rt nhiu thch thc (giao tip, vn ho, tin t, chnh lch mi gi,...) v nu ch i mt mnh, startup him khi c chun b tt  vt qua. y cng l vn  v mng li quan h, thng tin a phng v cc chin lc, chin thut. </p>\n<p>Hin khng c khun kh no tr gip cho cc startup m rng trn phm vi 15 quc gia tr ln v khng c  ngi hng dn (mentor)  st cnh cng nhng ngi sng lp i qua tng giai on pht trin.</p>\n<p>Hy thnh tht vi nhau, c startup tin phong no ang lm tt vic m rng trn 15 quc gia khng? Thc t l khng.</p>\n<p>C nh u t no sn sng tr gip startup  pht trin trn quy m ton cu? Cng khng lun. Nguyn nhn l do  giai on cui cng gip startup thu hi vn (exit), cc qu u t thng ngh n gii php n gin l bn li v thc t, hot ng IPO thng khng din ra hoc rt t khi din ra.</p>\n<p><i>Trn y l nhng chia s ca ti, hy cho ti bit bn ngh g v iu ny?</i></p>\n<div type=\"link\">Mc d c gi ti 16 triu ng cng thit k kh l i, th nhng chic qun b gy o gic ny vn chy hng</div></div>', 'C Flappy Bird hay VNG u cha phi l startup ton cu, vy l do no khin cc startup Vit khng thot ra khi \"ao lng\"?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ca-flappy-bird-hay-vng-deu-chua-phai-la-startup-toan-cau-vay-ly-do-nao-khien-cac-startup-viet-khong-thoat-ra-khoi-ao-lang', '', '', '2017-09-20 16:56:30', '2017-09-20 16:56:30', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/ca-flappy-bird-hay-vng-deu-chua-phai-la-startup-toan-cau-vay-ly-do-nao-khien-cac-startup-viet-khong-thoat-ra-khoi-ao-lang/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1603', '1', '2017-09-20 16:56:13', '2017-09-20 16:56:13', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"28\">\n<p>Ti 19/9, nh sn xut, DJ SlimV  chnh thc tung sn phm m nhc mi mang tn \"Em i c vui\" ln Youtube v cc trang nghe nhc trc tuyn. y l sn phm u tin \"o thut gia m nhc\" Slim V kt hp cng \"ph thy m nhc\" Hong Touliver.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/thumb_w/660/2017/img-0758-1505978355057.jpg\" w=\"2048\" h=\"1365\" alt=\"Slim V v&#xE0; Ho&#xE0;ng Touliver ra MV chung, x&#xF3;a nghi v&#x1EA5;n kh&#xF4;ng &#x1B0;a nhau - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"Slim V v&#xE0; Ho&#xE0;ng Touliver ra MV chung, x&#xF3;a nghi v&#x1EA5;n kh&#xF4;ng &#x1B0;a nhau - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"58f206c0-9e9d-11e7-a8db-1d1d88eac0e4\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/img-0758-1505978355057.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Slim V v Hong Touliver (bn phi).</p></div></div>\n<p>Mc d phong cch m nhc ca 2 ngi khng c nhiu im tng ng nhng SlimV v Hong Touliver  tm c ting ni chung v ho trn c style ca c 2 vo trong tc phm ny. </p>\n<p>Trc , nhiu ngi c ngh, Slim V v Hong Touliver khng a g nhau v cng dng nhc, cng  hot thm ch cn  th i u trong mt vi gameshow, chng trnh ca nhc. Thm ch tnh cch ca h cng kh tri ngc, nu Slim V l ngi ni tm, kn ting, hin lnh nhng c v ngoi y b him th Hong Touliver li mnh m, ngang tng, c tnh.</p>\n<p>Nhng thc t ngoi i, Hong Touliver v Slim l 2 anh em chi kh thn, h tr li cho khn gi bng cch ra mt cng sn phm v biu din DJ cng nhau. Gia cn bo pop ballad ang honh hnh cc bng xp hng Vpop th \" Em i c vui\" ha hn s l cn gi l lm thay i khng kh v gip cho ngi nghe cm thy yu i, lc quan hn.\n<br/></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/thumb_w/660/2017/img-0786-1505978355063.jpg\" w=\"2048\" h=\"1365\" alt=\"Slim V v&#xE0; Ho&#xE0;ng Touliver ra MV chung, x&#xF3;a nghi v&#x1EA5;n kh&#xF4;ng &#x1B0;a nhau - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" title=\"Slim V v&#xE0; Ho&#xE0;ng Touliver ra MV chung, x&#xF3;a nghi v&#x1EA5;n kh&#xF4;ng &#x1B0;a nhau - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"59201ba0-9e9d-11e7-8593-e994bba7bdba\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/img-0786-1505978355063.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">C hai u l nhng nh sn xut m nhc tr v DJ c ting hin nay ca showbiz.</p></div></div>\n<p>\"Em i c vui\" c sng tc bi 1DEE x F v cng do chnh 1DEE x F th hin cng Evy. MV ni v tinh thn lc quan vui ti, li bi ht ngn gn nhng y  ngha yu thng.</p>\n<p><span>Hnh nh MV ni v s kt hp lm vic cng nhau ca 2 nh sn xut m nhc chnh l Slim V v Hong Touliver. H</span><span> mang m nhc i biu din, m nhc ca h  lm khn gi \"get high\", chm m. Sau , h cng nhau trn chuyn xe ca con ng m nhc.</span></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/thumb_w/660/2017/job-0113-1505978355067.jpg\" w=\"5478\" h=\"7304\" alt=\"Slim V v&#xE0; Ho&#xE0;ng Touliver ra MV chung, x&#xF3;a nghi v&#x1EA5;n kh&#xF4;ng &#x1B0;a nhau - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" title=\"Slim V v&#xE0; Ho&#xE0;ng Touliver ra MV chung, x&#xF3;a nghi v&#x1EA5;n kh&#xF4;ng &#x1B0;a nhau - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"594a5ff0-9e9d-11e7-9cb4-091c7157a081\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/job-0113-1505978355067.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Slim V.</p></div></div>\n<p>Slimv nh gi Touliver l mt producer ti nng v chuyn nghip, trong tng lai 2 anh em d nh ra mt nhiu sn phm chung khc. \"Em i c vui\" ging nh liu thuc th ca h dnh cho khn gi.</p>\n<p><span>\"Vic kt hp sn phm cng nhau gia cc producer th gii  lm t lu. Vy ti sao  Vit Nam chng ta khng th? Ti tin rng s kt hp s khin bi ht phong ph hn, nhiu mu sc hn v tip cn c nhiu khn gi hn...\"  Slim V t tin chia s.</span></p>\n<div type=\"VideoStream\" data-src=\"http://vcplayer.mediacdn.vn/1.1/?_site=soha&amp;vid=sohanews/5lqimtez3f3fq3kzvk4bwg57tfgzil/2017/09/21/touliver-x-slimv-em-oi-cu-vui-official-video-1505977998585-93bb4.mp4&amp;autoplay=false&amp;_info=cf8c25addd3e4f2499024ea5dd1e34d5\" data-width=\"600px\" data-height=\"400px\" videoid=\"67801\" videoexternalid=\"undefined\">\n<div videoid=\"67801\" videoexternalid=\"undefined\"/>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">MV \"Em c vui i\" ca Slim V v Hong Touliver.</p></div></div>\n<div type=\"link\">Ca s hi ngoi Nguyn Hng t chi tit l ct-x, khoe v o iu luyn  tui 62</div></div>', 'Slim V v Hong Touliver ra MV chung, xa nghi vn khng a nhau', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'slim-v-va-hoang-touliver-ra-mv-chung-xoa-nghi-van-khong-ua-nhau', '', '', '2017-09-20 16:56:13', '2017-09-20 16:56:13', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/slim-v-va-hoang-touliver-ra-mv-chung-xoa-nghi-van-khong-ua-nhau/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
