INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1605', '1', '2017-09-20 16:48:44', '2017-09-20 16:48:44', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"16\">\n<p><span>Theo thng tin t bo ch Anh, ngi i din ca Lucas Lima  tit l rng c nhiu CLB ln mun c s phc v ca cu th ngi Brazil. Trong  nhit tnh nht l Man United.</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>\"Inter Milan, Roma, Barcelona u mun c s phc v ca Lucas Lima. Man United cng vy, h ang ro rit lin h vi chng ti. Ti ngh rng cu y thch hp vi Serie A nhng c l mi chuyn cn phi xem xt li.\" - ngi i din Luccas Badia cho hay.</p>\n<p>Lucas Lima hin ang khoc o CLB Santos(Brazil). Ma gii trc, anh ra sn 24 trn v ghi c 1 bn, 9 kin to cho ng i lp cng.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/684311840-1505985395215-1505985699788.jpg\" w=\"620\" h=\"478\" alt=\"Ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i trong cu&#x1ED9;c ti&#x1EBF;t l&#x1ED9; Man United &#x111;ang theo &#x111;u&#x1ED5;i r&#xE1;o ri&#x1EBF;t sao Brazil - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"Ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i trong cu&#x1ED9;c ti&#x1EBF;t l&#x1ED9; Man United &#x111;ang theo &#x111;u&#x1ED5;i r&#xE1;o ri&#x1EBF;t sao Brazil - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"487dc6b0-9eae-11e7-9ebe-f7ec689d934a\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/684311840-1505985395215-1505985699788.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Man United ang theo ui tin v ca Santos.</p></div></div>\n<p>\"Hp ng ca cu y s kt thc vo ngy 31/12 ti. Hin ti nhiu CLB quan tm n cu y. Ti khng chc chn  kin ca Lucas (Lima) l nh th no\".</p>\n<p>Trc , trong k chuyn nhng ma H 2017, c thng tin cho hay Crystal Palace v Fenerbahce  ch  n tin v ny. H cng ra gi v khao kht c c s phc v ca Lucas nhng khng nhn c ci gt u.</p>\n<p>Mc d thi im , Lima tng ng nh ln Instagram vi chi tit lin quan n Fenerbahce khin nhiu ngi lm tng c bn  mi.</p>\n<p>Lucas (Lima) gia nhp Santos t nm 2013 v tr thnh mt phn quan trng ca CLB ny t thi im  cho n nay.</p>\n<p>\n<br/></p>\n<div type=\"link\">Ngi hm m phn i quyt lit, khng mun Kiatisak nm qun  TQG Vit Nam</div></div>', 'Ngi trong cuc tit l Man United ang theo ui ro rit sao Brazil', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nguoi-trong-cuoc-tiet-lo-man-united-dang-theo-duoi-rao-riet-sao-brazil', '', '', '2017-09-20 16:48:44', '2017-09-20 16:48:44', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/nguoi-trong-cuoc-tiet-lo-man-united-dang-theo-duoi-rao-riet-sao-brazil/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
