INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1607', '1', '2017-09-20 16:33:43', '2017-09-20 16:33:43', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"17\">\n<p>Chiu 21/9, ti bui hp bo thng k, phng vin   ngh Ngi pht ngn B Ngoi giao thng tin thm v vic pha Nga ang chuyn tu chin Gepad 3.9 cho Vit Nam.</p>\n<p>\"Vic Nga giao tu khu trc Gepad 3.9 cho Vit Nam nm trong khun kh hp tc quc phng gia hai nc nhm p ng nhu cu m bo an ninh, quc phng ca Vit Nam\", Ngi pht ngn B Ngoi giao L Th Thu Hng tr li.</p>\n<p><span>V thng tin, sp ti c s iu lc lng ti tp trn ti Bin ng v y c coi l lc lng ln nht trong 20 nm qua, ng thi bo ch Trung Quc  c phn i, Ngi pht ngn B Ngoi giao nu:</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>\"Vit Nam lun tn trng quyn ca mi quc gia thc hin quyn t do hng hi, hng khng ph hp vi lut php quc t. </p>\n<p>Duy tr ha bnh n nh ca khu vc, trong , c Bin ng l trch nhim, quyn li ca mi quc gia trong khu vc.</p>\n<p>Mi hot ng ca cc quc gia nu ng gp vo mc tiu chung ny th u ng hoan nghnh\".</p>\n<div data-back=\"#FFFEC7\" data-border=\"#FF7D00\" type=\"content\">\n<div placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p n&#x1ED9;i dung]\" readability=\"10\">\n<p>Theo cp nht mi nht t trang thng tin hng hi Marinetraffic cho thy tu Rolldock Star ch theo tu h v tn la Gepard th 3 ca HQVN  ri cng Novorossiysk ln ng v nc.</p>\n<p>T bo Sina ca Trung Quc  dn li bc nh chp ngy 16/9, khi tu vn ti siu trng siu trng Rolldock Star ang ch chic Gepard 3.9 th ba ca Hi qun Vit Nam c chuyn gh thm ngn n Istanbul, lc ang trn ng di chuyn t qun cng Novorossiysk (Nga) n Cam Ranh.</p>\n<p>Theo thng tin cp nht n ngy 18/9 t trang thng tin hng hi marinetraffic.com th hin ti con tu ang  vng bin Ionia (thuc bin a Trung Hi). im n ca con tu cng  c ci t l cng Cam Ranh, Vit Nam.\n<br/></p>\n<p>Trc , vo ngy 4/9, tu Rolldock Star  di chuyn n cng Novorossiysk  Bin en, Nga ni cp tu h v tn la Gepard th hai (chic s 3 v s 4) thc hin cng tc th nghim v hun luyn chuyn loi cho cc kp tu HQVN  tin hnh vn chuyn chic Gepard th 3 v Vit Nam. </p></div></div>\n<div type=\"link\">Nh g  s ca Chi cc trng Kim lm: \'C c g tt, xu, nhiu ch hin b mi mt\"</div></div>', 'B Ngoi giao thng tin vic Nga chuyn tu chin Gepard 3.9 cho Vit Nam', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'bo-ngoai-giao-thong-tin-viec-nga-chuyen-tau-chien-gepard-3-9-cho-viet-nam', '', '', '2017-09-20 16:33:43', '2017-09-20 16:33:43', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/bo-ngoai-giao-thong-tin-viec-nga-chuyen-tau-chien-gepard-3-9-cho-viet-nam/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1608', '1', '2017-09-20 16:30:00', '2017-09-20 16:30:00', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"56\">\n<p>Thanh tra B Ni v va c thng bo Kt lun thanh tra vic thc hin cc quy nh ca php lut v qun l bin ch cng chc; tuyn dng cng chc; b nhim cng chc lnh o, qun l; s lng cp ph; qun l h s cng chc... trong cc c quan hnh chnh nh nc ca UBND tnh Lo Cai (t ngy 1/1/2014 n ngy 31/12/2016).</p>\n<p>Theo , v c bn, cng tc qun l bin ch cng chc c UBND tnh Lo Cai v cc c quan, n v thc hin theo quy nh php lut. </p>\n<p>Tuy nhin, s lng cng chc tinh gin bin ch theo Ngh nh s 108 2014/N-CP trong giai on thanh tra cha m bo t l theo  n  c ph duyt (trong giai on thanh tra  tinh gin c 40 trng hp)</p>\n<p>Vic tip nhn cng chc khng qua thi tuyn c UBND tnh Lo Cai c bn thc hin ng thm quyn, trnh t, th tc theo quy nh nhng mt s h s tip nhn cha m bo cc thnh phn h s, UBND tnh Lo Cai cha c vn bn bo co B Ni v v cc trng hp l vin chc c tip nhn vo cng chc khng qua thi.</p>\n<p>Vic b nhim, b nhim li cng chc gi chc v lnh o, qun l trong cc c quan, n v c xut pht t yu cu nhim v. </p>\n<p>Cc cng chc c b nhim, b nhim li  c bn p ng cc iu kin, tiu chun do nh nc v tnh quy nh.</p>\n<p>Tuy nhin, theo Thanh tra B Ni v, mt s cng chc c b nhim cha p ng y  cc iu kin, tiu chun v trnh  l lun chnh tr, qun l nh nc, ngoi ng, tin hc; mt s quyt nh b nhim li v quyt nh ko di thi gian gi chc v khng m bo thi gian theo quy nh.</p>\n<p>V qun l h s cng chc, Thanh tra B Ni v nhn nh c bn c cc c quan, n v trin khai thc hin, trong h s cng chc  lu gi c phn ln thnh phn h s theo quy nh. </p>\n<p>Nhng h s cng chc thuc thm quyn qun l ca Ch tch UBND tnh cha c trin khai v lu gi ti S Ni v. Ti liu lin quan n vic b nhim, b nhim li ca cc c quan, n v khng c lu trong h s cng chc.</p>\n<p>Ngoi ra, n thi im thanh tra, c 6 c quan, n v cn s dng 34 hp ng lao ng lm cng tc chuyn mn l khng ng quy nh ca Lut Cn b, cng chc v cc vn bn hng dn thi hnh.</p>\n<p>T kt lun trn, Thanh tra B Ni v kin ngh Ch tch UBND tnh Lo Cai ch o cc c quan, n v r sot, kp thi pht hin cc trng hp cn cha p ng iu kin, tiu chun  c k hoch c cng chc i o to, bi dng; quy nh thi hn bt buc  cng chc hon thin cc iu kin, tiu chun; min nhim cc trng hp khi ht thi hn m cha p ng y  cc iu kin, tiu chun chc danh; khng b nhim li i vi cc trng hp khng m bo iu kin, tiu chun.</p>\n<p>Cng vi  l ch o chm dt vic s dng 34 lao ng hp ng lm cng tc chuyn mn, nghip v trong c quan, t chc hnh chnh; chm dt vic k v s dng lao ng hp ng lm cng tc chuyn mn ti cc c quan, n v.</p>\n<p>Thanh tra B Ni v cng kin ngh kim im, lm r trch nhim cc c quan, t chc, c nhn c lin quan  xy ra nhng hn ch, tn ti nh  nu trn  c hinh thc x l ph hp./.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">Qun 1 buc thi vic Ph ch tch phng b nhim s</div></div>', 'Lo Cai b nhim mt s cng chc cha  iu kin, tiu chun', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'lao-cai-bo-nhiem-mot-so-cong-chuc-chua-du-dieu-kien-tieu-chuan', '', '', '2017-09-20 16:30:00', '2017-09-20 16:30:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/lao-cai-bo-nhiem-mot-so-cong-chuc-chua-du-dieu-kien-tieu-chuan/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1609', '1', '2017-09-20 16:28:00', '2017-09-20 16:28:00', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"31\">\n<p>Samsung  chn ng thi im  pht trin xe  t in c kh nng hot ng tm xa khi Trung Quc va c k hoch cm hon ton cc loi xe s dng ng c xng, v ngi khng l Volkswagen ca ngnh cng nghip -t cng  ha hn ti nm 2030 s a ra th trng nhng phin bn chy in ca tt c cc dng xe ca hng.</p>\n<p><strong>i t H Ni n Hu s n gin hn rt nhiu</strong></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505879382189.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"440\" alt=\"Tuy&#xEA;n chi&#x1EBF;n v&#x1EDB;i Tesla, Samsung ra m&#x1EAF;t pin m&#x1EDB;i cho &#xF4;-t&#xF4; &#x111;i&#x1EC7;n: &#x110;i t&#x1EEB; H&#xE0; N&#x1ED9;i &#x111;&#x1EBF;n Hu&#x1EBF; ch&#x1EC9; v&#x1EDB;i m&#x1ED9;t l&#x1EA7;n s&#x1EA1;c - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"Tuy&#xEA;n chi&#x1EBF;n v&#x1EDB;i Tesla, Samsung ra m&#x1EAF;t pin m&#x1EDB;i cho &#xF4;-t&#xF4; &#x111;i&#x1EC7;n: &#x110;i t&#x1EEB; H&#xE0; N&#x1ED9;i &#x111;&#x1EBF;n Hu&#x1EBF; ch&#x1EC9; v&#x1EDB;i m&#x1ED9;t l&#x1EA7;n s&#x1EA1;c - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"bbaceb50-9db6-11e7-a428-316e6a252121\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505879382189.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p>Mi cng ty u hiu rng: hng triu chic xe trong tng lai s cn cc thi pin tht tru, v ti trin lm Motor Show 2017 din ra  Frankfurt mi y Samsung  gii thiu khi pin a nng th h mi. </p>\n<p>Nh sn xut Hn Quc khng nh sn phm mi s gip cho nhng chic -t in i c 700 km ch vi mt ln sc.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505879383489.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"440\" alt=\"Tuy&#xEA;n chi&#x1EBF;n v&#x1EDB;i Tesla, Samsung ra m&#x1EAF;t pin m&#x1EDB;i cho &#xF4;-t&#xF4; &#x111;i&#x1EC7;n: &#x110;i t&#x1EEB; H&#xE0; N&#x1ED9;i &#x111;&#x1EBF;n Hu&#x1EBF; ch&#x1EC9; v&#x1EDB;i m&#x1ED9;t l&#x1EA7;n s&#x1EA1;c - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" title=\"Tuy&#xEA;n chi&#x1EBF;n v&#x1EDB;i Tesla, Samsung ra m&#x1EAF;t pin m&#x1EDB;i cho &#xF4;-t&#xF4; &#x111;i&#x1EC7;n: &#x110;i t&#x1EEB; H&#xE0; N&#x1ED9;i &#x111;&#x1EBF;n Hu&#x1EBF; ch&#x1EC9; v&#x1EDB;i m&#x1ED9;t l&#x1EA7;n s&#x1EA1;c - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"bcbe5b50-9db6-11e7-8c43-1b84942e6a4c\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505879383489.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p>Qung ng ny tng ng vi khong cch t H Ni n Hu, v nu bn chy -t in s dng pin ca Samsung th s khng phi gh cc trm xng  mua xng, ng thi trnh c tnh trng xng bn, xng pha. </p>\n<p>iu ny va th v li va kh tin khi m thm ch mu xe mnh nht ca Tesla cng cha th lm c iu ny, trong khi Model 3 gi r ch c th chy c 350 km vi mt ln sc.</p>\n<p><strong>T l thuyt n thc t</strong></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-2-1505879383491.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"440\" alt=\"Tuy&#xEA;n chi&#x1EBF;n v&#x1EDB;i Tesla, Samsung ra m&#x1EAF;t pin m&#x1EDB;i cho &#xF4;-t&#xF4; &#x111;i&#x1EC7;n: &#x110;i t&#x1EEB; H&#xE0; N&#x1ED9;i &#x111;&#x1EBF;n Hu&#x1EBF; ch&#x1EC9; v&#x1EDB;i m&#x1ED9;t l&#x1EA7;n s&#x1EA1;c - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" title=\"Tuy&#xEA;n chi&#x1EBF;n v&#x1EDB;i Tesla, Samsung ra m&#x1EAF;t pin m&#x1EDB;i cho &#xF4;-t&#xF4; &#x111;i&#x1EC7;n: &#x110;i t&#x1EEB; H&#xE0; N&#x1ED9;i &#x111;&#x1EBF;n Hu&#x1EBF; ch&#x1EC9; v&#x1EDB;i m&#x1ED9;t l&#x1EA7;n s&#x1EA1;c - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"bcc11a70-9db6-11e7-a3ce-dbff8e643ab9\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-2-1505879383491.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p>C mt s tht l: Pin ca Tesla  lm vic t nhiu nm nay trn nhng con ng thc t, cn sn phm t ph v sng to ca Samsung mi ch  giai on sn phm mu v cn cha c a vo sn xut. </p>\n<p>D con s 700 km m Samsung a ra l v cng n tng nhng mt khi n cha c th nghim trn ng chy th chng ta cng khng th bit c liu chic xe in no c th i c qung ng ln nh vy vi vin pin ca Samsung. </p>\n<p>Cc thng s k thut nh khi lng, kh nng vn hnh v nhng c tnh khc u khng c h l.</p>\n<p><strong>Musk s ni g?</strong></p>\n<p>Hin ti, chng ta mi ch bit rng pin ca Samsung c mt s im tng ng vi loi pin hnh tr m Tesla s dng trong Model 3.</p>\n<p>Theo li ca Elon Musk th y l loi pin c mt  cao nht trn th gii. Trong mt thng co bo ch, Samsung tuyn b rng ngi dng c th d dng lp thm cc khi pin vo vin pin ca hng  tng qung ng m xe c th i c.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-3-1505879383493.jpg\" w=\"578\" h=\"430\" alt=\"Tuy&#xEA;n chi&#x1EBF;n v&#x1EDB;i Tesla, Samsung ra m&#x1EAF;t pin m&#x1EDB;i cho &#xF4;-t&#xF4; &#x111;i&#x1EC7;n: &#x110;i t&#x1EEB; H&#xE0; N&#x1ED9;i &#x111;&#x1EBF;n Hu&#x1EBF; ch&#x1EC9; v&#x1EDB;i m&#x1ED9;t l&#x1EA7;n s&#x1EA1;c - &#x1EA2;nh 4.\" title=\"Tuy&#xEA;n chi&#x1EBF;n v&#x1EDB;i Tesla, Samsung ra m&#x1EAF;t pin m&#x1EDB;i cho &#xF4;-t&#xF4; &#x111;i&#x1EC7;n: &#x110;i t&#x1EEB; H&#xE0; N&#x1ED9;i &#x111;&#x1EBF;n Hu&#x1EBF; ch&#x1EC9; v&#x1EDB;i m&#x1ED9;t l&#x1EA7;n s&#x1EA1;c - &#x1EA2;nh 4.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"bc470870-9db6-11e7-a428-316e6a252121\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-3-1505879383493.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Pin ca Model 3</p></div></div>\n<p>Vi loi pin mi ca chng ti, ngi dng c th thay i s lng module ty  ging nh xp sch ln k vy. </p>\n<p>Ly v d, nu mt chic xe hng sang lp 20 module th n c th i c t 600 n 700 km, trong khi mt chic sedan thng thng th 10 -12 module s gip n chy c n 300 km trc khi phi sc li.</p>\n<p><strong>Li th ring ca Tesla</strong></p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-4-1505879383495.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"371\" alt=\"Tuy&#xEA;n chi&#x1EBF;n v&#x1EDB;i Tesla, Samsung ra m&#x1EAF;t pin m&#x1EDB;i cho &#xF4;-t&#xF4; &#x111;i&#x1EC7;n: &#x110;i t&#x1EEB; H&#xE0; N&#x1ED9;i &#x111;&#x1EBF;n Hu&#x1EBF; ch&#x1EC9; v&#x1EDB;i m&#x1ED9;t l&#x1EA7;n s&#x1EA1;c - &#x1EA2;nh 5.\" title=\"Tuy&#xEA;n chi&#x1EBF;n v&#x1EDB;i Tesla, Samsung ra m&#x1EAF;t pin m&#x1EDB;i cho &#xF4;-t&#xF4; &#x111;i&#x1EC7;n: &#x110;i t&#x1EEB; H&#xE0; N&#x1ED9;i &#x111;&#x1EBF;n Hu&#x1EBF; ch&#x1EC9; v&#x1EDB;i m&#x1ED9;t l&#x1EA7;n s&#x1EA1;c - &#x1EA2;nh 5.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"bcb819c0-9db6-11e7-a428-316e6a252121\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-4-1505879383495.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p>Li p tr mang tnh chin lc ca Tesla i vi Samsung chnh l mng li cc trm sc in c kh nng sc y pin cho -t in ch trong vi pht m hng ny hin ang tch cc pht trin. </p>\n<p>Cuc chin gia Tesla  vi th mnh v c s h tng - v Samsung  vi th mnh v cng ngh - chc chn s rt khc lit trong nhng nm sp ti khi m nhng chic xe -t chy in ang ngy cng xut hin nhiu hn trn ng ph.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">Cha bit \"c mp  Qung Ninh\" l tht hay gi, nhng y l nhng loi k d nht!</div></div>', 'Tuyn chin vi Tesla, Samsung ra mt pin mi cho -t in: i t H Ni n Hu ch vi mt ln sc', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tuyen-chien-voi-tesla-samsung-ra-mat-pin-moi-cho-o-to-dien-di-tu-ha-noi-den-hue-chi-voi-mot-lan-sac', '', '', '2017-09-20 16:28:00', '2017-09-20 16:28:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/tuyen-chien-voi-tesla-samsung-ra-mat-pin-moi-cho-o-to-dien-di-tu-ha-noi-den-hue-chi-voi-mot-lan-sac/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
