INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1611', '1', '2017-09-20 16:25:53', '2017-09-20 16:25:53', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"13\">\n<p><span>H H v Kim L d cha tng khng nh c mi quan h tnh cm nhng thng xuyn i du lch, check-in cng a im, mang  i,... nhng bng chng  phn no khin cho ngi hm m t c cu tr li cho chnh mnh. </span></p>\n<p><span>Ch cch y t ngy, cp i cng xut hin ti Php, trn instagram \"n hong gii tr\" ng ti hnh nh nm tay mt ngi n ng m khng kh  nhn ra  chnh l Kim L. Sau , H H tr v  chun b cho bui ra mt DVD \"Love Songs\" din ra vo ti ngy 20/9.</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>Va v ti Vit Nam t ngy, H Ngc H v Kim L ti tip tc ln ng sang New York sng nay (21/9). C hai din trang phc tng en ging nhau, i tch nhau kh xa nhng khi lm th tc xut cnh li ci a, ni chuyn vui v. </p>\n<p>Nhng hnh nh m chng ti ghi li c:</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505985853487.jpg\" w=\"620\" h=\"465\" alt=\"V&#x1EEB;a tr&#x1EDF; v&#x1EC1; t&#x1EEB; Paris, H&#xE0; H&#x1ED3; - Kim L&#xFD; ti&#x1EBF;p t&#x1EE5;c b&#x1ECB; b&#x1EAF;t g&#x1EB7;p di&#x1EC7;n &#x111;&#x1ED3; &#x111;&#xF4;i c&#xF9;ng nhau l&#xEA;n &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;ng sang New York - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"V&#x1EEB;a tr&#x1EDF; v&#x1EC1; t&#x1EEB; Paris, H&#xE0; H&#x1ED3; - Kim L&#xFD; ti&#x1EBF;p t&#x1EE5;c b&#x1ECB; b&#x1EAF;t g&#x1EB7;p di&#x1EC7;n &#x111;&#x1ED3; &#x111;&#xF4;i c&#xF9;ng nhau l&#xEA;n &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;ng sang New York - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"a2d16720-9eae-11e7-9e79-dd2fe1f3f432\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505985853487.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">H H - Kim L b bt gp ti sn bay sng nay.</p></div></div>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505985854710.jpg\" w=\"620\" h=\"465\" alt=\"V&#x1EEB;a tr&#x1EDF; v&#x1EC1; t&#x1EEB; Paris, H&#xE0; H&#x1ED3; - Kim L&#x