INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1613', '1', '2017-09-20 16:20:09', '2017-09-20 16:20:09', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"59\">\n<p><span>Nu quan im xung quanh vic H Ni d kin thc hin ch trng i t ly h tng l 4 cy cu bc qua sng Hng, ti bui hp bo qu 3 chiu 20/9, B trng B TN&amp;MT Trn Hng H cho rng, khi ngun lc ca t nc, Chnh ph kh khn th vic huy ng c hnh thc BT s c thm nhiu cng trnh thnh cng, ngi dn cng c hng li.</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>4 cy cu s to ra 4 vng pht trin mi, nh   Nng trc y, c ch t bn khng ai mua nhng khi lm cu xong th t  c nng gi ln. Tt nhin, phi tnh ton hi ho li ch cho nh u t, ngi dn v nh nc na. </p>\n<p>Cu chuyn nm  ch kim sot cht ch cc khu v thi im nh gi t. y l ch trng ng n, bi  H Ni c thm 4 cy cu mi th s c 4 vng pht trin mi v ti tin rng t tng gi cp s nhn, B trng Trn Hng H nh gi.</p>\n<p>Ni thm v hnh thc u t BT (xy dng- chuyn giao) khi thc hin 4 cy cu ny cc nh u t s c i t th no, ng o Trung Chnh, Ph Tng cc trng Tng cc Qun l t ai (B Ti nguyn v mi trng) ch ra im vng, khi m gi thu v cng trnh h tng th phi cho nh u t bit h s c bao nhiu t, tuy nhin phi ch khi no xy dng h tng xong th chng ti mi nh gi t c th c.</p>\n<p>c bit, n nay c cc nh u t ln ng k tham gia u t 4 cu cu tr gi gn 2 t ng bc qua sng Hng v sng ung gm c Tp on T&amp;T, SunGroup, Him Lam, VinGroup </p>\n<p>Cc nh u t b tin ra lm cng trnh, thnh ph s thanh ton bng qu t 836ha. Qu t ny thuc a phn ca 3 huyn: ng Anh, Gia Lm v Long Bin u nm  khu vc pha Bc Th .</p>\n<p>C th qu t ny nm ri rc ti cc x ng Hi, Xun Canh, Mai Lm, Dc T (huyn ng Anh); cc x Yn Thng, Yn Vin, Dng X, ng D, nh Xuyn (huyn Gia Lm) v cc phng Long Bin, C Khi (qun Long Bin)</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505985502244.jpg\" w=\"640\" h=\"439\" alt=\" B&#x1ED9; tr&#x1B0;&#x1EDF;ng Tr&#x1EA7;n H&#x1ED3;ng H&#xE0;: Gi&#xE1; &#x111;&#x1EA5;t s&#x1EBD; t&#x103;ng c&#x1EA5;p s&#x1ED1; nh&#xE2;n t&#x1EA1;i khu v&#x1EF1;c 4 c&#xE2;y c&#x1EA7;u m&#x1EDB;i g&#x1EA7;n 2 t&#x1EF7; USD s&#x1EAF;p x&#xE2;y t&#x1EA1;i H&#xE0; N&#x1ED9;i - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\" B&#x1ED9; tr&#x1B0;&#x1EDF;ng Tr&#x1EA7;n H&#x1ED3;ng H&#xE0;: Gi&#xE1; &#x111;&#x1EA5;t s&#x1EBD; t&#x103;ng c&#x1EA5;p s&#x1ED1; nh&#xE2;n t&#x1EA1;i khu v&#x1EF1;c 4 c&#xE2;y c&#x1EA7;u m&#x1EDB;i g&#x1EA7;n 2 t&#x1EF7; USD s&#x1EAF;p x&#xE2;y t&#x1EA1;i H&#xE0; N&#x1ED9;i - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"d178dfa0-9ead-11e7-99f0-ebffd5c9ed61\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505985502244.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Qu t d kin pht trin  th i ng xy dng cu mi (khu vc khoanh ).</p></div></div>\n<p>Theo kho st ca chng ti, hin ti, c 3 ng ln a c SunGroup, VinGroup v Him Lam u  v ang c k hoch ln pht trin cc d n BS ln  khu vc bn kia sng Hng (thuc huyn ng Anh, Gia Lm, Long Bin).</p>\n<p>Hin SunGroup ang trin khai xy dng D n cng vin Kim Quy, nm ti giao l gia ng V Nguyn Gip vi ng 5 ko di thuc a phn huyn ng Anh, c quy m din tch hn 100ha. </p>\n<p>D n c xy dng theo m hnh Universal Studios, Disneyland ni ting ton cu. Cng trnh c tng mc u t 4.600 t, d kin hon thnh sau 18 thng thi cng k t khi khi cng hi thng 9/2016.</p>\n<p>Trong khi , tp on Him Lam cng  c k hoch thu tm qu t ln trc  khi c giao lm BT d n nt giao trung tm qun Long Bin c tng mc u t 2.847 t ng. </p>\n<p>Theo , Him Lam c thanh ton bng qu t 20ha t ti Dng X (Gia Lm) 320ha t ti cc phng Long Bin v Cc Khi thuc qun Long Bin. D n nt giao ny  hon thnh vo u nm 2016.</p>\n<p>Cc siu d n ca Vingroup, Sungroup v Him Lam.. ang to nn mt c hch mi cho bt ng sn cc khu vc xung quanh nh Gia Lm, Long Bin, ng Anh, M Linh. Cng v th, gii u t a c cng  bt u  mt ti mt s khu vc ny.</p>\n<div type=\"insertembedcode\"/>\n<p><i>4 cy cu mi tr gi gn 2 t USD sp xy ti H Ni.</i></p>\n<div type=\"link\">N cng ln n hn 2 triu t ng, tng ng 61 GDP</div></div>', 'B trng Trn Hng H: Gi t s tng cp s nhn ti khu vc 4 cy cu mi gn 2 t USD sp xy ti H Ni', '', 'pu