INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1615', '1', '2017-09-20 16:19:36', '2017-09-20 16:19:36', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"77\">\n<p>Mt b m n thn tng c t nhiu tn thng sau  v vi chng c, nhng vn lc quan sng, lc quan yu. Mt anh chng Hn Quc thnh t, l trai tn li trt em lng yu c say m, sn sng vt mi ro cn  n vi ngi ph n mnh yu thng. Cu chuyn tnh p xa m khong cch trn l ca c gi Vit Trnh Thy Hng v anh chng Hn Quc si tnh Choi Bong Je.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505985204743.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"440\" alt=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"1f433b00-9ead-11e7-8ba8-c7be43bdd9b8\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505985204743.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Hng v Bong Je quen nhau khi Hng sang Hn du hc.</p></div></div>\n<p>Nm 2012, Hng trng mt hc bng sang Hn Quc hc ngn ng. Nguyn do ca c hi ny cng kh th v khi trong mt ln lm vic, thy nhng ngi Hn Quc ni chuyn vi nhau m Hng ch bit ng ngc v khng hiu g. </p>\n<p>n khi trao i vi sp, Hng c tuyn b thng thn vi anh rng c s i hc ting Hn  hiu c nhng g h ni. Ban u, sp Hng ch ci v bo: anh  nghe quen lm cu ni ny ri nhng sau 5 nm nhng ngi ni vi anh cu y thm ch cn chng cho anh c mt cu bng ting Hn Quc. </p>\n<p>Nghe sp ni vy, Hng ch lng lng i ra. Mt thng sau, c quay tr li v khin sp phi ngc nhin v kh nng giao tip ca mnh. C nhanh chng nhn c hc bng do ch thn sp trao tng. Nm  c 33 tui.</p>\n<p>Sang Hn hc ting  mt vic trc y Hng cha tng ngh ti li tr thnh s tht. Thi gian u sng  x kim chi, c hay chn cch lang thang bng tu in ngm i khp ni. Nhng chuyn i c ni tip nhau, chng my chc m gn ht thi gian du hc. </p>\n<p>Mt ngy n, Hng nhn c hng trm cuc gi l. Vi bn tnh t m, c gi li th c bit pha u dy bn kia l mt ngi n ng. Anh thao thao bt tuyt bng ting Anh nhng Hng khng th nghe ni mt t bi t qu. </p>\n<p>C bo: anh c th chuyn sang ting Hn c khng v hai ngi tip tc cu chuyn dang d bng ting Hn. Anh t gii thiu anh tn l Choi Bong Je. V cuc gi nh mnh   a hai ngi ti bn nhau.</p>\n<p>Gia nm 2013, Hng gp Choi Bong Je ngoi i ln u tin vo ng ngy sinh nht c ni x ngi. C nh mi hm , c phi ngi tu in ngm sut 1 ting ng h v ni hn gp kh xa. n khi gp nhau, n tng u tin ca Hng l: sao anh chng ny va xu trai li va ki th nh. </p>\n<p>Nhng ri li tc li v  nh ban u ca c cng ch gp chi chi thi. Sut c bui hn, Hng   thy anh chng mi m ngm ngha c n mc long ngng ri in thoi n 3 ln. </p>\n<p>Mc d mi gp nhng Hng cng thng thn ni rng c  c mt i chng v mt cu con trai 5 tui, Hng cng  33 tui ri. C l v m mn c gi Vit m anh chng cng chng nh ht nhng g c ni</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505985205875.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"825\" alt=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" title=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"20a6e9b0-9ead-11e7-8ba8-c7be43bdd9b8\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1505985205875.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-2-1505985205877.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"472\" alt=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" title=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"1ff83320-9ead-11e7-ad93-41df1fc652ef\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-2-1505985205877.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-3-1505985205878.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"472\" alt=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 4.\" title=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 4.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"20a3b560-9ead-11e7-ad93-41df1fc652ef\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-3-1505985205878.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Hai ngi  vt nhiu ro cn  n bn nhau.</p></div></div>\n<p>Kt thc bui hn, anh chng Hn Quc cn a c vt 200 km bng xe  t v k tc x ca trng. C nh th, u n th 7, Ch nht no Bong Je cng ti trng a n Hng i chi khp Hn Quc. Bui i chi no cng rt vui v th v.</p>\n<p>n ngy hon thnh kha hc, Hng tm bit Hn Quc, tm bit lun c anh chng Bong Je, trong u lc  khng c qu nhiu hi vng rng mi quan h ca c hai s tin xa hn. </p>\n<p>Ai ng, sau 1 thng Bong Je khng chu ni ni nh nhung Hng nn  mnh bo tm v Vit Nam thm c, mc d trc  anh cn cha tng t chn n y. </p>\n<p>Hm , Hng n Bong Je sau gi lm vic, a anh i do quanh ph c v gp g vi ngi bn thn. Hai ngi li chia tay nhau, Bong Je v Hn Quc.</p>\n<p>Nhng cuc tr chuyn c th tip din sut c nm tri sau . Ri mt ngy, Bong Je bt ng ni li chia tay, anh bo s sang rp lm vic. T i tri dy, Hng ng  chia tay cho d trong lng c nhiu m c.</p>\n<p>2 thng sau, Hng trn ng i cng tc  in Bin th nhn c tin nhn ca Bong Je: \"Anh sang gp em c khng?\". Hng ch tr li bng qu rng c ng . Cho n ti hm , tin nhn ca Bong Je hin n, anh thng bo rng mnh  n sn bay Ni Bi. Lc ny th Hng mi tin rng anh sang tm c tht.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-4-1505985205880.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"495\" alt=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 5.\" title=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 5.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"20a00be0-9ead-11e7-99f0-ebffd5c9ed61\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-4-1505985205880.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-5-1505985205881.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"495\" alt=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 6.\" title=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 6.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"20a1b990-9ead-11e7-9d76-6977fceb5047\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-5-1505985205881.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-6-1505985205882.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"495\" alt=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 7.\" title=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 7.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"20a4c6d0-9ead-11e7-8593-e994bba7bdba\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-6-1505985205882.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-7-1505985205883.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"495\" alt=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 8.\" title=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 8.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"216afd00-9ead-11e7-af3a-13b6315b65f4\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-7-1505985205883.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-8-1505985205884.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"528\" alt=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 9.\" title=\"Ch&#xE0;ng trai H&#xE0;n si t&#xEC;nh v&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;t r&#xE0;o c&#x1EA3;n, nhi&#x1EC1;u l&#x1EA7;n t&#xEC;m v&#x1EC1; Vi&#x1EC7;t Nam xin c&#x1B0;&#x1EDB;i b&#x1EB1;ng &#x111;&#x1B0;&#x1EE3;c m&#x1EB9; &#x111;&#x1A1;n th&#xE2;n - &#x1EA2;nh 9.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"20a5b130-9ead-11e7-b64e-5167602a163f\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-8-1505985205884.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">T m ca hai ngi hin ti.</p></div></div>\n<p>2 hm sau, Hng mi bay v H Ni. Gp c, Bong Je ch bit ni xin li c tht nhiu v xin c lm bn trai Hng mt cch nghim tc v xc nh tng lai lu di. Hai thng tip theo, anh li sang Vit Nam cu hn c. Hai ngi cng nhanh chng c tin vui ngay sau . Nghe Hng thng bo tin c bu, Bong Je vui mng khn xit, anh nng nc xin ci.</p>\n<p>Nm 2015 c gi l mt nm ng nh ca Hng - Bong Je khi cng lc n 2 tin vui: mt thin thn nh v m ci. Trong b nh ci chp theo phong cch lng mn, Hng lng ly trong chic vy ci snh bc bn ch r, hnh phc tro dng khi k t y h  chnh thc tr thnh mt gia nh, cng vun p dng xy t m. </p>\n<p>Nhng v cng vic v khong cch xa xi, hai ngi vn mi ngi mt ni cho ti tn nm ngoi mi chnh chc v chung mt nh.</p>\n<p>Trong mt Hng, ng x l mu ngi lch thip v sng quy tc. \"Ngy u gp gia nh mnh, anh mc comple tht cavat bc chn vo nh l qu ly b m. Sau kt hn th c kh nhiu khng hong do bt ng ngn ng vi gia nh v, mnh lun ng  gia  va l quan ta va l thng dch vin. </p>\n<p>Mnh th khng gp bt c kh khn no vi nh chng c. B m chng mnh rt hin hu, thng con ht mc. Anh y v con trai ring ca mnh u yu thng mnh nn cng ha thun vi nhau. Hai ngi c th cng nhau i bi, i du lch, nu n, i xem phim hay cng trng em b\", Hng chia s.</p>\n<p>K li cu chuyn ca mnh, Hng vn cho rng cho d  l c mt hnh trnh di nhng c th gi gn li bng hai t Hnh phc, bi nh c s xp t  m n gi c mi c th an yn tn hng tri ngt ca cuc i.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">Cho rng b \"nhn u\", thanh nin m  ln gi ti bi ngi i ng... ri ln phng</div></div>', 'Chng trai Hn si tnh vt ro cn, nhiu ln tm v Vit Nam xin ci bng c m n thn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chang-trai-han-si-tinh-vuot-rao-can-nhieu-lan-tim-ve-viet-nam-xin-cuoi-bang-duoc-me-don-than', '', '', '2017-09-20 16:19:36', '2017-09-20 16:19:36', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/20/chang-trai-han-si-tinh-vuot-rao-can-nhieu-lan-tim-ve-viet-nam-xin-cuoi-bang-duoc-me-don-than/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
