INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1617', '1', '2017-09-24 08:37:00', '2017-09-24 08:37:00', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"50\">\n<p><span>Jerry Sargeant, 39 giai on khng nh anh ta t bng cn sng st trong sut n tai nn xe hi  Romania v tn mt </span><span>nhn thy hn th nn nhn t vong trong sut ma vic bay ln tri i.</span></p>\n<p><span>K t b y, </span><span>anh ta bt u tuyn truyn rng t c th sa bnh phng phiu danh thiph dng nng lc c bit c g \"Star Magic\" hay ang c gi l \"Ngi ch dn\".</span></p>\n<p>Theo li ngi n ng 39 giai on ny, anh ta c th sa c n cn s loi bnh nh au bn u, nhn quan bi, au c, u nang... <span>iu khin d man ngi sng cn st hn na l vic sa trng tr c th thc hnh  bt k ch ny. </span></p>\n<p><span>Cha dng li  nhng cn bnh bnh thng, Sargeant ang cho bit, t c th sa hin hay chy t l iu trng tr bnh ung th. Khng cn gp bnh nhn, chun y phn mm mng lin h nh Skype, anh ta khng nh cng c th sa bnh cho nhng ngi c nhu cu. </span></p>\n<p><span>Tuy nhin, vic cng th Sargeant tho b nh chc trch a phng  .</span></p>\n<p>Theo y, anh ta tho b co bt bo co bnh din l vi phm o lut Ung th (Cancer Act), nm 1939 - cm lng x danh thip dch ma iu trng tr ung th sau khi chng tham lam tham gia phin xt x chc thng 3 nm nay.</p>\n<p>Hnh pht ti a m anh ny nu i x bnh din l 3 thng t giam cm. Sau khi lnh bt gi tho c ban hnh, Sargeant bt nu phc dch ta Westminster Magistrates, Anh trong sut ngy 20/9. </p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/44834c3e00000578-4902582-image-a-601505909736993-1506187905721-1506188154263.png\" w=\"634\" h=\"472\" alt=\"Bi&#x1EBF;t ch&#x1EEF;a b&#xE1;ch b&#x1EC7;nh sau khi th&#x1EA5;y linh h&#x1ED3;n ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i ch&#x1EBF;t bay l&#xEA;n, th&#x1EA7;n y &#x111;&#x1ED1;i m&#x1EB7;t v&#x1EDB;i &#xE1;n t&#xF9; - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"Bi&#x1EBF;t ch&#x1EEF;a b&#xE1;ch b&#x1EC7;nh sau khi th&#x1EA5;y linh h&#x1ED3;n ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i ch&#x1EBF;t bay l&#xEA;n, th&#x1EA7;n y &#x111;&#x1ED1;i m&#x1EB7;t v&#x1EDB;i &#xE1;n t&#xF9; - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"a63bc940-a085-11e7-84cf-011ebaba2567\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/44834c3e00000578-4902582-image-a-601505909736993-1506187905721-1506188154263.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Jerry Sargeant.</p></div></div>\n<p>Lc cy chc nng tin hnh iu tra ra thng 6 nm ngoi v pht by gi trang web m Sargeant kinh dinh danh thip dch ma sa bnh qua cn s c cung gp dch ma sa ung th. <span>Nhiu ngi bnh trng tin, thm chy tho ti tn ch mong tm ra danh thiph sa ung th tt nht.</span></p>\n<p>Qung co trn trang web c ghi: \"<i>n phng php iu trng tr c o (th Sargeant), c cng chng minh l c hiu qu trong sut vic sa ung th</i>\" v \"<i>(c kh nng tm ra) tn gc bnh tt</i>\", ngi bnh chng cn ha trng tr m vn khi bnh nh cy bn tay th Sargeant. </p>\n<p>Cnh p tin hnh thm vn i x tng ny ra ngy 23/11 nm ngoi, anh ny khai tho khm ph ra kh nng c bit th t sau tai nn  Romania, anh t bng ng tay ln u v v sa khi cng chng au bn u. </p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/44834c4600000578-4902582-image-m-651505909773950-1506187978412.jpg\" w=\"611\" h=\"500\" alt=\"Bi&#x1EBF;t ch&#x1EEF;a b&#xE1;ch b&#x1EC7;nh sau khi th&#x1EA5;y linh h&#x1ED3;n ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i ch&#x1EBF;t bay l&#xEA;n, th&#x1EA7;n y &#x111;&#x1ED1;i m&#x1EB7;t v&#x1EDB;i &#xE1;n t&#xF9; - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" title=\"Bi&#x1EBF;t ch&#x1EEF;a b&#xE1;ch b&#x1EC7;nh sau khi th&#x1EA5;y linh h&#x1ED3;n ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i ch&#x1EBF;t bay l&#xEA;n, th&#x1EA7;n y &#x111;&#x1ED1;i m&#x1EB7;t v&#x1EDB;i &#xE1;n t&#xF9; - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"3d96b170-a085-11e7-8a08-1bdf9c92da84\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/44834c4600000578-4902582-image-m-651505909773950-1506187978412.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Mt lng x trn trang web kinh dinh dch ma sa bnh th Sargeant.</p></div></div>\n<p>Thm chy anh ny ang co dn nhng di hp c bn thn cu cn sng v khng nh chng bit t tho phm lut. \"<i>Ti chng bit chng c php k em nhng lng x nh th ln trang web</i>\". </p>\n<p>Khi c hi anh gp bnh nhn ra th chm ny, Sargeant ni: \"<i>Ti chng cn gp gia tc, mnh sa bnh qua Skype</i>\". Tr li cho cu hi bay danh thiph thc c c \"nng cy k l\" ni trn, anh p: \"<i>Ti t gia tcc</i>\". </p>\n<p>Mt chc iu trng tr ko di hc 15 pht th Sargeant c gi nh 90 bng Anh (2,7 triu ng). Gi sa bnh di hc 3 thng, c lng x l \"gii quyt trng danh thip vn  bnh tt, nng cao hiu qu cng vic, tng cng nng cy v nha cn sng\" cho ngi bnh c gi nh 1.999 bng Anh (61,6 triu ng). </p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/star-magic-healing-750x563-1506076074578-1506188044276.jpg\" w=\"620\" h=\"465\" alt=\"Bi&#x1EBF;t ch&#x1EEF;a b&#xE1;ch b&#x1EC7;nh sau khi th&#x1EA5;y linh h&#x1ED3;n ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i ch&#x1EBF;t bay l&#xEA;n, th&#x1EA7;n y &#x111;&#x1ED1;i m&#x1EB7;t v&#x1EDB;i &#xE1;n t&#xF9; - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" title=\"Bi&#x1EBF;t ch&#x1EEF;a b&#xE1;ch b&#x1EC7;nh sau khi th&#x1EA5;y linh h&#x1ED3;n ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i ch&#x1EBF;t bay l&#xEA;n, th&#x1EA7;n y &#x111;&#x1ED1;i m&#x1EB7;t v&#x1EDB;i &#xE1;n t&#xF9; - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"65299d10-a085-11e7-94d9-7f221b28d2a0\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/star-magic-healing-750x563-1506076074578-1506188044276.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Hnh pht ti a m Sargeant nu i x bnh din l 3 thng t giam cm.</p></div></div>\n<p>Cc cng chng c co bt Sargeant nh danh thip lng x v video trn Youtube by gi tho c g xung, ang g vng maximumlife.tv dn trc tip ti trang web Cha bnh Php k dn ng (Star Magic Healing) th Sargeant. </p>\n<p>Trc y, trang web ny c vit: \"S<i>au n x ri danh thip s kin i thay cuc th, bao gm trng vic ht tt hi cn s v tai nn xe hi, chuyn i trn tu v tr v hnh trnh vi ba thng qua nhng Ngi di Php k lu i, Jerry Sargeant tho pht by gi ra \'</i><span><i>Php k dn ng</i></span><i>\'\"</i><span>.</span></p>\n<p>Thi bung tuyn n i x cng Sargeant tham gia nh l ra ngy 20/9, m sau y tho c chuyn xung ngy 8/11. </p>\n<div type=\"link\">Nghi con b ma m, b bm tr n dn ctrng con gi 15 thng giai on</div>\n<p>\n<br/></p></div>', 'Bit sa bch bnh sau khi ch hn ngi tt ngh bay ln, \"thn y\" i x phng din cng n t', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'biet-chua-bach-benh-sau-khi-thay-linh-hon-nguoi-chet-bay-len-than-y-doi-mat-voi-an-tu', '', '', '2017-09-24 08:37:00', '2017-09-24 08:37:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/24/biet-chua-bach-benh-sau-khi-thay-linh-hon-nguoi-chet-bay-len-than-y-doi-mat-voi-an-tu/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
