INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1619', '1', '2017-09-24 08:35:09', '2017-09-24 08:35:09', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"111\">\n<p><span><b>V sao nu nh vn dng ch chng n ung thng bng lin t b khi ng tr?</b></span></p>\n<p><span>Theo nghin cu lm sng cho ch, ngi sau chng giai on 40, c th l t b 46-55 giai on chnh l th on \"thp k m ly\", lc khe st gim chng vnh, cng bui c th bng chia pht lm cn bnh him, a mng trong sut mng y l bnh mn tnh, c th ko trng gia tcc ti ht i ngi.</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>Nu c mngng chng c nhng i thay theo b bn hng hi, lc khe s b e da. Khi thn cn trn trn i xung, c ng suy thoi, s bn bc chng v h min nhim u suy gim chc nng, bnh tt t b y ny chng hn rt lm so cng ngh suy ch quan hng bn. </p>\n<p>Nam gii sau giai on 40, c mngng v  vic cng lm lc p ngy n tng, rt d t cc bnh bay ct, tm bia, mp mp , bao t v phi. </p>\n<p>Ph n sau giai on 40 chnh l th on c nguy c cao chia pht khi cc bnh ung th, c bit l nu nh t  d bung ung th bung trng, t cung v ung th v. </p>\n<p>V vy, i x cng nhng ngi bc ra 40 giai on tang i, ngoi vic nu nh t  tng cng on luyn th chng, chm nom lc khe nh thc, th ng nu nh t  iu chnh ch chng n ung ph hp l, khoa gia tcc.</p>\n<p>Trong bi bc vit lch no, cc chuyn gia lc khe v dinh dng s gii thiu bay nhng nguyn tc n ung dnh cho la lung giai on, gip cc bn c th tham kho kp th, i thay nhng np xu trc y, bo m s duy tr t th n nh trong sut th on mn cm nht hng th c. </p>\n<p><b>Cng thc \"4 t\" ng ghi nh </b></p>\n<p><b><i>1. n t nng cy </i></b></p>\n<p>Tui cng tng cao l bao th cc chc nng trn thn cng gim xung by nhiu. Vi s gia tng giai on tc, t chc hng thn s xut hin s suy gim  chng chng khc rau, vic tiu th calo s gim, cng gim s tiu ha v hp th protein. </p>\n<p>Do y, bn c giai on ri th hy n t tht phm lm calorie, thay ra y l n thm n t nhtu tri b v trng, t bo m  chng m v vitamin thng nht. </p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506295503586-1506296619964.jpg\" w=\"800\" h=\"533\" alt=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"2c3e72c0-a182-11e7-aaaa-51ac0faef9da\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506295503586-1506296619964.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Tui cao hn th cn n gim nng cy i</p></div></div>\n<p><b><i>2. n t mui </i></b></p>\n<p>i cng nhng ngi sau giai on 40, rt d lm ra hin tng thch n mn, c khuynh bn thm lm mui hn khi un nu, hay thm cc gia v mn m hn so cng khi ng tr. </p>\n<p>Thi quen no nu nh duy tr trong sut th k trng gia tcc s dn ti ny cc bnh him nh p huyt cao, chngt gc v bnh tim mch. </p>\n<p><b><i>3. n t du m</i></b></p>\n<p>Nu n n cy chng mp mp qu lm cng l duyn c hoi ra bnh tim mch, hoi nh hng nghim trng ti lc mnh hng ngi cao giai on. </p>\n<p>Khi dung np n cy cholesterol qu lm ra thn, d dn ti vic ny cc bnh nh x rn v tc nghn huyt mch, t b y c th c nguy c hoi ra n x ri cc bnh h trng, in nh nht l nhi mu c tim v bnh mch banh. </p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/thumb_w/660/2017/photo-1-1506295642961.jpg\" w=\"720\" h=\"450\" alt=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" title=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"e63549e0-a17f-11e7-81d9-d137edec0f5b\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506295642961.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p><span><b><i>4. n t li</i></b></span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>Sau giai on lung giai on, d c l ngi ho ngt ngo th bn cng nu nh hn ch cy li em ra thn. Ngi n qu ngt ngo c th hoi ra ri lon chc nng ty. Khi cy li d, chng ch d dn ti mp mp , m ng cng tng gng gnh nh ln tuyn ty, chng vnh hoi ra bnh tiu li. </p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506295716757.jpg\" w=\"640\" h=\"400\" alt=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" title=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"11add420-a180-11e7-8e2d-d3f798772c52\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506295716757.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p><b>Cng thc \"4 lm\" chng cho nn b qua</b></p>\n<p><b><i>1. n lm chng x </i></b></p>\n<p>Sau 40 giai on, kh nng hot chngng hng h tiu ha s gim, nhu chngng rut yu dn s d hoi bnh to bn. Trong chng giai on no, cho nn b sung thm chng x trong sut t bng ba n hng ngy. </p>\n<p>Khi cy cellulose c cung gp m no cho thn, chng ch c th bung lnh to bn, cn  phng cc bnh bay li tiu ha, m ng gip bung lnh bnh cao p huyt, x rn chngng mch v tiu li. </p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/thumb_w/660/2017/photo-1-1506295943529.jpg\" w=\"1000\" h=\"643\" alt=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 4.\" title=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 4.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"9907a3b0-a180-11e7-a065-7937920d296b\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506295943529.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p><b><i>2. n lm Canxi </i></b></p>\n<p>Do c im hng ngi cao giai on, gia tc rt d b thiu canxi dn ti long xng. Do y, trong sut menu hng ngy cho nn b sung thm sa, to bp, , cc tht phm ng canxi...</p>\n<p>Nhng mn n no l c tc dng cn  phng long xng, cng th c th chng thiu mu, bo m cho khung xng t khe, cng mun qu trnh lo ha.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/thumb_w/660/2017/photo-1-1506296020536.jpg\" w=\"2232\" h=\"1400\" alt=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 5.\" title=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 5.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"c781d530-a180-11e7-a047-73f8081241a6\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506296020536.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p><b><i>3. n lm I- t hn</i></b></p>\n<p>Bc ra giai on lung giai on, nu nh thiu it trong sut thn d dn ti bnh bay tuyn p, chnh yu l bnh suy gim chc nng hot chngng tuyn p v cc b phn h trng, t b y cng gim s bn bc chng, nh hng ti s chia hy chng mp mp, dn ti mp mp . </p>\n<p>I-t chng cn qu lm, m bn nu nh t  ti n, v nu nh qu thiu th li hoi him cho lc khe. Ngoi cy i t c cho ra trong sut mui, cc tht phm ng lm cy t t thin nhin nh rong bin ln, c bin ln, t v bin ln, cua gh, khoai ty, trng, rau ci chn vt...</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/thumb_w/660/2017/photo-1-1506296415332.jpg\" w=\"675\" h=\"475\" alt=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 6.\" title=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 6.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"b23aa390-a181-11e7-a065-7937920d296b\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506296415332.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p><span><b><i>4. Ung lm nc</i></b></span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>Khi bc qua giai on 40, cm gic kht nc s b suy gim, cho nn lm ngi s t khi ch tui kht nc. iu no v tnh khin cho bn lm ra cnh \"qun\" ung nc m thn cng chng \"nhc\" bn ung. </p>\n<p>Cch tt nht l hy ln lch ung nc n nhp t bn chng b thiu nc. Ti thiu mi mt 2 gi/ln bn cho nn b sung nc. Khi thiu nc, thn s \"kh ho\" dn dn, t th s st gim, da xu v cc c quan ni tng d gp ri ro. </p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/thumb_w/660/2017/photo-1-1506296467592.jpg\" w=\"759\" h=\"422\" alt=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 7.\" title=\"Mu&#x1ED1;n gi&#x1EEF; s&#x1EE9;c kh&#x1ECF;e b&#x1EB1;ng c&#xE1;ch &#x103;n u&#x1ED1;ng, th&#xEC; ph&#x1EA3;i tu&#xE2;n th&#x1EE7; c&#xF4;ng th&#x1EE9;c 4 &#xED;t, 4 nhi&#x1EC1;u - &#x1EA2;nh 7.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"d12cb270-a181-11e7-9564-854b3c797542\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506296467592.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p><i>*Theo Kknews</i></p>\n<div type=\"link\">Mun ln da khe xinh xo trng sng: ng b qua 4 b quyt chm nom t b bn trong sut hng ng y</div></div>', 'Mun gi sc khe k cch n ung, th phi tun cng thc \"4 t, 4 nhiu\"', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'muon-giu-suc-khoe-bang-cach-an-uong-thi-phai-tuan-thu-cong-thuc-4-it-4-nhieu', '', '', '2017-09-24 08:35:09', '2017-09-24 08:35:09', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/24/muon-giu-suc-khoe-bang-cach-an-uong-thi-phai-tuan-thu-cong-thuc-4-it-4-nhieu/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
