INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1623', '1', '2017-09-24 08:30:00', '2017-09-24 08:30:00', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"13\">\n<p>Cuc tin cng mc cc tay sng khng b Hay\'at Tahrir Al-Sham v dm ng Hi gio Turkistan c c nhng kt qu ban s trn khu vc gip gii hai thc gic bn bc Hama, tn tranh c vi ba trm kim sot thuc L on 47 S on c gii mng 11.</p>\n<p>Nhng lin sau y, cc qun s thuc Lc cy Tiger kp thi tip cn chin trn, t chc n mi t tin cng y li cc tay sng HTS - Al-Qaeda Syria v chim li nhng trm kim sot b khng b cng tranh.</p>\n<p>Cuc tin cng chng v quyt lit no em li thng li to, hn 80 tay sng b tiu dit, trong sut y c th lnh ch huy dm Hay\'at Tahrir Al-Sham Aleppo. Truyn am hiu lc cy Tiger ng video, ghi li kt qu trn cng khc lit no.</p>\n<p>Sau cc tin cng tht bi mc Hayat Tahrir Al-Sham v cc dm chin binh khc trn a phn Idlib - Hama, qun i Syria bt u cng c chin tuyn, tp hp qun s chun b cho n chin nhnh tin cng mi trn x bc Hama.</p>\n<p>Chin nhnh no nhm ra cc a bn c th mc t chc khng b  Idlib t tiu dit hon ton dm Hayat Tahrir Al-Sham.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">9 v kh M c th xoi thng boong-ke su nht mc Triu Tin</div></div>', 'H Syria chp nhong tiu dit hn 80 tay sng phin qun  Hama', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ho-syria-chop-nhoang-diet-hon-80-tay-sung-phien-quan-o-hama', '', '', '2017-09-24 08:30:00', '2017-09-24 08:30:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/24/ho-syria-chop-nhoang-diet-hon-80-tay-sung-phien-quan-o-hama/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1624', '1', '2017-09-24 08:30:00', '2017-09-24 08:30:00', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"34\">\n<p><span> th chm </span><strong sut>Dybala</strong sut><span> ta sng, bo Anh bt thn a tin M.U mun mua ngi sao ngi Argentina ng gi nh 175 triu euro. Liu Dybala c xng ng ng mng tin  s no l?</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p><strong sut>Dybala cn vit lch li lch s</strong sut></p>\n<p>Ma trc, <strong sut>Dybala</strong sut> ch ghi tng cng 11 bn  Serie A. Ma no l, khi Serie A mi din ra c 6 vng tip kin, chn  ngi Argentina h c 10 bn, ngha l ch bi trng v trc ng n bn na.</p>\n<p>Dybala ghi n bn trong sut thng li trc Cagliari (3-0)  ngy ra qun. Tip y, anh lp hat-trick trc ht th v p gii trc Genoa (4-0), ghi thm n bn  thng li trc Chievo (4-0) trc khi c thm n hat-trick na trc Sassuolo (3-1). Mi nht, trc Torino, Dybala c thm n c lu ban gip Juve thng 4-0 trong sut trn derby ng  th.</p>\n<p>Sut 59 nm qua, chng c n tin tn gio no l ghi c 10 bn trong sut 6 trn trc ht th v banh. Tnh t qung qut v 1958-59 n nay, hai chn  v i nht l Gabriel Batistuta v Di Natale cng ch c 8 bn trong sut 6 vng u, ngha l bi Dybala ngy nay 2 bn. Quay ngc th k, Serie A ch c Antonio Valentin Angelillo (huyn thoi th Inter) t qung qutng cng tt hn <strong sut>Dybala</strong sut>. ng c 11 bn thng ch sau 4 vng tip kin th v 1958-59 v chm dt v p gii ng 33 bn sau 33 trn (lng nhng 1 bn/trn).</p>\n<p><strong sut>Dybala by gi hn c gi nh 175 triu?</strong sut></p>\n<p>Cng ngy Dybala lp c lu ban ra li Torino, t The Mirror phn pht i n thng bo hoi mngc: M.U mun hi mua Dybala ng gi nh 155 triu bng (175 triu euro). Do chng c iu khon ph v hip ng v vy Dybala hon ton c th t quyt toan mai sau. The Mirror khng toan Ph Ch ngoo Ed Woodward th M.U c mai quan h rt tt ng Tng gi nhm c Beppe Marotta th Juve.</p>\n<p>Liu <strong sut>Dybala</strong sut> c xng ng ng ci gi nh 175 triu euro? Juve mua Dybala bay t qung qut Palermo bui nm 2015, khi y h xut hin nhng him nghi bay mng tin 40 triu euro m Juve qung qut ra. Nm ngonh, Dybala mi t li du n tht th ln Juve, khi anh lp c lu ban n tng trong sut thng li 3-0 trc Barca  d i T kt Champions League. Nhng vic hoi tht vng  trn chung kt ng Real Madrid (Juve bi 1-4), khin ngi ta li t giu nghi bay kh hay tht th chn  23 giai on.</p>\n<p>Juventus vn t nim tin ra Dybala khi giao cho anh chic o mng 10, nguyn c coi l n mng o huyn thoi  nhm banh vch Turin. p sc to m Dybala chng b nh gc, m cng rc sng. Con mng 10 bn trong sut 6 trn Serie A u v h ni ln iu y. Dybala v no l h nhi b ra trung bi l giu hn thay v ch bm bin nu. Vi s h tr ti a t qung qut danh thip tin r bn sau, anh c iu kin t phn pht trin tt nht danh thip k hay.  s l chm da t Dybala hon thin v hn c n v bng n th Juve.</p>\n<p>Barca h hi mua <strong sut>Dybala</strong sut> ng gi nh 110 triu euro trong sut v H. By by gi, M.U sn sng chi n 175 triu euro. Trong bi trngnh gi nh cu th ti cn c p ln cao n danh thiph chng mt, ch cn Dybala tip kin ta sng, gi nh th anh c k vng s hiu gn con mng 222 triu euro (gi nh th Neymar) lin trong sut v H n.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">i bi Timor Leste 11 bn nhn nim vui to sau 49 d lng li  p gii l </div></div>', 'Dybala c thc th ng gi cng li yu cu 175 triu euro t b M.U?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'dybala-co-thuc-su-dang-gia-voi-loi-de-nghi-175-trieu-euro-tu-m-u', '', '', '2017-09-24 08:30:00', '2017-09-24 08:30:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/24/dybala-co-thuc-su-dang-gia-voi-loi-de-nghi-175-trieu-euro-tu-m-u/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1625', '1', '2017-09-24 08:27:27', '2017-09-24 08:27:27', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"60\">\n<p><span>Ngy mai (25-9), TAND thc gic Bnh Thun cho bit s tin hnh xt x i x vi b co Trn Thanh Tm (27 giai on, hm x  Tn, huyn  Huoai, Lm ng) bay khuyt chm Dm  vi tr em. y l n trong sut nhng ma n hoi chn chngng d lun v vic m thai nhi ra chngng ng danh thip thy thuc ti bnh vin lm cho chng thm toan c ADN?</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p><span>Theo ni dung ma n, Trn Thanh Tm quen bit vi b T. (SN 13-12-2000) v c quan h i tnh htm yu ng. </span></p>\n<p><span>Vo ngy 8-10-2016, khi cha m b T. bay Bnh nh t chu tang, trong sut bui b T. cn  nh vi a em gi V. (13 giai on) th Tm ti nh nhi v  li.</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>Trong m bc, khi b V. ng say, Tm ti nm ra T. v thc hnh hnh vi giao hp vi em. Cha tha mn cn th tnh, sau khi T. b i xung bp nc t nu nc, Tm thng xuyn tip cn b V., t khp ngi ng em gi i tnh nhn.</p>\n<p>D b V. h ra cng c, ht to t cu cu ch T. m Tm vn khng khng chng tha cho em. n khi ch b V. c du hiu nn ma i, bt tnh bt tnh th Tm mi tra cu ra t cho b T. xoa bp d gi.</p>\n<p>Sau y, hai b tin em s vic tng thut cho n ngi c th trong sut xm nghe t cy i in bo cho cha m  qu bit. Nhn c tin bo ng hai con, ng Q. (b 2 b) ngay thc th trnh bo ti cng an.</p>\n<p>Ti c quan iu tra, ht Tm v T. tha nhn quen rau qua Facebook v c quan h i tnh htm yu ng. </p>\n<p>C hai cng cho bit, h quan h i tnh dc vi rau trong sut m 8-10, trc y, ht hai cng giu d quan h ti danh thip nh hn  Phan Thit v Bo Lc.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506299813835.jpg\" w=\"620\" h=\"465\" alt=\"X&#xE9;t x&#x1EED; v&#x1EE5; b&#x1EA1;n trai l&#xE0;m ch&#x1ECB; g&#xE1;i c&#xF3; b&#x1EA7;u, d&#xE2;m &#xF4; em g&#xE1;i 13 tu&#x1ED5;i, ch&#x1EE9;ng c&#x1EE9; c&#xF3; nguy c&#x1A1; b&#x1ECB; m&#x1EA5;t do b&#xE0;o thai b&#x1ECB; ng&#xE2;m trong sut c&#x1ED3;n - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"X&#xE9;t x&#x1EED; v&#x1EE5; b&#x1EA1;n trai l&#xE0;m ch&#x1ECB; g&#xE1;i c&#xF3; b&#x1EA7;u, d&#xE2;m &#xF4; em g&#xE1;i 13 tu&#x1ED5;i, ch&#x1EE9;ng c&#x1EE9; c&#xF3; nguy c&#x1A1; b&#x1ECB; m&#x1EA5;t do b&#xE0;o thai b&#x1ECB; ng&#xE2;m trong sut c&#x1ED3;n - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"a2116550-a189-11e7-a047-73f8081241a6\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506299813835.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"2\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Cn nh bc li, phung ph s chn 2 ch em T. b Tm xm hi trong sut m.</p></div></div>\n<p>Thy T. c nhng du hiu tht thng, b nn ma i, nc da lt lt, v cht ng Q. h dn em i khm xt v pht hin em h c thai 6 tun giai on. </p>\n<p>Tuy nhin, bc 31-12-2016, T. ln cn au bng v c em ti BV II Lm ng r v em h b rm thai. Ti y, thy thuc h tin hnh thu gi bo thai t bn giao cho c quan CST Cng an huyn Hm Thun Bc t thm toan ADN. </p>\n<p>Nhng do thiu kinh nghim thnh ra danh thip thy thuc  BV h m bo thai ra dung dch chngng thnh ra chng th thm toan c ADN ng thai nhi?</p>\n<p>Ngy 10-2-2017, CST Cng an huyn Hm Thun Bc ra thng tin chng khi t ma n hnh s v cho rng giy khai sinh ng T. l ngy 13-12-2000 m ngy i khai sinh li l 19-3-2001 chm th hn khai sinh thnh ra quyt toan by cu thm toan chng giai on.</p>\n<p>\"Ti th chm thm toan, chng giai on ng T. t b 15 giai on 9 thng ti 16 giai on 3 thng\". T kt qu n, CQT tnh ngy m d giao hp dn ti c thai, T. h 16 giai on 7 ngy. Do y hnh vi ng Tm chng bu thnh h giao hp vi tr em. </p>\n<p>ng th, c quan cng an li che nhn li khai ng ht T. v Tm bay nhng d quan h i tnh dc trc y v chng c c s.</p>\n<p>Vi hnh vi dm  vi b V., theo CQT \"Tm h tha nhn m l li khai ng danh thip i x tng, chng c bng chng n khc t chng minh (theo kt qu thm toan min sinh dc b V. chng c du tch thng tn) thnh ra cng chng  c s t chng minh Tm c hnh vi dm  vi V.\".</p>\n<p>Bc xc trc quyt toan chng khi t ma n ng c quan iu tra, ng Q. u gi ti ti danh thip gp chnh quyn t cy s gip nng.</p>\n<p>Sau khi coi xt li ma n, ngy 3-8-2017, c quan CST Cng an huyn Hm Thun Bc h hon thnh kt lun iu tra, di h s qua Vin KSND vi gp, yu cu truy t b can Trn Thanh Tm (27 giai on, hm x  Tn, huyn  Huoai, Lm ng) khuyt chm dm  vi tr em c quy toan ti iu 116 BLHS.</p>\n<p>Gn 2 thng khi t b can, sng mai ma n s c tin em ra xt x cng khai ti TAND thc gic Bnh Thun.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">Nguyn cn b thanh tra rao na  pa thi cng chc</div></div>', 'Xt x ma bn nam cng ch gi c bu, dm  em gi 13 giai on, bng chng c nguy c b cht do bo thai b m trong sut ru cn', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'xet-xu-vu-ban-trai-lam-chi-gai-co-bau-dam-o-em-gai-13-tuoi-chung-cu-co-nguy-co-bi-mat-do-bao-thai-bi-ngam-trong-con', '', '', '2017-09-24 08:27:27', '2017-09-24 08:27:27', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/24/xet-xu-vu-ban-trai-lam-chi-gai-co-bau-dam-o-em-gai-13-tuoi-chung-cu-co-nguy-co-bi-mat-do-bao-thai-bi-ngam-trong-con/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
