INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1629', '1', '2017-09-24 08:17:00', '2017-09-24 08:17:00', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"16\">\n<p> l kt qu d hi sau b thm  c ngy 24/9.</p>\n<p>Theo BBC, tuy vn thng li v l b kho nht trong sut Quc gia tcp m b h lu CDU/CSU mc b Merkel tho nhn kt qu bc nht trong sut 70 nm qua. Khong 32,5% tng mng phiu thu bay chng nu l n bt thn v con mng no tng i thp so cng danh thip d on tm 36-37% trc bu c.</p>\n<p>T lu no c ngha l CDU-CSU s chim c chng 219 dt ti Quc gia tcp, t hn 30 dt so cng trc. N cng c ngha l vic vch lp lin minh cm quyn mi s cng tr vch phc tp.</p>\n<p>Tri ngc cng CDU-CSU, b ba hu \"Con ng khc cho nc c\" (AfD) tho c lc vn lch s khi chim chng 13,5% mng phiu, ngha l s cm chng 87 dt trong sut Quc gia tcp mi. y l d trc ht Quc gia tcp c chng kin s tr li mc n b ba hu em t tng pht xt k t sau Th chin 2.</p>\n<p>AfD thng to hn danh thip d on chng t x gia tcp c cn c s chia r kho m bay danh thip ch  bay sc tc, o. N cng cho ch s bin ng kho m trn chnh di c.</p>\n<p>Cuc bu c lin bang  c c t chc 4 nm n d. Khong 61,5 triu ngi trn 18 giai on  iu kin d b thm. C hai cc b thm bit lp, n cc c tri la ra n ng vin trong sut ht bu c mc tao, v n cc khc b thm cho b chnh tr m gia tc a thch.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">\"Ma thu\" ca 72 mc Lin Hp Quc sng gi hn v s xut hin mc ng Trump</div><article readability=\"0\"><p/>\n<p>\n<br/></p></article></div>', 'N Th tng t c Merkel ti c nhim k ca 4', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'nu-thu-tuong-duc-merkel-tai-cu-nhiem-ky-thu-4', '', '', '2017-09-24 08:17:00', '2017-09-24 08:17:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/24/nu-thu-tuong-duc-merkel-tai-cu-nhiem-ky-thu-4/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1630', '1', '2017-09-24 08:15:13', '2017-09-24 08:15:13', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"112\">\n<p><b>Ngi cha git vn trn qu tim khn gi</b></p>\n<p>Cu chuyn ng hai ba con din vin Quc Tun git vn trn qu tim t, v kin c l qu tim rt giu c gi khc, trong sut nhng ngy cht tun qua. </p>\n<p>T mt ca bnh d gi l hn hu trong sut y gia tcc - cn bnh ch xy ra  tr lt lng vi t l 1/88.000 - m cchcg qu hn hu ngoi th h gi d coi y l mt ca lt lng d tt, kp cha - con y h to do vy mt cu chuyn c tch duy nht trn th h. </p>\n<p>H h dt tay rau qua c chc d s phnng cc, qua 15 nm ng ng cht n au, hy vng, tht vng, an i rau, ta nng ra rau. Cu chuyn c tch s cchcg vch, gi d cchcg c nim tin mnh lit ng Quc Tun, mt ngi cha.</p>\n<p>ng vy, vi i i tnh ng mt ngi cha, Quc Tun h lm do vy php thut mu cho th cuc ng con trai anh.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506268503428.png\" w=\"660\" h=\"409\" alt=\"TIN T&#x1ED0;T L&#xC0;NH 25/9: Ph&#xE9;p m&#xE0;u thi&#xEA;ng li&#xEA;ng c&#x1EE7;a ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i cha, 675 gi&#x1EA5;y ph&#xE9;p con v&#xE0; tu&#x1EA7;n m&#x1EDB;i &#x111;&#x1EA7;y c&#x1EA3;m h&#x1EE9;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"TIN T&#x1ED0;T L&#xC0;NH 25/9: Ph&#xE9;p m&#xE0;u thi&#xEA;ng li&#xEA;ng c&#x1EE7;a ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i cha, 675 gi&#x1EA5;y ph&#xE9;p con v&#xE0; tu&#x1EA7;n m&#x1EDB;i &#x111;&#x1EA7;y c&#x1EA3;m h&#x1EE9;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"b851ffd0-a140-11e7-aeea-a394e698d7aa\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506268503428.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p><span>D thnh thong vn nghe ti nhng ma \"c mu\" nh p con ch v vi ba ngn ti thing, hay cn bng qung qut ri con mi sinh cho nhng bn tay xa l, m trn th h ta vn n gp giu hn nhng ngi cha, ngi bm vi i i tnh v b dnh cho con.</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>L nhng ngi bm em vn trng r bnh sn sng rt ngn th k s phnng t oi ng t t con c th c cho th h, nhng ngi cha giu nm rng r bn ba khp ch tm a con tht lc, ngi bm cc c nh ca sau cn bo m quyt cchcg t con nu hn gia tcc. C giu ngi nh th, bui no cng c th ch c.</p>\n<p>Cng trong sut ngy cht tun, ti phin to x ba n OceanBank, cc trng s h h bi l mt cu chuyn khc: B vin Phm Hong Giang c con b sinh ra vi bnh tim bm sinh v giu d nu m mt, m kp mt ng chu vn yu i. 8 giai on, chu ng trc nguy c m lo.</p>\n<p>B vin Phm Hong Giang ging gii: L mt ngi cha, nu ton bng ton  lo cho con, do vy b nh gi l cchcg cng tc tt vi c quan liu iu tra.</p>\n<p>ng Giang xin to cchcg cch ly t khi x hi, do ng lo gi d b t, th con ng c th cchcg c th c no nhn ch cha na. Anh Quc Tun, gi d c bit chuyn ng ng Giang, t cng hon ton thu o hiu, v gia tc u l nhng ngi cha.</p>\n<p>Vic xt x ng to n s nu cn c ra lut, m lan truyn thng dn tc ta l cchcg bao gi v ch vit l m cchcg xt ti ci i tnh.</p>\n<p>Tnh cm cha con l mt iu thing, trn thut c n c xut by gi  ch mt ngi phm khuyt im. Hy tin v vui v iu y, do n khi gi  mi mt chng ta nhng iu tt lnh hn so vi vic cn c nu nghi y l mt chiu bay khuyt im. </p>\n<p><span><b>Cm hng th t qung qut B Cng Thng</b></span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>\"Con s phn ln c cha t qung qutng c trong sut lch s ngnh Cng Thng\" l mt s kinh ngc th v khin c Th tng mo cng t s khen ngi. 675 \"giy php thut con\" c xo qung qut trong sut ch mt th k ngn.</p>\n<p> 675 iu kin kinh dinh h t qung qutng khin l bao doanh nghip \"ln l b toi\", ni nh B c Ch nhim Vn bung Chnh che Mai Tin Dng: \"Nu cchcg tho d g th doanh nghip rt kh khn.</p>\n<p>Ngi ng u ngnh Cng Thng cng cho bit, c quan liu no s u tin hnh ti c bu, tinh gim c my, vi th tng cng hiu qu qun l Nh nc, bn ra kinh t th trng. </p>\n<p>B cng s \"ngi li\" vi mt s phn c ngnh t tm ting ni chung, lnh s cht cho trong sut r chuyn ngnh vi doanh nghip. (c tin chnh)</p>\n<p>Ngoi ra, vic B Cng Thng, trc u l B c, h ch o x l 12 d n bi l l, bi hiu qu ko di, cng c nh gi cao. C quan liu no h vch lp bng cng tc t t vn, em ra gii php x l t qung qutng d n.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506268916096.jpg\" w=\"660\" h=\"409\" alt=\"TIN T&#x1ED0;T L&#xC0;NH 25/9: Ph&#xE9;p m&#xE0;u thi&#xEA;ng li&#xEA;ng c&#x1EE7;a ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i cha, 675 gi&#x1EA5;y ph&#xE9;p con v&#xE0; tu&#x1EA7;n m&#x1EDB;i &#x111;&#x1EA7;y c&#x1EA3;m h&#x1EE9;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" title=\"TIN T&#x1ED0;T L&#xC0;NH 25/9: Ph&#xE9;p m&#xE0;u thi&#xEA;ng li&#xEA;ng c&#x1EE7;a ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i cha, 675 gi&#x1EA5;y ph&#xE9;p con v&#xE0; tu&#x1EA7;n m&#x1EDB;i &#x111;&#x1EA7;y c&#x1EA3;m h&#x1EE9;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"ae7b93d0-a141-11e7-a89b-d53b14af2463\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506268916096.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Nh my sinh sn phn bn DAP 2 Lo Cai l 1 trong sut 3 d n yu bi b que tra. nh: Infonet</p></div></div>\n<p><span/><span>Ni t tm, lin sau vic bc qung qut iu kin kinh dinh th B c B Cng Thng h khn trng ban hnh cc quyt nh que tra ti 3 d n l: Nh my sinh sn phn bn DAP 2 Lo Cai; Nh my Bt giy Phng Nam; D n Nh my yng tu Dung Qut. ( </span>c tin chnh<span>)</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>Cm hng th t qung qut B Cng Thng liu chng c lan truyn c ti cc c ban ngnh khc t mi mt sng ca Hai, ca T, ca Su, Tin Tt Lnh ng chng t c vinh danh gia tc cchcg?</p>\n<p><b>Khng ngh hu n v m phn gim chi ph</b></p>\n<p>Li thm 2 Tin tt lnh lan truyn cm hng th cho c gi u tun!</p>\n<p>u tin l vic Vin Kim st nhn dn cp cao TP HCM h k khng ngh hu qung qut bn n s thm m To n Nhn nn TP HCM l tuyn vi ma n Cng ty VN Pharma v c du hiu b lt ngi, lt khuyt im.</p>\n<p> y l ma n hoi xn xang d lun do sau khi ta tuyn n, d lun cchcg vi i tnh vi khuyt im danh v ca n m ta n h tuyn v cho rng x cchcg ng vi khuyt im danh ng cc b vin. </p>\n<p>Bn ven y, cc chuyn gia lut v d lun ng cho rng nu x l bn phn ng lnh o Cc Qun l Dc thuc B Y t. (c tin chnh)</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506269028214.png\" w=\"540\" h=\"361\" alt=\"TIN T&#x1ED0;T L&#xC0;NH 25/9: Ph&#xE9;p m&#xE0;u thi&#xEA;ng li&#xEA;ng c&#x1EE7;a ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i cha, 675 gi&#x1EA5;y ph&#xE9;p con v&#xE0; tu&#x1EA7;n m&#x1EDB;i &#x111;&#x1EA7;y c&#x1EA3;m h&#x1EE9;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" title=\"TIN T&#x1ED0;T L&#xC0;NH 25/9: Ph&#xE9;p m&#xE0;u thi&#xEA;ng li&#xEA;ng c&#x1EE7;a ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i cha, 675 gi&#x1EA5;y ph&#xE9;p con v&#xE0; tu&#x1EA7;n m&#x1EDB;i &#x111;&#x1EA7;y c&#x1EA3;m h&#x1EE9;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"f11152c0-a141-11e7-80e3-897aa0f332fe\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506269028214.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">B vin Nguyn Minh Hng (nguyn Ch ngoo HQT kim Tng gim c Cng ty CP VN Pharma)</p></div></div>\n<p><span>Tip theo l mt Tin tt lnh h vn trng r ti cu chuyn bay BOT h tn giy ca ti nguyn s phn sut th k qua.</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>ng Nguyn Vn Huyn - Tng cc cn Trng Tng cc cn ng c cho bit, Tng cc cn by gi cn y mnh cng tc r r li 54 d n BOT do B GTVT qun l trn c nc v tin hnh thng tho vi cc ch u t t iu chnh phng n ti chnh theo bn gim chi ph cho ngi dn trong sut min nh hng ng trm thu chi ph cng nh gim chi ph chung cho cc dng c. </p>\n<p>D kin vic thng tho v r r s hon vch trong sut thng 10 t Tng cc cn gi vn bn  xut ln B GTVT coi xt chun y. Nu c chun y, cc trm s tin hnh gim chi ph trong sut thng 11. </p>\n<p>Trc mt, d n BOT Php Vn - Cu Gi h hon vch cng tc thng tho vi Tng cc cn ng c bay phng n gim chi ph t qung qut 22-25% cho t cc nhm dng c v  xut ln B GTVT t quyt nh trong sut ngy 22.9. (c tin chnh)</p>\n<p><b>Thc mt xc cm cho u tun mi</b></p>\n<p>La cgia tcn xc cm hng hi m bn mun c chng cho tun mi ng bn t qung qut menu tin tt lnh ng chng t!</p>\n<p>CHP NH T SNG- KHEN MNH P TRAI RI CP LUN IN THOI (c tin chnh)</p>\n<p>o Vn Long, 29 giai on, tr qun Thanh Xun ra mt ca hng in thoi hi mua chic iPhone 6S Plus c gi chp nh t khoi khen ngi t p trai ri ba chn ban cng qung qut bay. </p>\n<p>C nh v anh chng qu p trai thc do vy clip c camera gim st ng ca hng ghi li h lan lan truyn trn s phn x hi mt cch chng mt. 2 hm sau, cchcg chu ni p lc ng d lun, Long ti cng an th khuyt im.</p>\n<p>MT ANH CHNG   CHO V TRN TAXI <span>(</span>c tin chnh<span>)</span></p>\n<p>Anh Hong nh Thng, cht ng sn ph Nguyn Ngc Ly  Ngh An h tang vch \"ng \" vi bt c d cho chnh v ng t trn taxi. </p>\n<p>B gi 3,2kg chc s c mt th cuc th v mai no khi trn thut li chuyn t h c ba   trn taxi. Mt s c hy hu may mn l tt lnh!</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\" data-style=\"align-right\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506269200525.png\" w=\"500\" h=\"453\" alt=\"TIN T&#x1ED0;T L&#xC0;NH 25/9: Ph&#xE9;p m&#xE0;u thi&#xEA;ng li&#xEA;ng c&#x1EE7;a ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i cha, 675 gi&#x1EA5;y ph&#xE9;p con v&#xE0; tu&#x1EA7;n m&#x1EDB;i &#x111;&#x1EA7;y c&#x1EA3;m h&#x1EE9;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 4.\" title=\"TIN T&#x1ED0;T L&#xC0;NH 25/9: Ph&#xE9;p m&#xE0;u thi&#xEA;ng li&#xEA;ng c&#x1EE7;a ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i cha, 675 gi&#x1EA5;y ph&#xE9;p con v&#xE0; tu&#x1EA7;n m&#x1EDB;i &#x111;&#x1EA7;y c&#x1EA3;m h&#x1EE9;ng - &#x1EA2;nh 4.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"57d28f60-a142-11e7-ad77-9f411bebcc1b\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506269200525.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"0\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\"/></div></div>\n<p><span>3 CP I KHIN TRI TIM BN RUNG NG</span>\n<br/></p>\n<p>K nim 1 nm ngy thng rau ty vic chun b li k nim y trong sut bn nm. Cp cp d thng Quang Thnh- Vn Anh no khin t (v giu ngi na, t tin th) s nh ti da dit th giai on xanh. </p>\n<p>Khi m i i tnh u th h trong sut veo ti th, chng ta m t qung qutng ngy thng rau ty nhng li k nim 1 thng- 3 thng- 1 nm </p>\n<p>Ai cng t qung qutng c mt th nh th! Ti ch nhng ng nh ng hnh phc trong sut mt c b Vn Anh, nh mt ng ngi cn thng lan to hnh phc ti lin min (c tin chnh)</p>\n<p>Mt kp cp khc th dnh ti c mt nm tri t t chun b cho mng cu hn sau 10 nm thng rau. Hong Duy- H My sinh vi ngy, vi thng, vi nm. </p>\n<p>Hong Duy ni: H My h dnh vn trn giai on que xun ng c y cho t, cho mi i tnh no do vy t cm ch cn nu c bn phn t to do vy mt k nim ng nh nht cho c y. (c tin chnh)</p>\n<p>V mt kp cp na, Choi Bong Je- Trnh Thu Hng cho nhng ngi n b h t qung qutng i qua  v u thm mt nim tin bay hnh phc d na. Choi Bong Je si i tnh bt chp d man ca t ci cho ty c c gi Vit anh thng. </p>\n<p>Cho d c gi 33 giai on y h t qung qutng  v mt d v h c cu con trai 5 giai on. (c tin chnh)</p>\n<div type=\"link\">Ph ph phn, kim im gim c s, ch to huyn tr xin l li dn</div></div>', 'TIN TT LNH 25/9: Php mu l ng ngi cha, 675 giy php con v tun mi cht cm hng', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'tin-tot-lanh-259-phep-mau-thieng-lieng-cua-nguoi-cha-675-giay-phep-con-va-tuan-moi-day-cam-hung', '', '', '2017-09-24 08:15:13', '2017-09-24 08:15:13', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/24/tin-tot-lanh-259-phep-mau-thieng-lieng-cua-nguoi-cha-675-giay-phep-con-va-tuan-moi-day-cam-hung/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
