INSERT INTO `np_posts` VALUES ('1632', '1', '2017-09-24 08:14:00', '2017-09-24 08:14:00', '<div data-field=\"body\" readability=\"38\">\n<p>iPhone 8 v iPhone 8 Plus tho chnh thc bt na t u ti mt mng th trng. Mt mng t my cng tho c xch tay bay Vit Nam t p ng nhu cu ca ngi s dng trong sut nc. Th m nm nay, chng kh nhng ngy u iPhone mi bay nc kh u m. </p>\n<p>Theo ng lch ca Apple, iPhone mi s bt na ra ngy 22 thng 9. Th m b ngy 20 thng 9, nhng chic my trc ht tho c mt ti Vit Nam. </p>\n<p>Nhng ng chng s li c ca v... trn tri t i nh d man nm th tht ti li c cho v kh nh nhm, ch trn di 20 triu vi, v khi chm cho iPhone 8.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506271252347.jpg\" w=\"640\" h=\"426\" alt=\"Chuy&#x1EC7;n x&#x1B0;a nay hi&#x1EBF;m: Ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i d&#xF9;ng Vi&#x1EC7;t th&#x1EDD; &#x1A1; v&#x1EDB;i iPhone m&#x1EDB;i - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" title=\"Chuy&#x1EC7;n x&#x1B0;a nay hi&#x1EBF;m: Ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i d&#xF9;ng Vi&#x1EC7;t th&#x1EDD; &#x1A1; v&#x1EDB;i iPhone m&#x1EDB;i - &#x1EA2;nh 1.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"24421530-a147-11e7-a89b-d53b14af2463\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506271252347.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">iPhone nm nay chng cn cng no lon th trng vi nhng ca... \"v in\".</p></div></div>\n<p>\"Cha bao gi v iPhone mi ti Vit Nam li thp ti vy,\" mt ngi i m Apple san s. Cn nh nm ngoi, nhng chic iPhone 7 trc ht c v ln ti 37 triu vi m vn chng c  my t na. </p>\n<p>Mc d v na cng chng vnh c iu chnh xung trng chc triu vi sau  t lu, th m v cao trong sut nhng ngy u xut hin lin gn lin vi hnh hnh nhng chic iPhone mi.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506271254113.png\" w=\"620\" h=\"709\" alt=\"Chuy&#x1EC7;n x&#x1B0;a nay hi&#x1EBF;m: Ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i d&#xF9;ng Vi&#x1EC7;t th&#x1EDD; &#x1A1; v&#x1EDB;i iPhone m&#x1EDB;i - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" title=\"Chuy&#x1EC7;n x&#x1B0;a nay hi&#x1EBF;m: Ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i d&#xF9;ng Vi&#x1EC7;t th&#x1EDD; &#x1A1; v&#x1EDB;i iPhone m&#x1EDB;i - &#x1EA2;nh 2.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"250d0650-a147-11e7-8e2d-d3f798772c52\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-1-1506271254113.png\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Din bin v cht kch tnh ca iPhone 7 v 7 Plus bui nm ngoi.</p></div></div>\n<p>D vy, danh thip li bun ti chng t ra qu bt thn vi khuynh hng no. Ch mt ca dy di ng ti H Ni san s. \"Chng mnh gn nh chng nhn c danh thip mt t dy trc cho iPhone 8 v 8 Plus xch tay trong sut nm nay,\" anh vch tht cho bit. </p>\n<p>\"Ngi s dng Vit Nam, nguyn tho nu i qu lu cho mt chic iPhone c i thay to, cn nhn th i chic iPhone X c na ra ra thng 11 ti,\" ngi no ni thm. </p>\n<p>T<span>hc t, iPhone 8 v 8 Plus nm nay chng c giu d bit so vi bn b tin nhim, ngoi ngoi tr vic c bn k l s phi hp gia kim kh - king vi mt mng tnh hay mi h trng ti camera v kh hay sc chng dy. </span></p>\n<p>\"Khng c l do g t iPhone 8, 8 Plus hoi mngt  th chm no. Ngi s dng s i my chnh hng ra mt t c nhng chnh sch tt hn, v n nh hn hay i iPhone X,\" Minh Tm, mt ngi i m Apple lu nm, nhn nh.</p>\n<div type=\"Photo\">\n<div><img src=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-2-1506271254116.jpg\" w=\"620\" h=\"413\" alt=\"Chuy&#x1EC7;n x&#x1B0;a nay hi&#x1EBF;m: Ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i d&#xF9;ng Vi&#x1EC7;t th&#x1EDD; &#x1A1; v&#x1EDB;i iPhone m&#x1EDB;i - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" title=\"Chuy&#x1EC7;n x&#x1B0;a nay hi&#x1EBF;m: Ng&#x1B0;&#x1EDD;i d&#xF9;ng Vi&#x1EC7;t th&#x1EDD; &#x1A1; v&#x1EDB;i iPhone m&#x1EDB;i - &#x1EA2;nh 3.\" rel=\"lightbox\" photoid=\"2521c6d0-a147-11e7-8a08-1bdf9c92da84\" type=\"photo\" data-original=\"http://sohanews.sohacdn.com/2017/photo-2-1506271254116.jpg\" width=\"\" height=\"\"/></div>\n<div readability=\"1\">\n<p data-placeholder=\"[nh&#x1EAD;p ch&#xFA; th&#xED;ch]\">Bn ngoi Apple Store ti London Anh ra ngy u bt na iPhone 8.</p></div></div>\n<p> giu th trng bt na iPhone 8/ 8 Plus, cng chng cn nhng dy trng hc ngi xp dy i mua iPhone mi.  Singapore, nm nay l nm trc ht Apple Store chnh thc i ra hot ng, th m ra ngy u bt na iPhone mi, cng ch c chng 200 ngi i mua my. </p>\n<p>Nhng nm trc, mc du cha c Apple Store, tnh trng n rnh nm i trng m t i mua iPhone mi ti nh nc bt na iPhone sm nht ng Nam  no chng c t bt gp. Ti danh thip th trng to khc nh c, Anh hay thm ch l qu hng iPhone M cng cho ch tht ti tng t.</p>\n<div type=\"link\">Nhng mu ta xe tay ga \"sang chhnh\" ch dnh cho gii i gia</div></div>', 'Chuyn c nay him: Ngi s dng Vit bng quan cng iPhone mi', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'chuyen-xua-nay-hiem-nguoi-dung-viet-tho-o-voi-iphone-moi', '', '', '2017-09-24 08:14:00', '2017-09-24 08:14:00', '', '0', 'http://localhost/wordpress/2017/09/24/chuyen-xua-nay-hiem-nguoi-dung-viet-tho-o-voi-iphone-moi/', '0', 'post', '', '0');
